#. [message]: speaker=Bagork
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/08_Xenophobia.cfg:694
msgid "I will kill all of you!"
msgstr "Eu matarei todos vocês!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. The unit who killed Bagork responds to Bagork's last breath, which was "I will kill all of you!"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/08_Xenophobia.cfg:705
