#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/09_Castle_in_the_Ice.cfg:1529
msgid "GROARRR!!!"
msgstr "GROARRR!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/09_Castle_in_the_Ice.cfg:1540
msgid "I’ve never tried Yeti meat. I wonder what it tastes like?"
msgstr "Eu nunca provei carne de Yeti. Eu me pergunto qual será o gosto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. the player has moved a unit (any unit) to the castle
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/09_Castle_in_the_Ice.cfg:1563
msgid "This is the place! Let us enter."
msgstr "Este é o lugar! Vamos entrar."

#. [scenario]: id=10_Dark_Sanctuary
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:4
msgid "Dark Sanctuary"
msgstr "Santuário Sombrio"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Sequestered away under ice and stone, the dark places of the world quietly "
"count the long years, biding their time until once more disturbed."
msgstr ""
"Isolados sob gelo e pedra, os lugares escuros do mundo silenciosamente "
"contam os longos anos, aguardando o momento certo até uma vez mais serem "
"perturbados."

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:125
msgid "Goblins"
msgstr "Goblins"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:261
msgid "Injured Yeti"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. a significant hint, exploring would take a long time with no reward
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:296
msgid ""
"Ugh, more ants. I doubt there’s anything of value in here, just more of that "
"lousy ambrosia."
msgstr ""
"Argh, mais formigas. Eu duvido que exista algo de valor aqui, apenas mais "
"daquela nojenta ambrosia."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:544
msgid "Study Guard"
msgstr "Guarda de Estudo"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:573
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2916
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:514
msgid "Cowardly Goblin"
msgstr "Goblin Covarde"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:580
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1920
msgid "Thirsty Goblin"
msgstr "Goblin Sedento"

# Acho que é um nome, mas não tenho certeza, não conhegi perceber onde aparece.
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:585
msgid "Dushab"
msgstr "Dushab"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:620
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2235
msgid "Goblin Leader"
msgstr "Líder Goblin"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:678
msgid "Move Dacyn, Gweddry, and reinforcements into the gate"
msgstr "Mova Dacyn, Gweddry, e reforços para o portão"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:685
msgid "Find both gate keys"
msgstr "Ache ambas as chaves do portão"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:692
msgid "Move Dacyn, Gweddry, and reinforcements into the inner gate"
msgstr "Mova Dacyn, Gweddry, e reforços para o portão interno"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:699
msgid "Defeat the sanctum guard"
msgstr "Derrote o guarda do santuário"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:706
msgid "Retrieve the amulet"
msgstr "Recupere o amuleto"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:711
msgid "Survive the orcish assault"
msgstr "Sobreviva ao ataque dos orcs"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:728
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "To enter the castle, move Dacyn into the gated area."
msgid "To enter the castle, move Dacyn into the gated area and end your turn."
msgstr "Para entrar no castelo, mova Dacyn para a área fechada."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:734
msgid ""
"Dacyn has been here before and will have better outcomes when stepping on "
"runes."
msgstr ""
"Dacyn já esteve aqui antes e terá melhores resultados ao pisar em runas."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. Iliah-Malal was the male lich antagonist of Delfador's Memoirs, around 160 years ago
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:762
msgid ""
"We have arrived. This is a long-abandoned sanctum that you may know as the "
"lair of the mage Iliah-Malal."
msgstr ""
"Chegamos. Este é o a muito abandonado santuário que vocês talvez conheçam "
"como o covil do mago Iliah-Malal."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. once again Dacyn is an unreliable narrator and does not speak absolute truth, he only says what he knows
#. in fact the Amulet by itself can't do what he says it does, that's just his assumption
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:768
msgid ""
"It is here that I seek Iliah-Malal’s Amulet of the Veil, an artifact "
"possessing the power to open gates between the land of the living and that "
"of the dead.\n"
"\n"
"I once thought such a power too dangerous to use; I am no longer so naive."
msgstr ""
"É aqui que procuro o amuleto do Véu de Iliah-Malal, um artefato que possui o "
"poder de abrir o portais entre a terra dos vivos e a dos mortos.\n"
"\n"
"No passado eu considerei tal poder perigoso demais para ser usado; Já não "
"sou mais tão ingênuo."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:774
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Iliah-Malal? I know that name from the legends..."
msgid "Iliah-Malal? I know that name from the histories..."
msgstr "Iliah-Malal? Eu conheço este nome das lendas..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:783
msgid ""
"All this time... all this time I thought we were questing towards a noble "
"goal. Searching for a legendary sword, an ancient tome, a holy relic."
msgstr ""
"Todo esse tempo... todo esse tempo eu pensei que estávamos atrás de um nobre "
"objetivo. Procurando uma espada lendária, um tomo ancião, uma relíquia "
"sagrada."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:787
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Instead, our quest brings us to the lair of one of the most evil beings "
#| "that ever lived. How can you possibly mean to make use of anything ever "
#| "possessed by such an evil? As soldiers of Wesnoth we are honor-bound to "
#| "fight for the Light, not the darkness!"
msgid ""
"Instead, our quest brings us to the lair of a necromancer?! How can you "
"possibly mean to make use of anything ever possessed by such an evil? As "
"soldiers of Wesnoth we are honor-bound to fight for the Light, not the "
"darkness!"
msgstr ""
"Ao invés disso, nossa missão nos levou até o covil de um dos seres mais "
"malignos já viveu. Como você pode sequer pensar em usar algo que pertenceu a "
"um ser tão maligno? Como soldados de Wesnoth, nós somos é nosso dever lutar "
"pela Luz, não pelas trevas!"

# Não estou feliz com a tradução.
#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:791
msgid ""
"Do not be so shortsighted. With the power to open portals to the Land of the "
"Dead, I can pull Mal-Ravanal’s spirit out of this world. Then, the spells "
"granting false life to the dead will fail, and their fearsome armies will "
"collapse into piles of bones. I am wielding this power for the good of "
"Irdya, not for your honor’s sake."
msgstr ""
"Não seja tão moralista. Com o poder de abrir portais para a Terra dos "
"Mortos, eu posso arrastar o espírito de Mal-Ravanal para fora deste mundo. "
"Então, as magias que dão vida falsa para os mortos-vivos falharão, e seus "
"temíveis exércitos se tornarão nada mais do que pilhas de ossos. Eu estou "
"empunhando este poder para o bem de Irdya, não para o bem de sua honra."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:795
msgid ""
"Dacyn, I am uneasy about this course of action. I know little of the Land of "
"the Dead, but everything I have heard suggests-"
msgstr ""
"Dacyn, eu estou apreensivo com este curso de ação. Sei pouco sobre a Terra "
"dos Mortos, mas tudo que eu ouvi sugere-"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:799
msgid ""
"You would violate the dead’s eternal peace to fight a war, yet you call me "
"shortsighted?! And while our homeland bleeds, you have the gall to speak of "
"the good of all life?! Madness! As a mage of the Light, you should know "
"better!"
msgstr ""
"Você violaria a paz eterna dos mortos para lutar uma guerra, e ainda assim "
"me chama de moralista?! E enquanto nossa terra natal sangra, você tem a "
"audácia de falar do bem de toda a vida?! Loucura! Como um mago da Luz, você "
"deveria agir de forma melhor!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:803
msgid ""
"I have had enough of your second-guessing. You, fool of a horse boy, know "
"nothing of the mystic arts, yet you mask your ignorance by cowering behind a "
"pretend morality. If that is what you insist on doing, then by all means "
"return to Wesnoth and add your corpses to Mal-Ravanal’s ever-growing hordes."
msgstr ""
"Eu já ouvi palpites o suficiente de você. Você, tolo garoto dos cavalos, não "
"sabe nada sobre as artes místicas, e ainda assim mascara sua ignorância "
"atrás de uma falsa moralidade. Se isto é o que insistes em fazer, então pode "
"voltar para Wesnoth e dar mais corpos para as hordas crescentes de Mal-"
"Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:807
msgid ""
"Unlike you, I have the knowledge and power to defeat the undead, and I "
"intend to use it to destroy Mal-Ravanal. Will you wallow in your "
"shortsightedness, or do you intend to help me safeguard all that lives?"
msgstr ""
"Ao contrário de você, eu tenho o conhecimento e o poder para derrotar os "
"mortos-vivos, e eu pretendo usá-lo para destruir Mal-Ravanal. Você vai se "
"prender a sua falsa moralidade, ou pretende me ajudar a proteger todas essas "
"vidas?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:816
msgid ""
"I will help you. We have come this far, and it seems a waste to turn back "
"now."
msgstr ""
"Eu irei ajudar você. Nós viemos tão longe, e parece um desperdício desistir "
"agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:820
msgid ""
"By the Clans, I will not!! Would that I had perished in battle against the "
"undead! Better that than living to see Wesnoth’s high mage succumb to the "
"temptation of darkness."
msgstr ""
"Pelos clãs, eu não irei te ajudar!! Quem me dera ter morrido em batalha "
"contra os mortos-vivos! Melhor isso do que viver para ver o mais alto mago "
"de Wesnoth sucumbir à tentação das trevas."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:824
msgid ""
"Gweddry, if you truly wish to aid this madman, I will guard the outer gates "
"for you. But I will not enter that evil stronghold. I would sooner perish "
"than travel one step closer towards Dacyn’s foul amulet."
msgstr ""
"Gweddry, se você realmente insiste em ajudar este louco, eu irei guardar os "
"portões externos para você. Mas eu não entrarei nesta fortaleza maligna. "
"Preferiria morrer do que dar mais um passo em direção do amuleto pérfido de "
"Dacyn."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:833
msgid ""
"Ah, I still remember this place quite clearly. Now that I think of it, Ravan "
"had always been very interested in the magic of darkness. Apparently, the "
"balance between light and dark would be crucial to the safety of Irdya in "
"the future, at least according to Ravan’s theory. In hindsight, that was all "
"nonsense."
msgstr ""
"Ah, eu ainda me lembro bem deste local. Agora, penso bem, Ravan sempre teve "
"muito interesse pela magia das trevas. Aparentemente, o equilíbrio entre a "
"luz e as sombras seria crucial para a segurança de Irdya no futuro, ao menos "
"de acordo com a teoria de Ravan. Agora posso dizer que isso tudo era tolice."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:837
msgid "The irony seems lost on you."
msgstr "Parece que você não percebeu a ironia."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:841
msgid ""
"Back then this place was full of traps and undead, and it will no doubt be "
"worse now that the wild beasts have had a chance to move in."
msgstr ""
"Naquela época este lugar era cheio de armadilhas e mortos-vivos, e sem "
"dúvida será pior agora que bestas selvagens tiveram a chance de se "
"estabelecer aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:852
msgid ""
"Ravan sealed this place before our last meeting. I need a moment to remember "
"the incantation."
msgstr ""
"Ravan selou este lugar antes de nosso último encontro. Eu preciso de um "
"momento para me lembrar do encantamento."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. the "red star" refers to the Ruby of Fire, and the "red stone" refers to the Amulet of the Veil FYI but these are not to be explicitly mentioned
#. the "black pool" would be located near or under Weldyn, but again not to be explicitly mentioned
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:862
msgid ""
"The red star blazes,\n"
"The red stone bleeds.\n"
"The black pool swallows all voices,\n"
"The darkness between worlds opens its maw."
msgstr ""
"A estrela vermelha em chamas,\n"
"A rocha vermelha sangra.\n"
"A piscina negra devora todas as vozes,\n"
"A escuridão entre mundos abre sua boca."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:889
msgid ""
"Ugh, spellcasting always gives me the shivers. There’s a reason the more "
"civilized people of my homeland don’t trifle with magic!"
msgstr ""
"Ugh, conjurar feitiços sempre me dá arrepios. Existe uma razão para as "
"pessoas mais civilizadas da minha terra natal não brincarem com magia!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:893
msgid "For a mage of the Light, the words you speak are dark indeed."
msgstr ""
"Para um mago da Luz, as palavras que você profere são verdadeiramente "
"sombrias."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:897
msgid ""
"I’m a simple man. I use simple tools and weapons. This magic stuff is givin’ "
"me the creeps."
msgstr ""
"Eu sou um homem simples. Eu uso ferramentas e armas simples. Essa tal magia "
"está me dando arrepios."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:907
msgid ""
"This antechamber only has room for eight. I must go to retrieve the "
"artifact, and Gweddry has agreed to accompany me, so that leaves room for "
"six more."
msgstr ""
"Esta antecâmara só tem espaço para oito pessoas. Eu devo ir recuperar o "
"artefato e Gweddry concordou em me acompanhar, então temos espaço para mais "
"seis."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. the player needs to choose 6 troops
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:926
msgid ""
"Gweddry, are you still choosing your troops? I must end my turn in the "
"antechamber to cycle the gate and enter the sanctuary."
msgstr ""
"Gweddry, você ainda está escolhendo suas tropas? Eu preciso terminar meu "
"turno na antecâmara para acionar o portão e entrar no santuário."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:945
msgid "I will not aid in this evil quest."
msgstr "Eu não me juntarei a esta missão maligna."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. somewhat like an airlock
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:999
msgid "I am ready to cycle the gates. Gweddry, shall we proceed?"
msgstr "Eu estou pronto para acionar os portões. Gweddry, devemos proceder?"

#. [option]
#. 6 soldiers
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1002
msgid "Yes, these are the soldiers I want."
msgstr "Sim, estes são os soldados que eu quero."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1010
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2486
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:849
msgid "No, not yet."
msgstr "Não, ainda não."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1019
msgid ""
"Gweddry, you agreed to accompany me. We must both enter this antechamber "
"before I cycle the gates."
msgstr ""
"Gweddry, você concordou em me acompanhar. Nós dois precisamos entrar nesta "
"antecâmara antes de eu ativar os portões."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1079
msgid "Cave scary! Grug no like!"
msgstr "Caverna apavorante! Grug não gosta!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. the torches were already burning before any of Gweddry's party entered the castle
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1087
msgid "The torches are lit..."
msgstr "As tochas estão acesas..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#. "I have seen my fair share of dark caves, but something about this place is making me shake."
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1100
msgid ""
"I ha’ seen my fair share o’ dark caves, but summat ’bout this place be "
"givin’ me the shakes."
msgstr ""
"Eu já vi a miña cota de covas escuras, pero algo neste lugar está a fazer me "
"tremer."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#. at the moment he's seeing the inside of a castle, the lit torches, and a wild yeti
#. there's nothing particularly unholy to focus on
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1115
msgid "May this unholy place be cleansed by the Light!"
msgstr "Que este lugar profano seja purificado pela Luz!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1199
msgid "GROWWR!!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. 200, 160, or 130 gold
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1214
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "This wyvern was rich! I count $gold gold in its hoard."
msgid "This yeti was rich! I count $gold gold in its hoard."
msgstr "Este wyvern era rico! Eu conto $gold peças de ouro em seu tesouro."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1219
msgid "Ho ho, northerners’ gold, now that begins to make this all worth it!"
msgstr "Ho ho, ouro dos nortistas, agora tudo isso começa a valer a pena!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. a signpost. "Study" as in a room with a reading desk and small library
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1239
msgid "East: Study and Vaults"
msgstr "Leste: Estudo e Cofres"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. a signpost
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1257
msgid "West: Laboratory and Experiment Testing"
msgstr "Oeste: Laboratório e Teste de Experimentos"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1308
msgid ""
"I have triggered a trap. As long as I stay on this rune I will be safe, but "
"once I step away, fire spirits will rise from the lava."
msgstr ""
"Acionei uma armadilha. Enquanto permanecer nesta runa eu estarei seguro, mas "
"assim que eu me pisar fora dela, espíritos de fogo se levantarão da lava."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the feeling that they've triggered a trap
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1319
msgid "Uh oh..."
msgstr "Ha não..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. no obvious effect yet, it triggers when that unit moves again
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1328
msgid "Oh, nothing happened."
msgstr "Ah, nada aconteceu."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. a walking corpse of a rat or spider
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1336
msgid ""
"That corpse has triggered a trap. When next it moves, fire spirits will rise "
"from the lava."
msgstr ""
"Aquele corpo acionou uma armadilha. Quando ele se mover de novo, espíritos "
"de fogo se levantarão da lava."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. the rune is on the floor in front of the door (using one of the terrains that make the rune occupy most of the hex)
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1388
msgid ""
"This gate is locked, and I recognize the petrification trap concealed within "
"its guardian rune. I should avoid trying to open it."
msgstr ""
"Este portão está trancado, e eu reconheço a armadilha de petrificação oculta "
"em sua runa guardiã. Eu devo evitar abri-la."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the rune is on the floor in front of the door (using one of the terrains that make the rune occupy most of the hex)
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1399
msgid "Looks like this gate is locked. I wonder if this rune opens it?"
msgstr "Parece que o portão está trancado. Eu me pergunto se esta runa o abre?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1446
msgid "That was a petrification rune. It should wear off in a few moments."
msgstr ""
"Essa era uma runa de petrificação. O efeito deve passar em alguns instantes."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1453
msgid ""
"We are fortunate, that enemy has triggered a petrification rune. Be warned "
"though, it will only last a few moments."
msgstr ""
"Demos sorte, aquele inimigo foi pego por uma runa de petrificação. Fiquem "
"atentos, isso durará somente alguns instantes."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the unit triggers the trap immediately
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1507
msgid ""
"Hmm, looks like a magic lamp. I’ve heard stories that these can grant "
"wishes. Today must be my lucky day!"
msgstr ""
"Hmm, aparenta com uma lâmpada mágica. Eu já histórias que essas conseguem "
"garantir desejos. Hoje deve ser meu dia de sorte!"

#. [message]: speaker=Jinn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1544
msgid "WHO DARES DISTURB MY SLUMBER?"
msgstr "QUEM OUSA PERTURBAR MEU SONO?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. an item on a display rack, ready to be worn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1558
msgid ""
"This fine silken cloak would be priceless back in Wesnoth, but is useless to "
"us here."
msgstr ""
"Este fino casaco de seda seria inestimável em Wesnoth, mas é inútil para nós "
"aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. 70, 55, or 45 gold
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1578
msgid "This chest contains $gold gold!"
msgstr "Este baú contém $gold peças de ouro!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. there was a closed chest on this hex, and it's been opened
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1598
msgid "It’s full of... toilet paper?!?"
msgstr "Está cheio de... papel higiênico?!?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. and the unit immediately does that, changing a closed-gate terrain to open-gate
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1613
msgid "I can unlock this gate from the inside."
msgstr "Eu consigo destrancar este portão por dentro."

#. [message]: speaker=Study Guard
#. the Study Guard is a Deathblade (or Draug on hard difficulty) that's stood immobile in the doorway
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1634
msgid "Who. Comes?"
msgstr "Quem. Vem?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1638
msgid "Err... don’t mind me, I’m just taking a look around."
msgstr "Err... não se importe comigo, eu só estou dando uma olhando por aí."

#. [message]: speaker=Study Guard
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1642
msgid "Master. Is away. Intruders. Must die."
msgstr "Mestre. Está ausente. Intrusos. Devem morrer."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. a quote from the journal written in SotA, also quoted in DiD
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1676
msgid ""
"What’s this? Looks like a book on necromancy? <i>‘To become a lich, one must "
"first-</i>"
msgstr ""
"O que é isso? Parece um livro sobre necromancia? <i>\"Para se tornar um "
"lich, primeiro é preciso-</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1680
msgid "Drop that at once! That journal is dangerous!"
msgstr "Largue isso agora! Este diário é perigoso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. a book on necromancy
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1700
msgid ""
"I recognize this volume. Such a thing could be dangerous in the wrong hands. "
"Perhaps I should hold on to it... for safekeeping."
msgstr ""
"Eu reconheço este volume. Tal tomo seria perigosa nas mãos erradas. Talvez "
"eu devesse ficar com a custódia dele... para que não caia nas mãos erradas."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1707
msgid ""
"... I recognize this volume. It is fortunate that I found it first; such a "
"thing could be dangerous in the wrong hands. Perhaps I should hold on to "
"it... for safekeeping."
msgstr ""
"... Reconheço este volume. Fui afortunado por tê-lo encontrado primeiro; tal "
"coisa seria perigosa nas mãos erradas. Talvez eu devesse ficar com a "
"custódia dele... para que não caia nas mãos erradas."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1726
msgid "There are a few loose pages on the ground here..."
msgstr "Há algumas páginas soltas aqui no chão..."

# Iliah-Malal é uma referência a campanha "Memórias de Delfador"
#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1730
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<i>Journal of Ravan - 13 Blackfire, 588 YW.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "This expedition is proving a greater success than I had anticipated. "
#| "While Dacyn disarms the traps littered around this place, I have been "
#| "able to conduct extensive research into the other plane beyond the Maw. "
#| "There is a realm of souls that can be reached from our very own world, "
#| "one that Iliah-Malal doubtlessly made contact with using the Amulet of "
#| "the Veil. From time to time, I hear spirits whispering from the other "
#| "side, but their voices are faint as of yet. I suspect that if I can "
#| "somehow reach them, they will be able to answer some of the questions I "
#| "have been pondering. However, there seems to be a piece of the puzzle "
#| "still missing.</i>"
msgid ""
"<i>Journal of Ravan — 13 Blackfire, 588 YW.\n"
"\n"
"This expedition is proving a greater success than I had anticipated. While "
"Dacyn disarms the traps littered around this place, I have been able to "
"conduct extensive research into the other plane beyond the Maw. There is a "
"realm of souls that can be reached from our very own world, one that Iliah-"
"Malal doubtlessly made contact with using the Amulet of the Veil. From time "
"to time, I hear spirits whispering from the other side, but their voices are "
"faint as of yet. I suspect that if I can somehow reach them, they will be "
"able to answer some of the questions I have been pondering. However, there "
"seems to be a piece of the puzzle still missing.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Diário de Ravan - 13 Blackfire, 588 AW.\n"
"\n"
"Esta expedição está se provando um sucesso maior do que eu esperava. "
"Enquanto Dacyn desarma as armadilhas espalhadas ao redor deste lugar, eu "
"tenho sido capaz de conduzir uma extensa pesquisa sobre o outro plano além "
"da Boca. Existe um reino de almas que pode ser alcançado através do nosso "
"mundo, um que Iliah-Malal sem dúvida fez contato usando o Amuleto do Véu. De "
"tempos em tempos, eu ouço espíritos sussurrando do outro lado, mas suas "
"vozes ainda são tênues. Eu suspeito que se de alguma forma eu for capaz de "
"chegar a eles, eles serão capaz de responder algumas das questões que eu "
"tenho ponderado. Entretanto, parece haver um pedaço do quebra-cabeça "
"faltando.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1736
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<i>Journal of Ravan - 21 Whitefire, 589 YW.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "I had a dream tonight. Was it a dream? It seemed much more like a vision. "
#| "I saw a scorching light from twin orbs in the sky, radiating searing "
#| "brightness over a land teeming with aberrations of constantly shifting "
#| "flesh. I saw a jewel, no, a key, alight with fire bridging the vast "
#| "nothingness of the Maw. I saw darkness, merged with light and "
#| "transfigured, rending the indestructible core of those without form. I "
#| "hear voices recounting these muddled dreams, yet their words are "
#| "disjointed, incomprehensible. What are they trying to tell me?</i>"
msgid ""
"<i>Journal of Ravan — 21 Whitefire, 589 YW.\n"
"\n"
"I had a dream tonight. Was it a dream? It seemed much more like a vision. I "
"saw a scorching light from twin orbs in the sky, radiating searing "
"brightness over a land teeming with aberrations of constantly shifting "
"flesh. I saw a jewel, no, a key, alight with fire bridging the vast "
"nothingness of the Maw. I saw darkness, merged with light and transfigured, "
"rending the indestructible core of those without form. I hear voices "
"recounting these muddled dreams, yet their words are disjointed, "
"incomprehensible. What are they trying to tell me?</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Diário de Ravan - 21 Whitefire, 589 AW.\n"
"\n"
"Eu tive um sonho esta noite. Será que foi mesmo um sonho? Pareceu-me muito "
"mais como uma visão. Eu vi uma luz ardente saindo de orbes gêmeos no céu, "
"irradiando um brilho abrasador sobre uma terra fervilhando com aberrações de "
"carne em constante transformação. Eu vi uma joia, não, uma chave, acesa com "
"fogo, sendo uma ponte para o vasto vazio da boca. Vi a escuridão, misturada "
"com luz e transfigurada, rasgando a indestrutível essência daqueles sem "
"forma. Eu ouço vozes recontando estes sonhos confusos, mas suas palavras são "
"desconexas, incompreensíveis. O que eles estão tentando me contar?</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1749
msgid ""
"This volume has something to do with a dwarf named Tharga... Thursag-"
"something? The text is very faded."
msgstr ""
"Este volume tem algo a ver com um anão chamado Tharga... Thursag-alguma "
"coisa? O texto está bem apagado."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1760
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<i>Journal of Ravan - 5 Bleeding Moon, 597 YW.\n"
#| "\n"
#| "Nothing is going well. My research has come to a dead end and even the "
#| "spirits from the other plane no longer speak to me. I can no longer rely "
#| "on Dacyn either. That stupid man! He decided that playing politics would "
#| "be a better use of his abilities than helping me decipher this crucial "
#| "puzzle. As if he could do any good, being the advisor to that half-"
#| "decrepit old King Haldric. Then again, maybe that is the game Dacyn wants "
#| "to play. What a shame. I had held him in higher regard than that.</i>"
msgid ""
"<i>Journal of Ravan — 5 Bleeding Moon, 597 YW.\n"
"\n"
"Nothing is going well. My research has come to a dead end and even the "
"spirits from the other plane no longer speak to me. I can no longer rely on "
"Dacyn either. That stupid man! He decided that playing politics would be a "
"better use of his abilities than helping me decipher this crucial puzzle. As "
"if he could do any good, being the advisor to that half-decrepit old King "
"Haldric. Then again, maybe that is the game Dacyn wants to play. What a "
"shame. I had held him in higher regard than that.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Diário de Ravan - 5 Bleeding Moon, 597 AW.\n"
"\n"
"Nada está indo bem. Minha pesquisa chegou em um beco sem saída e mesmo os "
"espíritos do outro plano não mais falam comigo. E também já não posso mais "
"confiar no Dacyn. Aquele homem estúpido! Ele decidiu que se meter com "
"política seria um uso melhor de suas habilidades do que me ajudar a decifrar "
"este enigma crucial. Como se ele pudesse fazer algo de bom, sendo o "
"conselheiro deste velho e meio decrépito Rei Haldric. Mas, pensando bem, "
"talvez este seja o jogo que Dacyn queira jogar. Mas que pena. Eu esperava "
"mais dele.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. just flavortext, could be any books that are irrelevant to the story
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1774
msgid ""
"This shelf appears to be full of accounting ledgers detailing the movement "
"of funds and goods hundreds of years ago."
msgstr ""
"Esta estante aparenta estar cheia de Ledgers detalhando o movimentação dos "
"fundos e bens de centenas de anos atrás."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. a wooden crate, using the items/box.png image
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1788
msgid "This box is empty."
msgstr "Esta caixa está vazia."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. a wooden crate, using the items/box.png image
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1800
msgid "Yuck, this box is full of pickled fingers!"
msgstr "Eca, esta caixa está cheia de dedos em conserva!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. a barrel, using items/barrel.png
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1812
msgid ""
"This cask of wine is from nearly 200 years ago! If only I was allowed to "
"drink while on duty."
msgstr ""
"Este barril de vinho tem cerca de 200 anos! Se ao menos eu pudesse beber em "
"serviço."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1826
msgid ""
"These three orbs must be ancient, but still pulse with some kind of dark "
"energy. Just standing near them gives me a splitting headache."
msgstr ""
"Estas três orbes devem ser bem antigas, mas ainda pulsam com algum tipo de "
"energia sombria. Só de ficar perto deles me deu uma dor de cabeça terrível."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1839
msgid ""
"I’ve found a key! It must be magical; it started glowing as soon as I "
"touched it."
msgstr ""
"Eu achei uma chave! Ela deve ser mágica; começou a brilhar assim que a "
"toquei."

#. [message]: speaker=Cowardly Goblin
#. Cowardly Goblin is male, and appears in just two events. This one, and the end-of-level event.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1872
msgid "Aaah, humans! Run away!"
msgstr "Aaah, humanos! Fujam!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1879
msgid ""
"I guess there are goblins living here. Well, that explains the lit torches."
msgstr ""
"Eu acho que há góblins vivendo aqui. Bem, isso explica as tochas acesas."

#. [message]: speaker=Thirsty Goblin
#. the goblin has moved to a hex with a green potion bottle. After this he drinks it, gets poisoned, and then turns into a walking corpse.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1894
msgid "Hey, this looks tasty!"
msgstr "Ei, isso parece gostoso!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the player's unit has moved to a hex with a blue potion, drunk it, and become slowed
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1953
msgid "Ugh, my head hurts. Was this room always spinning?"
msgstr "Ai, minha cabeça dói. Essa sala está girando ou sou eu?"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the player's unit has moved to a hex with a yellow potion, drunk it, and become poisoned
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:1981
msgid ""
"Blech, this tastes awful! Whatever used to be in here, it went bad long ago."
msgstr ""
"Eca, o gosto disso é horrível! O que quer que estivesse ali, estragou faz "
"muito tempo."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the player's unit has moved to a hex with a grey potion, drunk it, and ...
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2004
msgid "ACK! I’M DYING!"
msgstr "ACK! EU ESTOU MORRENDO!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the grey potion
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2013
msgid "Hah, just messing with you, it’s only water."
msgstr "Hah, estava só brincando com você, isso aí é água."

# Sobre Ghast, a tradução Brasileira traduziu como Ghast, então deixe assim.
#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. the player's unit is outside the room with all of this in
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2042
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Look, a key! But it’s guarded by all those goblins... and there are "
#| "ghasts in cages!"
msgid ""
"Look, a key! But it’s guarded by all those goblins... and there are ghouls "
"in cages!"
msgstr ""
"Veja, uma chave! Mas ela está guardada por todos esses góblins... e há "
"ghasts em celas!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. the player's unit is outside the room with ghasts and goblins in, and there are a lot of campfires in there too
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2047
msgid ""
"The goblins’ eyes must be blinded by their fires. I still haven’t been "
"spotted."
msgstr ""
"Os olhos dos góblins devem estar cegos por causa do fogo. Eu ainda não fui "
"visto."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. rune on the floor that will open floor-to-ceiling gates
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2071
msgid ""
"Hmm, it looks like this rune is connected to those cages. I’ll bet I could "
"get one of them open..."
msgstr ""
"Hmm, parece que esta runa está conectada àquelas celas. Eu aposto que "
"conseguiria abrir uma delas..."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2073
msgid "Yes, release some ghouls."
msgstr "Isso, libere alguns carniçais."

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2097
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2180
msgid "Aaahh!! The monsters have escaped!"
msgstr "Aaahh!! Os monstros escaparam!"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2108
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2191
msgid "No, keep them locked up."
msgstr "Não, os mantenha trancados."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. rune on the floor that will open floor-to-ceiling gates
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2132
msgid ""
"Ah, this is the control for the experiment testing cages. Should I open them?"
msgstr "Ah, este é o controle para as celas de experimento. Devo abri-las?"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2134
msgid "Yes, release all the ghouls."
msgstr "Sim, liberte todos os carniçais."

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2218
msgid "Humans! Get them!"
msgstr "Humanos! Peguem eles!"

#. [message]: speaker=Goblin Leader
#. death of a wolf rider's mount
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2239
msgid "Noooo, wolfieeee!!!"
msgstr "Nãooo, lobinhooo!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2254
msgid "Look what I found! This key started glowing as soon as I touched it."
msgstr "Olhem o que eu achei! Esta chave começou a brilhar assim que a toquei."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. although there's no filter on this event, the location is only reachable by a flying unit, presumably a walking corpse bat or walking corpse drake
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2293
msgid "Ruuuh... Brains..."
msgstr "Ruuuh... Cérebros..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. This is an easter egg, and the details don't matter because there's no way to get the staff out of the room.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2299
msgid ""
"This legendary magical staff has the power to reshape reality at will! "
"Unfortunately, this zombie is not intelligent enough to understand the "
"significance of what it has found, and merely perceives a lifeless room."
msgstr ""
"Este lendário cajado mágico tem o poder de remodelar a realidade ao seu bel "
"prazer! Infelizmente, este zumbi não é inteligente o suficiente para "
"entender o significado do que encontrou, e meramente vê uma sala sem vida."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2341
msgid ""
"The Amulet should be just beyond that gate, within the inner sanctum. We "
"will have to find a pair of magical keys to open the door."
msgstr ""
"O amuleto deve estar logo depois desse portão, no santuário interno. Nós "
"teremos que encontrar um par de chaves mágicas para abrir o portão."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2356
msgid ""
"Both keys are found! We can now enter the inner sanctum and retrieve the "
"Amulet."
msgstr ""
"As duas chaves foram encontradas! Nós agora podemos entrar no santuário "
"interno e recuperar o Amuleto."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. by this time Owaec is probably fighting orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2387
msgid "I hope Owaec hasn’t gotten into any trouble outside..."
msgstr "Eu espero que Owaec não tenha se metido em confusão lá fora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2413
msgid "Are we ready to enter the inner sanctum?"
msgstr "Estamos prontos para entrar no santuário interno?"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2415
msgid "Yes, I’m ready."
msgstr "Sim, estamos prontos."

#. [command]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2422
msgid "Sanctum Guard"
msgstr "Guarda do santuário"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. looking at it from about 3 indoor hexes away
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2458
msgid "Is that... the Amulet?"
msgstr "Este é... o Amuleto?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2462
msgid ""
"Yes. We now look upon one of the most powerful artifacts ever to taint "
"Irdya. But first, we must clear out this room."
msgstr ""
"Sim. Nós estamos olhando um dos mais poderosos artefatos que corromperam "
"Irdya. Mas, primeiro, nós precisamos limpar esta sala."

#. [message]: speaker=Sanctum Guard
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2466
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "TRESSPASSERS!"
msgid "TRESPASSERS!"
msgstr "INVASORES!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2470
msgid "Prepare for incoming undead!"
msgstr "Preparem-se para mortos-vivos vindo!"

#. [event]
#. [side]: type=Orcish Sovereign, id=Chief Dra-Nak
#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2503
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2907
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:42
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:119
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:29
msgid "Chief Dra-Nak"
msgstr "Chefe Dra-Nak"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. the wyrms being the drakes in S09
#. Talking about Owaec, who's waiting outside the sanctum, probably on a keep.
#. Owaec probably hasn't recruited, but the entire recall list is available to him so they're presumably "here".
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2519
msgid "What do we have here? This is what those wyrms were groveling about?"
msgstr "O que temos aqui? É isso que humilhou aqueles wyrms ?"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. he's a chief from the Whitefangs because he's not the only one, just a particularly powerful one
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2524
msgid ""
"I’m Dra-Nak, Chief from the Whitefang clan. What’re you doing so far away "
"from home, human?"
msgstr ""
"Eu sou Dra-Nak, Chefe do clã Presas-brancas. O que está fazendo tão longe de "
"sua casa, humano?"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2528
msgid ""
"I am a lord of the Horse Clans, and we are here on Wesnoth business. You "
"would do well not to bother us."
msgstr ""
"Eu sou um lorde do Clã dos Cavalos, e estamos aqui por conta de assuntos de "
"Wesnoth. Você faria bem em não nos incomodar."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2532
msgid ""
"Wesnoth business, huh. ...you’re not the first group of deserters I’ve "
"caught fleeing the undead."
msgstr ""
"Negócios de Wesnoh, huh. ...vocês não são o primeiro grupo de desertores que "
"eu encontrei fugindo dos mortos-vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2536
msgid ""
"I’ll tell you what. I’m a fair orc, I won’t take advantage of your "
"situation. Maybe I can help you. Let’s make a deal."
msgstr ""
"Vamos fazer o seguinte. Eu sou um orc justo, eu não vou me aproveitar da sua "
"situação. Talvez eu consiga ajudar você. Vamos fazer um trato."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2540
msgid ""
"Those necromancers down south are paying me good coin to keep them supplied "
"with corpses. Hand over, let’s say, eight of your soldiers as tribute, and "
"you’re free to go about your business. I’ll even give you a cut of the "
"profit!"
msgstr ""
"Esses necromantes no sul estão me pagando uma boa quantia de ouro para que "
"eles fiquem abastecidos com corpos. Entregue, vamos ver, oito de seus "
"soldados como tributo, e você estará livre para fazer o que quiser. Eu até "
"lhe darei um parte dos lucros!"

# Empalhe = Taxidermia
# Empale = Vlad
#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2544
msgid ""
"Today I have been called shortsighted, then a coward, and now a deserter?! "
"My honor will stand no more insult! Begone, fetid orc, lest I mount your "
"head on a pike! I don’t fear the dead and I don’t fear you."
msgstr ""
"Hoje eu fui chamado de moralista, depois de covarde, e agora de desertor?! "
"Minha honra não será mais insultada! Vá embora, orc fétido, antes que eu "
"empale sua cabeça em uma estaca! Eu não temo os mortos e eu não temo você."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. This is the start of the second night, and around 4 orcs will enter the map this turn, and 3 more next turn.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2549
msgid "(grinning) I was hoping you’d say that!"
msgstr "(sorrindo) Eu esperava que você fosse dizer isso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. this is a reminder to the player that Owaec is a leader and can recruit.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2566
msgid ""
"Gweddry may command the whole of our party, but do not forget that I too can "
"recruit and recall! I will need soldiers to hold the line against these orcs."
msgstr ""
"Gweddry pode comandar todo o nosso grupo, mas não se esqueça que eu também "
"posso recrutar e convocar! Eu precisarei de soldados para segurar o fronte "
"contra estes orcs."

#. [dummy]: id=amla_dummy
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2668
msgid "AMLAs"
msgstr ""

#. [dummy]: id=amla_dummy
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2669
msgid ""
"This veteran fighter has advanced one or more times past his maximum level, "
"gaining increased damage each time."
msgstr ""

#. [message]
#. Medium-sized groups of orcs are arriving every 2 days to attack the player. This is one message they might say when they arrive.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2717
msgid "Time to chop some human heads!"
msgstr "Hora de arrancar umas cabeças humanas!"

#. [message]
#. Medium-sized groups of orcs are arriving every 2 days to attack the player. This is one message they might say when they arrive.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2724
msgid "Keep attacking, hit ’em while the sun’s down!"
msgstr "Continuem atacando, ataquem eles enquanto o sol está baixo!"

#. [message]
#. Medium-sized groups of orcs are arriving every 2 days to attack the player. This is one message they might say when they arrive.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2731
msgid "Chief’s orders, let’s get them!"
msgstr "Ordens do chefe, vamos pegar eles!"

#. [message]
#. Medium-sized groups of orcs are arriving every 2 days to attack the player. This is one message they might say when they arrive.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2738
msgid "Burn and pillage!"
msgstr "Queimem e pilhem!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2767
msgid "Excellent. Now..."
msgstr "Excelente. Agora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. before he picks up the amulet
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2774
msgid ""
"Wait, Dacyn, before you pick that up... are you sure this is the right "
"decision? Even if you can wield it safely, something this evil will "
"doubtlessly corrupt anyone who possesses it."
msgstr ""
"Espere, Dacyn, antes de pegar isso... você tem certeza que está é a decisão "
"correta? Mesmo que você consiga usá-lo com segurança, algo tão maligno sem "
"dúvida irá corromper quem o possuir."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2778
msgid ""
"Why, I’m incredibly touched by your deep show of affection. I’m sure that "
"will be of great comfort when thousands are massacred after Wesnoth loses "
"its greatest war in living memory."
msgstr ""
"Nossa, eu estou muito movido pela sua profunda demonstração de afeto. Tenho "
"certeza que isto será de grande conforto quando milhares forem massacrado "
"após Wesnoth perder sua maior guerra dos últimos tempos."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. there's a short pause between the "deep show of affection" message and this one
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2788
msgid ""
"No, Gweddry, I am not sure. But I know of no other way to defeat Mal-"
"Ravanal. I have tried once before. Even as a mage, Ravan’s powers near "
"outmatched my own. As the lich Mal-Ravanal, perhaps only Delfador the Great "
"could have stood a chance."
msgstr ""
"Não, Gweddry, eu não tenho certeza. Mas eu não conheço nenhum outro meio de "
"derrotar Mal-Ravanal. Eu tentei uma vez antes. Mesmo quando ele era apenas "
"um mago, o poder de Ravan quase superava o meu. Como o lich Mal-Ravanal, "
"talvez apenas Delfador, o Grande, poderia ter uma chance contra ele."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2792
msgid ""
"This Amulet will give us the edge that I need. With it, I can open a gate to "
"the Land of the Dead and pull Mal-Ravanal’s unholy spells out of this world."
msgstr ""
"Este amuleto nos dará a vantagem que eu preciso. Com ele, posso abrir um "
"portal para a Terra dos Mortos e destruir os profanos feitiços de Mal-"
"Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2796
msgid ""
"But if what you said is true, the very same could be said of Ravan. How do "
"you know you will not fall down the same path as well?"
msgstr ""
"Mas, se o que você diz é verdade, o mesmo poderia ser dito de Ravan. Como "
"você sabe que não terá o mesmo fim dele?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2805
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "You are right, Gweddry. I cannot know. But I must try. If I do not, "
#| "Wesnoth — nay, all of Irdya — will surely fall to ruin. As long as I try, "
#| "there is still a chance. Sacrificing myself means nothing for the greater "
#| "good."
msgid ""
"You are right, Gweddry. I cannot know. But I must try. If I do not, Wesnoth "
"— nay, all of Irdya — will surely fall to ruin. As long as I try, there is "
"still a chance. Sacrificing myself is of no consequence if it is for the "
"greater good."
msgstr ""
"Você está certo, Gweddry. Eu não tenho como saber. Mas eu devo tentar. Se "
"não tentar, Wesnoth — não, toda Irdya — com certeza irá cair em ruína. "
"Enquanto eu tentar, ainda há uma chance. Não tenho problema em me sacrificar "
"pelo bem maior."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2809
msgid "(picks up the amulet)"
msgstr "(pega o amuleto)"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. [message]
#. on putting on the amulet, he's been dropped to 1 hp
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2857
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2867
msgid "AAAAHHHH!"
msgstr "AAAAHHHH!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. "everyone" being 6 units, or less
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2872
msgid "Dacyn! Everyone stand back, give him some air."
msgstr "Dacyn! Todo mundo para trás, deem espaço para ele respirar."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2876
msgid ""
"... do not fear, I am unharmed. I just... need a moment to catch my breath."
msgstr ""
"... não tenham medo, eu estou ileso. Eu apenas... preciso de um momento para "
"recuperar o fôlego."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. A wall of the inner sanctum (where the amulet was) has just exploded, revealing a cave that extends off the west edge of the map.
#. Introduction implying that Whitefang has other chiefs, but that Dra-Nak is particularly powerful.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2941
msgid ""
"Hah, did you think you were safe hiding back in here? Nobody can escape from "
"Dra-Nak, greatest chief east of the Listra."
msgstr ""
"Hah, vocês pensaram que estavam seguros se escondendo aqui? Ninguém escapa "
"de Dra-Nak, o maior chefe a leste de Listra."

#. [message]: speaker=Cowardly Goblin
#. male speaker
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2946
msgid ""
"See see! I told you there were humans in here! And I showed you the secret "
"passage! Reward reward?"
msgstr ""
"Viu viu! Eu te disse que tinha humanos aqui! E eu te mostrei a passagem "
"secreta! Recompensa recompensa?"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. gives the Cowardly Goblin some gold
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2951
msgid "Sure, here you go. You did well."
msgstr "Claro, aqui está. Você fez bem."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. presumably still 8 humans, unless the player has lost some
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2962
msgid ""
"As for you humans, you might as well convince your friends outside to "
"surrender. Otherwise, we’ll slaughter you all starting with that injured old "
"man. I gave you a chance to do things fairly before, but now we’re doing "
"things my way."
msgstr ""
"Quanto a vocês humanos, seria mais fácil para todo mundo se vocês "
"convencessem os amigos lá fora a se renderem. Caso contrário, nós iremos "
"matar todos vocês, começando pelo velho ferido. Eu dei uma chance para "
"fazerem as coisas da maneira correta antes, mas agora vamos fazer isso do "
"meu jeito."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2966
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<span size='small'><i>I don’t know what these orcs want with us, but we "
#| "can’t hope to escape with Dacyn so badly hurt.</i></span>"
msgid ""
"I don’t know what these orcs want with us, but we can’t hope to escape with "
"Dacyn so badly hurt."
msgstr ""
"<span size='small'><i>Eu não sei o que esses orcs querem da gente, mas não "
"temos como fugir com o Dacyn nesse estado.</i></span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/10_Dark_Sanctuary.cfg:2970
msgid "Very well, orc, we will surrender."
msgstr "Muito bem, orc, nós nos renderemos."

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:4
msgid "Captured"
msgstr "Capturado"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:15
msgid ""
"After their surrender, Gweddry, Dacyn, and Owaec were promptly taken before "
"the orcish chieftain, Dra-Nak. The rest were thrown into the prisons to "
"await their turn..."
msgstr ""
"Depois de se renderem, Gweddry, Dacyn e Owaec foram prontamente levados "
"perante o chefe orc, Dra-Nak. Os outros foram jogados nas prisões para "
"aguardarem pela sua vez..."

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:94
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:414
msgid "Prisoners"
msgstr "Prisioneiros"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:103
msgid "Bats"
msgstr "Morcegos"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Warlord, id=Varrak-Klar
#. In S11, an orc with so much gold for recruitment that the player can't beat them, acts as a turn limit.
#. In S12, a leader with a high but not unbeatable amount of gold.
#. However, if Chief Dra-Nak survived S11 then S12's Varrak-Klar will be changed to an Orcish Sovereign and renamed to appear to be the Chief pursuing the escapees.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:129
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:70
msgid "Varrak-Klar"
msgstr "Varrak-Klar"

#. [side]: type=Orcish Slurbow, id=Rakkha
#. In S11, an orc with so much gold for recruitment that the player can't beat them, acts as a turn limit.
#. In S12, a leader with a high but not unbeatable amount of gold.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:155
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:183
msgid "Rakkha"
msgstr "Rakkha"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:473
msgid "Boja"
msgstr "Boja"

#. [effect]: type=impact
#. [effect]: type=impact, type=impact
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:633
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:649
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1076
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1090
msgid "unarmed"
msgstr "desarmado"

# É apenas um desertor
#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. Exactly four units are in this jail cell, identified as "role=escapee ..." in the po hints.
#. 3 were in Gweddry's recall list, but escapee sidekick 2 deserted from another Wesnoth commander
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:687
msgid ""
"Several of Gweddry’s men find themselves locked away in a crude orcish cell."
msgstr ""
"Muitos dos homens de Gweddry encontram-se trancafiados em uma rudimentar "
"celas feita por orcs."

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 1
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:692
msgid "We’ve got to get out of here!"
msgstr "Nós temos que sair daqui!"

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 2
#. Speaker is the male deserter, however the other units don't know his backstory yet
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:697
msgid "I’m sure your commanders will come and save us!"
msgstr "Estou certo de que o seus comandantes vão vir salvar vocês!"

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 0
#. Male speaker talking to male deserter, also the huge enemies changed in 1.17 from trolls to orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:702
msgid "What? Didn’t you see those huge orcs drag them away? It’s hopeless!"
msgstr ""
"O quê? Você não viu aqueles gigantescos orcs arrastando eles pra longe? "
"Estamos perdidos!"

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 0
#. Female speaker talking to male deserter, also the huge enemies changed in 1.17 from trolls to orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:704
msgid ""
"female^What? Didn’t you see those huge orcs drag them away? It’s hopeless!"
msgstr ""
"O quê? Você não viu aqueles gigantescos orcs arrastando eles pra longe? "
"Estamos perdidos!"

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:708
msgid "Be quiet, you three! There’s something back here..."
msgstr "Façam silêncio, vocês três! Tem algo aqui atrás..."

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:713
msgid ""
"Look! There’s a gap in the wall over here. I think I can slip through if I "
"clear away some of these rocks..."
msgstr ""
"Vejam! Há um buraco na parede bem aqui. Acho que consigo passar por ele se "
"eu retirar algumas dessas pedras..."

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:741
msgid "Come on! This way!"
msgstr "Vamos! Por aqui!"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:748
msgid "Find Gweddry, Dacyn and Owaec"
msgstr "Encontre Gweddry, Dacyn e Owaec"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#. Initially shown with 4 escapees.
#. Later shown meaning all of the released prisoners. Some can die, just not all.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:753
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1205
msgid "Death of the escapees"
msgstr "Morte dos fugitivos"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. the escapees' cell door
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:772
msgid "The door won’t open from this side."
msgstr "A porta não abre por este lado."

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 1
#. The speaker is male. The deserter, "escapee sidekick 2", will always be male.
#. The other escapees, including the speaker, are 3 random units from the player's recall list.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:792
msgid ""
"$deserter_name, I don’t recognize you, and you look like you’ve been locked "
"up longer than the rest of us. How did you get here?"
msgstr ""
"$deserter_name, eu não reconheço você, e parece que você está aqui há mais "
"tempos do que nós. Como você veio parar aqui?"

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 1
#. The speaker is female. The deserter, "escapee sidekick 2", will always be male.
#. The other escapees, including the speaker, are 3 random units from the player's recall list.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:795
msgid ""
"female^$deserter_name, I don’t recognize you, and you look like you’ve been "
"locked up longer than the rest of us. How did you get here?"
msgstr ""
"$deserter_name, eu não reconheço você, e parece que você está aqui há mais "
"tempos do que nós. Como você veio parar aqui?"

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 2
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:800
msgid ""
"When the undead burned Tath, I got... lost. I have family up north, but I "
"didn’t even get across the ford before some orcs captured me. They marched "
"me and many other slaves east along the river, until we arrived here."
msgstr ""
"Quando os mortos-vivos queimaram Tath, eu fiquei... perdido. Eu tinha "
"família mais para o norte, mas eu nem consegui cruzar o vau antes de alguns "
"orcs me capturarem. Eles me obrigaram a marchar com muitos outros escravos "
"ao longo do rio, até chegarmos aqui."

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#. The speaker is male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:805
msgid "(scowling) A deserter. We should lock you back in your cell."
msgstr ""
"(franzindo a testa) Um desertor. Deveríamos te prender de volta na sua cela."

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#. The speaker is female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:807
msgid "female^(scowling) A deserter. We should lock you back in your cell."
msgstr ""
"(franzindo a testa) Um desertor. Deveríamos te prender de volta na sua cela."

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 2
#. "you" being an audience of three units
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:812
msgid ""
"No, please, you don’t understand! The undead are everywhere! I didn’t want "
"to die like all my friends..."
msgstr ""
"Não, por favor, vocês não entendem! Os mortos-vivos estão em todo lugar! Eu "
"não quero morrer como todos os meus amigos..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:826
msgid "Do you hear something coming from those pits?"
msgstr "Vocês estão ouvido algo vindo daqueles poços?"

#. [message]: race=bats
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:834
msgid "Neep! Neep!"
msgstr "Neep! Neep!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:848
msgid "Ack! Get away from me!"
msgstr "Argh! Saia de perto de mim!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:861
msgid "This tunnel seems to go deeper into the caves. We can’t go that way."
msgstr ""
"Pelo visto esse túnel leva mais para dentro das cavernas. Não podemos ir por "
"esse caminho."

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 0
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:878
msgid ""
"How do we know these caves aren’t all dead ends? We might be stuck wandering "
"until we die of thirst!"
msgstr ""
"Como sabemos que todas essas cavernas não levam a becos sem saída? Podemos "
"ficar vagando por aí até morrermos de sede!"

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:882
msgid "You’re welcome to go back to your cell."
msgstr "Você é bem vindo para voltar à sua cela."

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 2
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:900
msgid ""
"Even if we do find your commanders and escape, maybe we should consider "
"staying in the north? It’s tranquil, and quiet.... and there’s no undead..."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo que encontremos os seus comandantes e escapemos, talvez deveríamos "
"considerar continuar no norte? É tranquilo, quieto... e não tem mortos-"
"vivos..."

#. [message]: role=escapee sidekick 0
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:904
msgid "I didn’t come all this way just to give up at the words of a deserter!"
msgstr ""
"Eu não cheguei até aqui apenas para desistir por causa das palavras de um "
"desertor!"

#. [message]: role=escapee leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:908
msgid ""
"Let’s focus on escaping the orcs before worrying about the future. Now "
"quiet, I smell something foul up ahead."
msgstr ""
"Vamos focar em escapar dos orcs antes de nos preocuparmos com o futuro. "
"Agora, façam silêncio, eu sinto o cheiro de algo horrível a frente."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:926
msgid ""
"Ugh, here’s where that wretched stench is coming from. This must be the "
"orcish storeroom, full of their discarded gear and trash. At least we can "
"find ourselves some proper weapons."
msgstr ""
"Eca, então é daqui que o fedor horrível está saindo. Esse deve ser o "
"depósito dos orcs, cheio de seu equipamento descartado e lixo. Ao menos "
"podemos achar algumas armas de verdade."

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:934
msgid "weapons restored"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:955
msgid ""
"And look, our captured equipment and provisions are here too! I’ve recovered "
"supplies worth $gold_amount_S11 gold."
msgstr ""
"E vejam só, nosso equipamento e provisões capturados também estão aqui! Eu "
"recuperei suprimentos valendo $gold_amount_S11 de ouro."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:989
msgid ""
"The other prison cells should be to the north of that chamber. If we can get "
"past those guards we could set everyone free."
msgstr ""
"As outras celas devem estar ao norte daquela câmara. Se conseguirmos passar "
"por aqueles guardas poderemos libertar todo mundo."

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:998
msgid "But there’s too many of them!"
msgstr "Mas há muitos deles!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1002
msgid "Hmm... I have an idea."
msgstr "Hmm... Eu tenho uma ideia."

#. [message]: id=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1060
msgid "So, how do I look?"
msgstr "Então, como estou?"

#. [message]: id=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1064
msgid "I’ll try to slip past the guards. You wait here."
msgstr "Eu vou tentar passar pelos guardas. Vocês esperem aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. Gweddry, Dacyn and Owaec are being held by guards in front of Dra-Nak's throne
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1111
msgid ""
"You’ve been a difficult prize to capture, but well worth the cost! Human "
"corpses may not sell as well as dwarf or drake tribute, but with this many "
"of you, I’ll still fetch a hefty bounty."
msgstr ""
"Vocês tem sido um prêmio difícil de capturar, mas valeram o esforço! Corpos "
"humanos podem não vender tão bem quanto os de anões ou tributo dos "
"draconatos, mas vocês são tão numerosos que conseguirei uma recompensa "
"considerável."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. The nearest guards are orcs, but there are drakes guarding the edge of the room.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1116
msgid ""
"Drakes, surely you can see that this orc does not have your best interests "
"at heart? He is bleeding your numbers to fund his empire while your leader "
"stands by and does nothing!"
msgstr ""
"Draconatos, vocês certamente percebem que esse orc não está do seu lado? Ele "
"está dizimando os seus números para financiar o próprio império enquanto o "
"seu líder não faz nada sobre isso!"

#. [message]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1120
msgid ""
"I follow the Ways of our Flight.\n"
"Mortic is Aspirant.\n"
"I serve his will."
msgstr ""
"Eu sigo os Preceitos da nossa Revoada.\n"
"Mortic é um Aspirante.\n"
"Eu sirvo à sua vontade."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1148
msgid ""
"You Wesnothians still don’t get it? These weaklings <i>need</i> me! Before I "
"came, this place was a wasteland, with drake, dwarf, and naga fighting over "
"scraps and bleeding in the snow."
msgstr ""
"Vocês Wesnothianos ainda não entenderam? Estes fracotes <i>precisam</i> de "
"mim! Antes de eu vir para cá, esse lugar era uma imensidão devastada, com "
"draconatos, anões e nagas lutando por migalhas e sangrando na neve."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1152
msgid ""
"I united them all under my banner, bringing <i>peace</i> and <i>order</i> to "
"these mountains! And once I sell you off, we will have enough money and "
"power to rival even the great tribes of the north. I will usher in a new "
"golden age for my people!"
msgstr ""
"Eu reuni todos eles sob meu estandarte, trazendo <i>paz</i> e <i>ordem</i> "
"para estas montanhas! E quando eu vender você, nós teremos dinheiro e poder "
"o suficiente para rivalizar até as maiores tribos do norte. Eu começarei uma "
"nova era de ouro para o meu povo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1156
msgid ""
"You murder your allies and call it peace? Bah, this place will only know "
"peace once you are dead!"
msgstr ""
"Você mata seus aliados e chama isto de paz? Bah, este lugar só conhecerá a "
"paz quando você estiver morto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. Owaec has attacked the orc
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1185
msgid ""
"Hah, that almost hurt! I’m gonna enjoy shipping you lot down south. Maybe "
"this time, the necromancers will let me watch..."
msgstr ""
"Ha, essa quase doeu! Eu vou adorar levá-lo para o sul. Talvez desta vez os "
"necromantes me deixem assistir..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. speaker is the escapee wearing the orc disguise, there are around 10 guards
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1192
msgid ""
"Opening the cells should confuse the guards for a moment. But I better not "
"get too close to them..."
msgstr ""
"Abrir as celas deve confundir os guardas por algum tempo. Mas é melhor eu "
"não me aproximar muito deles..."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#. At least one cell is still locked. There's one with 8 Wesnothians, one with 6 Wesnothians,
#. and one containing 4 Wesnothians plus 2 Drakes.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1200
msgid "Release the other prisoners"
msgstr "Liberte os outros prisioneiros"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. while the speaker is still in disguise
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1277
msgid ""
"Here’s one of the prison cells! As soon as I open this, all hell is going to "
"break loose."
msgstr "Aqui está uma das celas! Assim que eu abri-la, teremos problemas."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1294
msgid ""
"I’m already well-equipped, but we’ll have to pay upkeep to arm and armor "
"each prisoner I free. I hope we’ll have enough gold left over for the next "
"battle!"
msgstr ""
"Eu já estou bem equipado, mas teremos custo de manutenção para armar e "
"equipar cada prisioneiro que eu libertar. Espero que nos reste ouro o "
"suficiente para a próxima batalha!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. prompt to the player
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1328
msgid "Open the cell?"
msgstr "Abrir a cela?"

#. [option]
#. choice when prompted "open the cell?"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1331
msgid "Yes! <i>(freed units will incur upkeep)</i>"
msgstr "Sim! <i>(unidades libertas estarão sujeitas a custo de manutenção)</i>"

#. [option]
#. choice when prompted "open the cell?"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1362
msgid "Not yet..."
msgstr "Ainda não..."

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1369
msgid "Huzzah, we’re free at last!"
msgstr "Viva, finalmente estamos livres!"

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1370
msgid "Hooray, we’re rescued!"
msgstr "Hoarrr, fomos resgatados!"

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1371
msgid "Yes! Get us out of here!"
msgstr "Sim! Nos tire daqui!"

#. [message]: speaker=Ga'all
#. Ga'all and Verash are drakes from S10
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1376
msgid ""
"I am free!\n"
"Never again shall I be prisoner!"
msgstr ""
"Estou livre!\n"
"Nunca mais serei prisioneiro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Verash
#. Ga'all and Verash are drakes from S10, this is followed by Verash killing Ga'all
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1382
msgid ""
"You disobey the Aspirant.\n"
"For your treachery,\n"
"Your punishment is death."
msgstr ""
"Você desobedece o Aspirante.\n"
"Por sua traição,\n"
"Sua punição é a morte."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1449
msgid "The guards are distracted! Let us make our daring escape!"
msgstr "Os guardas estão distraídos! Vamos fazer nossa fuga audaz!"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1454
msgid "Move Gweddry, Dacyn, or Owaec to the south-west exit"
msgstr "Mova Gweddry, Dacyn ou Owaec até a saída ao sudoeste"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1458
msgid "Release the remaining prisoners"
msgstr "Liberte os prisioneiros restantes"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1476
msgid "Save as much gold as possible for the next scenario!"
msgstr "Guarde o máximo de ouro possível para o próximo cenário!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. shouted to the two leaders who are positioned outside the orcs' caves, happens 2 turns after the main escape starts
#. combined with removing shroud to reveal that those two leaders recruited last turn (and have full castles on normal or hard)
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1526
msgid "The prisoners are escaping! Get in here and stop them!"
msgstr "Os prisioneiros estão escapando! Venham pra cá e parem eles!"

#. [message]: speaker=Rakkha
#. orc leader who was guarding against external threats sends troops into the orcs' throneroom
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1541
msgid "Protect the Chief!"
msgstr "Protejam o Chefe!"

#. [message]: speaker=Varrak-Klar
#. orc leader who was guarding against external threats sends troops into the orcs' throneroom
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1546
msgid "Into the caves!"
msgstr "Para as cavernas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1556
msgid ""
"Guess we’re on the run again! My mercenary boys back home woulda made short "
"work o’ these Whitefang punks... I sure am missin’ the Estmarks right about "
"now."
msgstr ""
"Parece que é hora de fugir de novo! Meus velhos mercenários dariam um jeito "
"nesses Presas-brancas rapidinho... Estou sentindo muita falta das Marcas "
"Orientais agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1563
msgid "Everyone hurry, we have to get out of here!"
msgstr "Apressem-se, precisamos sair daqui!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. 3 turns after the main escape starts
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1586
msgid ""
"Such carnage in this dark confined cave... how I long to once again gaze "
"upon the rolling plains of my homeland. These lands are cold, but the "
"thought of my fellow Clansmen is as a fire burning in my breast."
msgstr ""
"Mas que carnificina nesta caverna escura e confinada... como anseio ver "
"novamente as vastas planícies de minha terra natal. Estas terras são frias, "
"mas o pensamento nos meus companheiros de Clã é como um fogo ardente em meu "
"peito."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. "there" being the Horse Clans' plains
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1591
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Wesnoth’s best horses and much of Weldyn’s food is come from there. I’m "
#| "sure it’s well-defended, despite never having visited there myself."
msgid ""
"Wesnoth’s best horses and much of Weldyn’s food comes from there. I’m sure "
"it’s well-defended, despite never having visited there myself."
msgstr ""
"Os melhores cavalos de Wesnoth assim como também muita da comida de Weldyn "
"vêm de lá. Eu tenho certeza que lá é bem defendido, apesar de nunca ter "
"estado lá pessoalmente."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. "them" being the Horse Clans' plains
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1596
msgid ""
"There is naught that I can speak that would truly do them justice! You will "
"have to see the plains yourself to appreciate their majesty."
msgstr ""
"Não há nada que eu poderia dizer que faria justiça a eles! Você terá que ver "
"as planícies por si mesmo para apreciar sua majestade."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. "their" being the Horse Clans' plains
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1601
msgid "Then let us return quickly to Wesnoth to aid in their defense!"
msgstr ""
"Então deixe-nos retornar rapidamente a Wesnoth para ajudar na sua defesa!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. Boja is the name of the cave bear
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1616
msgid "Hey, who are you? Boja, sic ’em!"
msgstr "Ei, quem é você? Boja, pegu' eles!"

#. [message]: speaker=$unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1620
msgid "Uh oh!"
msgstr "Uh oh!"

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1678
msgid "70 gold"
msgstr "70 de ouro"

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1678
msgid "You’ve pillaged 70 orcish gold pieces!"
msgstr "Você saqueou 70 peças de ouro dos orcs!"

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1679
msgid "115 gold"
msgstr "115 de ouro"

#. [scenario]: id=11_Captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1679
msgid "You’ve pillaged 115 orcish gold pieces!"
msgstr "Você saqueou 115 peças de ouro dos orcs!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. goblin with a ring of invisibility
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1700
msgid "Oooh so shiny, my precious... what a great gift from the Chief..."
msgstr ""
"Oooh tão brilhante, meu precioso...que maravilhoso presente do Chefe..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. goblin with a ring of invisibility (although not enough sense to wear it when running away)
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1705
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Aaah! Humans! Run away run away!"
msgid "Aaah! Who’re you?! Run away run away!"
msgstr "Aaah! Humanos! Fujam, fujam!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. unit who discovered the goblin with a ring of invisibility
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1712
msgid "Hmm, looks like he dropped something."
msgstr "Hum, parece que ele deixou cair algo."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1730
msgid ""
"This looks like a disused mineshaft. I don’t feel any fresh air, so we "
"shouldn’t expect to escape this way."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. if the disguised unit runs out of the caves alone, without rescuing any other prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1752
msgid "Phew! I made it."
msgstr "Ufa! Consegui."

#. [message]
#. if the disguised unit runs out of the caves alone, without rescuing any other prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1762
msgid "Where are you going?! Come back!"
msgstr "Onde você vai?! Volte aqui!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. One of the main heroes gets outside, triggering the victory condition
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1780
msgid "I’ve reached the exit! We’ll have to make a run for it!"
msgstr "Cheguei na saída! Vamos ter que correr!"

#. [message]
#. The player didn’t open all the cells before moving a hero to the exit and triggering the victory event
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1785
msgid "Wait, you can’t leave us behind!"
msgstr "Espere, você não pode nos deixar para trás!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. immediate response to Boja's death
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1811
msgid "You killed my bear, you filthy humans! You’ll pay for that!"
msgstr "Vocês mataram meu urso, seus humanos imundos! Vocês pagarão por isso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. [message]: speaker=Varrak-Klar
#. last breath event for Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1848
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:969
msgid ""
"Curse you all! Why couldn’t you have just died as tribute like everyone "
"else? Now my glorious golden Empire will never be..."
msgstr ""
"Malditos sejam, todos vocês! Porque vocês não podiam morrer como tributo "
"assim como todos os outros? Agora meu glorioso Império dourado nunca "
"existirá..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. die event for Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/11_Captured.cfg:1869
msgid "Look, he was carrying the key to their treasury!"
msgstr "Olhe só, ele estava carregando a chave para o tesouro deles!"

#. [scenario]: id=12_Evacuation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:33
msgid "Evacuation"
msgstr "Evacuação"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:45
msgid ""
"Gweddry and his men escaped from the orcish prisons and fled westward as "
"swiftly as they could, closely pursued by the orcs and their drake vassals."
msgstr ""
"Gweddry e seus homens escaparam das prisões dos orcs e fugiram para oeste o "
"mais rápido que puderam, sendo perseguidos de perto pelos orcs e seus "
"vassalos draconatos."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:274
msgid "Move Owaec to the end of the bridge"
msgstr "Mova Owaec para o fim da ponte"

#. [objectives]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:277
msgid "Defeat all enemy leaders"
msgstr "Derrote todos os líderes inimigos"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:294
msgid ""
"<b>Every unit east of the bridge when it is destroyed will be lost "
"(including non-recalled units)</b>"
msgstr ""
"<b>Todas as unidades ao leste da ponte quando ela for destruída serão "
"perdidas (incluindo unidades que não foram convocadas)</b>"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:303
msgid ""
"Dacyn, are you feeling better? We must keep moving! The orcs have almost "
"caught up to us."
msgstr ""
"Dacyn, você está se sentindo melhor? Nós precisamos continuar em frente! Os "
"orcs estão quase nos alcançando."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:307
msgid "(cough) (cough) Yes, yes, I’m perfectly fine... (cough)"
msgstr "(tosse) (tosse) Sim, sim, estou perfeitamente bem... (tosse)"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:311
msgid ""
"Such decrepitude is one ten-thousandth of what you deserve for wielding that "
"evil amulet! But lo, a bridge in the distance! Hope is not yet lost."
msgstr ""
"Tamanha decrepitude é apenas um milésimo do que você merece por empunhar "
"este amuleto maligno! Mas olhem, uma ponte ao longe! A esperança ainda não "
"está perdida."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:315
msgid ""
"We must get across quickly before we are cut off and overwhelmed. But the "
"men are exhausted! We cannot keep running for much longer."
msgstr ""
"Nós temos que cruzar rapidamente antes de sermos cercados e destruídos. Mas "
"os homens estão exaustos! Nós não podemos continuar correndo muito mais "
"tempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:319
msgid "(nodding) Gruuhhh... Grug tired. Leg hurt..."
msgstr "(acenando) Gruuhhh... Grug cansado. Perna dói..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#. "Yeah, don't forget! My legs aren't as long as you humans'!"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:324
msgid "Aye, dinnae forget, my legs ain’t as long as ye human-folks’!"
msgstr ""
"É, non esqueçam! As miñas pernas non son tan longas coma as de vocês, "
"humanos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:328
msgid ""
"Tell the men they need not fear! I will cross last and destroy the bridge "
"behind us so that the orcs cannot follow!"
msgstr ""
"Diga aos homens que eles não precisam temer! Eu atravessarei por último e "
"destruirei a ponte atrás de nós para que os orcs não possam seguir!"

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:333
msgid ""
"Well I intend to cross first! Gold’s no good if I die before I can spend it! "
"I’m not about to sacrifice myself to save you bunch of barbarians."
msgstr ""
"Bem, eu pretendo atravessar primeiro! Ouro não é bom se eu morrer antes de "
"gastá-lo! Não vou me sacrificar para salvar vocês, bando de bárbaros."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:337
msgid ""
"Everyone, get moving! Anyone left behind on this side of the bridge will "
"surely be killed!"
msgstr ""
"Todo mundo, andando! Qualquer um que ficar deste lado da ponte certamente "
"morrerá!"

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:341
msgid "I’m gettin’ too old for this life..."
msgstr "Eu estou ficando velho demais para essa vida..."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:346
msgid ""
"All units <b>(including non-recalled units!)</b> left behind will be lost."
msgstr ""
"Todas as unidades <b>(incluindo as não convocadas!)</b> deixadas para trás "
"serão perdidas."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:363
msgid ""
"It is unfortunate (cough) that we have not saved any gold to recruit or "
"recall. Escape for our soldiers is impossible, yet if us few rush "
"immediately across the bridge we may be able to (cough)(cough) reach the far "
"shore before the orcs can attack."
msgstr ""
"É um infortúnio (tosse) que nós não salvamos ouro o suficiente para recrutar "
"ou convocar. A fuga para os nossos soldados é impossível, mas se corrermos "
"imediatamente pela ponte devemos ser capazes de (tosse)(tosse) chegar na "
"margem oposta antes que os orcs ataquem."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:373
msgid ""
"It is unfortunate (cough) that we have saved little gold to recruit or "
"recall. Escape for everyone is likely impossible, yet if the 3 of us rush "
"immediately across the bridge we may be able to (cough)(cough) reach the far "
"shore before the orcs can attack."
msgstr ""
"É um infortúnio (tosse) que nós salvamos pouco ouro para recrutar ou "
"convocar. A fuga para todos os nossos soldados será impossível, mas se nós "
"três corrermos imediatamente pela ponte devemos ser capazes de (tosse)"
"(tosse) chegar na margem oposta antes que os orcs ataquem."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:383
msgid ""
"We have enough gold to put up a fight, but the orcs are numerous (cough) and "
"strong. Escape for everyone is likely impossible, yet if the 3 of us rush "
"immediately across the bridge we may be able to (cough)(cough) reach the far "
"shore before the orcs can attack."
msgstr ""
"Temos ouro o suficiente para lutar, mas os orcs são numerosos (tosse) e "
"fortes. A fuga para todos é provavelmente impossível, mas se nós 3 corrermos "
"imediatamente pela ponte devemos ser capazes de (tosse)(tosse) chegar na "
"margem oposta antes que os orcs ataquem."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:390
msgid ""
"We have gold for many soldiers, but the bridge (cough) is long and narrow. "
"Escape for everyone is likely impossible, yet if the 3 of us rush "
"immediately across the bridge we may be able to (cough)(cough) reach the far "
"shore before the orcs can attack."
msgstr ""
"Nós temos ouro para muito soldados, mas a ponte (tosse) é longa e estreita. "
"Seria quase impossível fugir com todo mundo, mas se apenas nós 3 corrermos "
"imediatamente pela ponte devemos ser capazes de (tosse)(tosse) chegar na "
"margem oposta antes que os orcs ataquem."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. Although Dacyn is a Mage of Light, he currently doesn't have a halo.
#. In the unlikely case that he was still L2 when he picked up the amulet, he's automatically advanced at that point in S10.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:402
msgid ""
"Small wonder your Light has abandoned you, if you would leave our companions "
"to the mercy of the orcs! We should all cross together and leave none behind!"
msgstr ""
"Não me admira que sua Luz o abandonou, se você deixaria nossos companheiros "
"à mercê dos orcs! Nós devemos cruzar todos juntos e não deixar ninguém para "
"trás!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. After this message the halo flickers and then stays on.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:407
msgid "(cough) My light? ...oh, oh yes, yes of course. Just one moment."
msgstr "(tosse) Minha luz? ...ah, ah sim, mas é claro. Só um momento."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#. He drinks an elixir between this message and the next one
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:459
msgid ""
"Trapped among barbarians and pursued by orcs... how in the sands did I get "
"here? Time to break out something I’ve been saving for a rainy day..."
msgstr ""
"Preso entre bárbaros e perseguido por orcs... pelas areias, como eu fui "
"parar aqui? Hora de beber algo que estava guardando para uma emergência..."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#. He drank an elixir between the last message and this one
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:472
msgid "Nothing like some extra speed to help me get away!"
msgstr "Nada como velocidade extra para me ajudar a escapar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. Addressed to Gweddry, but many of the heroes except Dacyn are together in this conversation, assuming the player managed to collect them.
#. It has to still make sense with only Gweddry and Owaec talking to each other.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:482
msgid ""
"Gweddry, you saw how Dacyn struggled to channel his Light. What do you think "
"of this?"
msgstr ""
"Gweddry, você viu como Dacyn lutou para canalizar sua Luz. O que você pensa "
"disso?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:486
msgid "Aye, and have ye noticed the man’s cough? He be trying to hide it."
msgstr "Si, e notaches a tosse do home? Esteve tentando esconde-la."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:490
msgid ""
"... it is a bad sign, to be sure. But Dacyn is determined to protect Wesnoth "
"and destroy Mal-Ravanal, and I believe he is our only chance at doing so."
msgstr ""
"... não é um bom sinal, com certeza. Mas Dacyn está determinado a proteger "
"Wesnoth e destruir Mal-Ravanal, e eu acredito que ele é nossa única "
"esperança."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:494
msgid "Magic man kind! Be good magic man be."
msgstr "Homem mágico gentil! Seja bom homem mágico."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:498
msgid ""
"I agree his intentions are good, but with each passing hour, that foul "
"amulet’s darkness festers within him. What influence may it have?"
msgstr ""
"Eu concordo que suas intenções são boas, mas a cada hora que passa, a "
"escuridão daquele amuleto sombrio se alastra por ele. Que influência isso "
"pode ter?"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:502
msgid ""
"I choose to place my faith in the holy Light, not the darkness! We will "
"overcome Mal-Ravanal’s evil, and this dark amulet’s as well."
msgstr ""
"Eu escolho botar minha fé na Luz sagrada, não nas trevas! Nós iremos "
"derrotar o mal de Mal-Ravanal, e também esse amuleto sombrio."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#. Last message in the "Gweddry, you saw how Dacyn struggled to channel his Light" conversation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:507
msgid ""
"Bah, magic! There’s a reason the civilized people of my world eschew magic — "
"we would never have to deal with problems like this back in my homeland."
msgstr ""
"Bah, magia! Existe uma razão porque que as pessoas civilizadas do meu mundo "
"rejeitam magia — nós nunca teríamos que lidar com problemas como esse em "
"minha terra natal."

#. [message]: race=orc
#. Speaker might be any of Chief Dra-Nak, Varrak-Klar or Rakkha; all three are male orcs.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:531
msgid ""
"(squinting) I can’t see anything in this searing sunlight. Fall back, wait "
"for dusk!"
msgstr ""
"(franzindo os olhos) Eu não consigo ver nada nesta escaldante luz solar. "
"Recuem, esperem o anoitecer!"

# Levemente alterado por não ter uma tradução boa para "Daytime"
#. [message]: id=Mortic
#. to the male orc leader who's ordering the retreat
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:536
msgid ""
"The sun strengthens my kin.\n"
"Daytime is our Domain.\n"
"We should press the attack."
msgstr ""
"O sol fortalece a minha raça.\n"
"O Dia é o nosso Domínio.\n"
"Nós deveríamos pressionar o ataque."

#. [message]: race=orc
#. The messages in this event give the player a chance to react to the retreat.
#. By now they should know that enemies retreat during the day, but it's especially important to know now so they can evacuate.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:545
msgid "You heard me, wyrm! Wait. For. Dusk."
msgstr "Você me ouviu, wyrm! Espere. O. Anoitecer."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:586
msgid "Is everyone across? I’m ready to chop down the bridge."
msgstr "Todo mundo atravessou? Estou pronto para derrubar a ponte."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:590
msgid "Hmm..."
msgstr "Hmm..."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:592
msgid "Yes, destroy the bridge."
msgstr "Sim, destrua a ponte."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. Owaec has just destroyed the bridge
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:626
msgid ""
"Owaec, you fool! I am trapped on the east bank! Without my help Wesnoth will "
"surely fall to Mal-Ravanal..."
msgstr ""
"Owaec, seu tolo! Eu estou preso na margem leste! Sem minha ajuda, Wesnoth "
"certamente será destruída por Mal-Ravanal..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. Owaec has just destroyed the bridge
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:640
msgid ""
"Owaec, you fool! Gweddry is trapped on the east bank! Without his help "
"Wesnoth will surely fall to Mal-Ravanal..."
msgstr ""
"Owaec, seu tolo! Gweddry está preso na margem leste! Sem a ajuda dele, "
"Wesnoth certamente será destruída por Mal-Ravanal..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. Several high-level units were left unrecalled. For a brief cutscene, 10 unrecalled units (high levels preferred) appear on the starting castle.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:688
msgid ""
"Alas, what have I done? So many brave soldiers of Wesnoth, left behind in "
"the wildlands..."
msgstr ""
"Essa não, o que eu fiz? Tantos bravos soldados de Wesnoth, deixados para "
"trás nessas terras selvagens..."

#. [message]
#. Said by any left-behind unit except ogres (they can't speak fluently) and Hahid al-Ali (it would be very out of character for him).
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:702
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "At least you three commanders are safe. From here, we must ride swift, "
#| "ride strong, and ride to save all of Wesnoth!"
msgid ""
"At least you three commanders are safe. From here, you must ride swift, ride "
"strong, and ride to save all of Wesnoth!"
msgstr ""
"Ao menos vocês três comandantes estão a salvo. A partir daqui, vocês devem "
"correr para salvar toda Wesnoth!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. either got everyone across or left behind at most one L2 or L3 unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:710
msgid ""
"Huzzah, we have escaped the northerners! A true Clansman would never "
"willingly leave his companions behind, and so have we clutched victory from "
"the jaws of defeat!"
msgstr ""
"Viva, nós escapamos dos nortistas! Um verdadeiro homem do Clã jamais "
"voluntariamente deixaria seus companheiros para trás, e assim nós arrancamos "
"a vitória das garras da derrota!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:727
msgid ""
"Yes, yes, (cough)(cough) that’s all well and good. With the bridge "
"destroyed, the orcs cannot (cough) cross, but what of the drakes?"
msgstr ""
"Sim, sim, (tosse)(tosse) isso é ótimo. Com a ponte destruída, os orcs não "
"conseguem (tosse) atravessar, mas e quanto aos draconatos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:734
msgid ""
"(cough) And with the drakes defeated, (cough)(cough) no enemies will be able "
"to pursue us. Now, it is finally time for us to once again travel toward "
"Weldyn."
msgstr ""
"(tosse) E com os draconatos derrotados, (tosse)(tosse) nenhum inimigo será "
"capaz de nos perseguir. Agora, finalmente é chegada a hora de nós mais uma "
"vez viajarmos para Weldyn."

#. [message]: race=orc
#. Spoken to Mortic, but at this point it's possible that all the orc leaders are dead, in which case it doesn't get said.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:752
msgid ""
"Useless pathetic ugly weakling wyrms! Fly across and chase after them, or "
"we’ll sell you <i>all</i> to the necromancers!"
msgstr ""
"Inúteis, patéticos, feios, fracos wyrms! Voem e persigam eles, ou nós "
"venderemos <i>todos</i> vocês aos necromantes!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#. to his fellow drakes, and any surviving orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:760
msgid ""
"Dra-Nak is dead,\n"
"His armies weakened,\n"
"His prey fled."
msgstr ""
"Dra-Nak está morto,\n"
"Seu exército enfraquecido,\n"
"Sua presa fugiu."

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#. to his fellow drakes, and any surviving orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:770
msgid ""
"Dra-Nak is feeble,\n"
"His armies weakened,\n"
"His prey fled."
msgstr ""
"Dra-Nak está fraco,\n"
"Seu exército enfraquecido,\n"
"Sua presa fugiu."

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#. to his fellow drakes, and any surviving orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:779
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Long has our Honor been stained.\n"
#| "No longer shall it be.\n"
#| "Now we reclaim our Aerie,\n"
#| "And the strength of our Flight."
msgid ""
"Long has our Honor been stained.\n"
"No longer shall it be.\n"
"Now we reclaim our Eyrie,\n"
"And the strength of our Flight."
msgstr ""
"Por muito tempo nossa Honra esteve manchada.\n"
"Não mais ela ficará.\n"
"Agora nós reclamamos nosso Ninho,\n"
"E a força de nossa Revoada."

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#. Speaker is an orc, and Mortic is flying towards them. "What? Hey!" *gets killed by Mortic*
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:805
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Wha- hey!"
msgid "Wha— hey!"
msgstr "O qu- ei!"

# Voo de Mortic fica estranho
#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:824
msgid ""
"The Hunt is called!\n"
"The orcs our prey!\n"
"Flight of Mortic, we fight!"
msgstr ""
"A Caçada começou!\n"
"Os orcs são nossa presa!\n"
"Revoada de Mortic, lutaremos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:861
msgid ""
"Hurry! If we cannot secure a position on the west bank, the drakes will "
"surely fly behind and cut off our retreat!"
msgstr ""
"Rápido! Se nós não conseguirmos assegurar uma posição na margem oeste, os "
"draconatos certamente voarão por trás de nós e cortarão nossa retirada!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:868
msgid ""
"The sun arises.\n"
"Second and third Wings,\n"
"Capture the west bank."
msgstr ""
"O sol surge.\n"
"Segunda e terceira Asas,\n"
"Capturem a margem oeste."

#. [message]
#. spoken by the leader of either orc side. Lots of drakes appear immediately after this.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:884
msgid ""
"We need help over here! Where are the rest of those lousy drakes? They "
"should be in position by now!"
msgstr ""
"Nós precisamos de ajuda aqui! Onde está o resto destes nojentos draconatos? "
"Eles já deveriam estar em suas posições!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:912
msgid "Gel’ka"
msgstr "Gel’ka"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:917
msgid "We have not crossed the bridge in time. Now we will all be killed!"
msgstr "Não cruzamos a ponte a tempo. Agora seremos todos mortos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:928
msgid ""
"I can hardly believe it! We didn’t need to destroy the bridge after all."
msgstr ""
"Eu mal posso acreditar! No final das contas nem precisamos destruir a ponte."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:932
msgid ""
"Huzzah, a glorious victory in the name of the Clans! Man will never flee "
"from orc and drake; we have taught these northerners not to trifle with "
"Wesnoth!"
msgstr ""
"Viva! Uma vitória gloriosa no em nome dos Clãs! Os Homens jamais fugirão de "
"orcs ou draconatos; nós ensinamos a esses nortistas a não mexer com Wesnoth!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:936
msgid ""
"(cough)(cough) Yes, yes, very well, well done. (cough) Now, it is finally "
"time for us to see what has become of Wesnoth in our absence."
msgstr ""
"(tosse)(tosse) Sim, sim, muito bem, bem feito. (tosse) Agora, é finalmente "
"chegada a hora de descobrirmos o que aconteceu em Wesnoth durante nossa "
"ausência."

#. [message]: speaker=Varrak-Klar
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:963
msgid "Graahh! Stupid humans..."
msgstr "Gaargh! Humanos estúpidos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#. Aspirant is a drake military rank
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:985
msgid "I am Aspirant no more."
msgstr "Não sou mais um aspirante."

#. [message]: speaker=Rakkha
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/12_Evacuation.cfg:998
msgid "I hate you! Hate... hate... hate you..."
msgstr "Eu te odeio! Odeio... odeio... odeio você..."

#. [scenario]: id=13_Spoils_of_War
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:8
msgid "Spoils of War"
msgstr "Espólios de Guerra"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:27
msgid "Part III: Wesnoth at War"
msgstr ""

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:40
msgid ""
"As Gweddry, Owaec, and Dacyn fled across the Listra, a frenzy of shouts, "
"screams, and roars broke out from behind. Neither the orcs nor the drakes "
"attempted to give pursuit."
msgstr ""
"Enquanto Gweddry, Owaec, e Dacyn fugiam através de Listra, um frenesi de "
"gritos, urros e rugidos irrompeu atrás deles. Nem os orcs nem os draconatos "
"tentaram persegui-los."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:45
msgid ""
"Leaving the tumultuous wildlands far behind, the soldiers of Wesnoth "
"prepared to cross the Great River once more and return to their homeland..."
msgstr ""
"Deixando as tumultuosas terras do norte muito para trás, os soldados de "
"Wesnoth se prepararam para cruzar o Grande Rio mais uma vez e retornar para "
"sua terra natal..."

#. [side]: type=Death Knight, id=Ducatithil
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:254
msgid "Ducatithil"
msgstr "Ducatithil"

#. [side]: type=Necromancer, id=Mal-Yrna, gender=female
#. female necromancer, will be renamed to Mal-Mana if Mal-Mana wasn't killed in a previous scenario
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:280
msgid "Mal-Yrna"
msgstr "Mal-Yrna"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:442
msgid "Vaenyc"
msgstr "Vaenyc"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:454
msgid "Vovan"
msgstr "Vovan"

# Seria bom achar um arcaísmo para carcereiro, pois o original em Inglês é um arcaísmo
#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:466
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:843
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:916
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:998
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1080
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1247
msgid "Gaoler"
msgstr "Carcereiro"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:479
msgid "Rescue as many prisoners as possible (6 groups arrive soon)"
msgstr ""
"Resgate tantos prisioneiros quanto possível (6 grupos chegarão em breve)"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:486
msgid "Rescue as many prisoners as possible (5 groups arrive soon)"
msgstr ""
"Resgate tantos prisioneiros quanto possível (5 grupos chegarão em breve)"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:493
msgid "Rescue as many prisoners as possible (4 groups arrive soon)"
msgstr ""
"Resgate tantos prisioneiros quanto possível (4 grupos chegarão em breve)"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:500
msgid "Rescue as many prisoners as possible (3 groups arrive soon)"
msgstr ""
"Resgate tantos prisioneiros quanto possível (3 grupos chegarão em breve)"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:507
msgid "Rescue as many prisoners as possible (2 groups arrive soon)"
msgstr ""
"Resgate tantos prisioneiros quanto possível (2 grupos chegarão em breve)"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:514
msgid "Rescue as many prisoners as possible (1 group arrives soon)"
msgstr "Resgate tantos prisioneiros quanto possível (1 grupo chegará em breve)"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#. Mal-Yrna, a female necromancer
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:522
msgid "Defeat the southern necromancer"
msgstr "Derrote a necromante ao sul"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:526
msgid "Death of Owaec"
msgstr "Morte de Owaec"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:535
msgid "Death of Terraent"
msgstr "Morte de Terraent"

#. [note]
#. two prisoners and one jailer per gang
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:551
msgid "Prisoner gangs will alternate arriving on north and south paths."
msgstr ""
"Grupos de prisioneiros chegarão alternadamente pelos caminhos norte e sul."

#. [note]
#. "enemy" in this case meaning "player's unit"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:555
msgid "Bats prefer to fly towards the nearest enemy."
msgstr "Morcegos preferem voar em direção ao inimigo mais próximo."

#. [message]: id=Owaec,Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:594
msgid ""
"Alas, my long days of riding have been for naught. I could not catch the "
"undead scout before it could report back to its mistress!"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: id=Owaec,Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:598
msgid ""
"Gweddry had hoped we might take this necromancer by surprise. But now that "
"she is alerted, and with the rest of our army yet weeks away, she will have "
"more than enough time to prepare for our arrival."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. speaking to a bat
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:608
msgid ""
"Minion, what’s this? Soldiers of Wesnoth approach from the north? That area "
"should have been cleansed over a month ago."
msgstr ""
"Servo, o que é isso? Soldados de Wesnoth se aproximando pelo norte? Esta "
"área deveria ter sido limpa a mais de um mês."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:612
msgid ""
"No matter. Bring in the next batch of prisoners. I have need of them a "
"little sooner than expected."
msgstr ""
"Não importa. Tragam o próximo grupo de prisioneiros. Preciso deles um pouco "
"mais cedo que o esperado."

#. [message]: speaker=Vovan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:620
msgid "Wait a moment, can we talk about thi-"
msgstr "Espere um momento, podemos conversar sobr-"

#. [message]
#. Vovan has been turned into a ghoul, and the other prisoner has been too.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:626
msgid "I... Hunger..."
msgstr "Eu... Tenho fome..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:631
msgid ""
"By the Clans, she wields slaves as weapons! This injustice will not stand!"
msgstr "Pelos Clãs, elas usa escravos como armas! Essa injustiça acaba aqui!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:635
msgid ""
"By all that is holy, she wields slaves as weapons! This evil will not stand!"
msgstr ""
"Por tudo o que é sagrado, ela usa escravos como armas! Esse mau acaba aqui!"

#. [message]: id=Owaec,Terraent
#. two dwarves, with a Deathblade as the jailer
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:649
msgid ""
"More prisoners approach from the northwest! I have not the time to depart "
"and return with Gweddry, or those dwarves will surely be slain."
msgstr ""
"Mais prisioneiros se aproximam pelo noroeste! Eu não tenho tempo para partir "
"e retornar com Gweddry, ou estes anões certamente serão assassinados."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:653
msgid ""
"I may have failed my original mission, but in the name of the Clans, I will "
"not fail these prisoners now!"
msgstr ""
"Eu posso ter falhado na minha missão original, mas em nome dos Clãs, não "
"falharei com esses prisioneiros agora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:657
msgid ""
"I may have failed my original mission, but by the holy Light, I will not "
"fail these prisoners now!"
msgstr ""
"Eu posso ter falhado na minha missão original mas, pela Luz sagrada, não "
"falharei com esses prisioneiros!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. the speaker was renamed to Mal-Mana at the start
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:674
msgid ""
"Wait — I remember you! You’re one of the ones who fled from me last autumn "
"near Soradoc!"
msgstr ""
"Espere — eu me lembro de você! Você é um dos que fugiu de mim no último "
"outono perto de Soradoc!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:678
msgid ""
"This time I’ve traded my bats for ghouls. There’s no way you’ll escape now!"
msgstr ""
"Desta vez eu troquei meus morcegos por carniçais. Agora não tem como você "
"escapar!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:809
msgid "Nargaril"
msgstr "Nargaril"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:826
msgid "Urmarol"
msgstr "Urmarol"

#. [message]: speaker=Nargaril
#. to a Deathblade
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:851
msgid "Get yer filthy chains off my wrists, ye pile o’ bones!"
msgstr "Retire as tuas imundas correntes dos meus pulsos, pilha de ósos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Urmarol
#. "Thank you kindly for freeing us! My runesmithing arts are not meant to be used outside of knalga, but I think now is an exception. I just hope the East Gate didn't fare too bad after I was captured..."
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:865
msgid ""
"Thank ye kindly fer freein’ us! Me runesmithin’ arts are not meant ta be "
"used outside o’ Knalga, but methinks now is an exception. I just hope tha "
"East Gate dinnae fare’n too bad after I were captured..."
msgstr ""
"Moitas grazas por libertar-nos! As miñas artes rúnicas non deberían ser "
"usadas fóra de Knalga, pero creo que agora é uma exceção. Só espero que o "
"Portão Leste non se sairam tan mal despois de que me capturaram..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:882
msgid "Vinreddoc"
msgstr "Vinreddoc"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:899
msgid "Tunreoryr"
msgstr "Tunreoryr"

#. [message]: speaker=Vinreddoc
#. spoken between two prisoners, "them" being the undead forces
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:924
msgid "How are there so many of them? Is this the end of all Wesnoth?"
msgstr "Como que eles podem ser tão numerosos? Será esse o fim de Wesnoth?"

#. [message]: speaker=Tunreoryr
#. spoken between two prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:929
msgid "Don’t worry. I’m sure the Crown has a plan..."
msgstr "Não se preocupe. Eu tenho certeza de que a Coroa tem um plano..."

#. [message]: speaker=Vinreddoc
#. Vinreddoc is a mage, but with random gender
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:943
msgid ""
"Thank you! When the undead overran the academy I thought I was dead for "
"sure. I just wonder what has happened to my friends..."
msgstr ""
"Obrigado! Quando os mortos-vivos conquistaram a academia, pensei que esse "
"seria o meu fim. Me pergunto o que aconteceu com os meus amigos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:947
msgid "Take heart! As long as there is Light, hope always remains."
msgstr "Tenha coragem! Enquanto existir Luz, a esperança não morrerá."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:964
msgid "Ugzush"
msgstr "Ugzush"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:981
msgid "Hibro"
msgstr "Hibro"

#. [message]: speaker=Hibro
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1008
msgid "I’ll take you all on! As soon as I get out of these chains..."
msgstr "Eu enfrentarei todos vocês! Assim que eu me livrar dessas correntes..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaoler_Orcs
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1012
msgid "Silence. Orcs. March."
msgstr "Silêncio. Orcs. Marchem."

#. [message]: speaker=Ugzush
#. he's just been rescued
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1026
msgid ""
"Cruddy undead think they can chain me up! I’ll grind their bones into dust!"
msgstr ""
"Esses mortos-vivos imundos pensam que conseguem me prender! Eu irei reduzir "
"seus ossos para o pó!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1043
msgid "Syner"
msgstr "Syner"

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#. this Dark Adept is a prisoner too
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1091
msgid ""
"I swear, it was an accident! Please, if you’ll just let me talk to Mel "
"Guthrak, I’m sure this can all be straightened out."
msgstr ""
"Eu juro, foi um acidente! Por favor, se vocês me deixarem falar com Mel "
"Guthrak, eu tenho certeza que isso pode ser resolvido."

#. [message]: speaker=Syner
#. to Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1096
msgid ""
"Your time is done, necromancer. If I have one small comfort, it’s that I’ll "
"get to watch you die alongside me."
msgstr ""
"Sua hora chegou, necromante. Me serve de consolo que eu verei você morrer."

#. [message]: speaker=Syner
#. speaking of Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1110
msgid "I’m free! Now I’ll have the pleasure of killing this dark adept myself."
msgstr ""
"Estou livre! Agora terei o prazer de matar este aprendiz da escuridão "
"pessoalmente."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#. speaking to Syner about Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1123
msgid ""
"Stay your hand, man of Wesnoth! A killing in cold blood is no justice and "
"revenge will bring you no peace."
msgstr ""
"Alto lá, homem de Wesnoth! Matar a sangue frio não é justiça e vingança não "
"o trará paz alguma."

#. [message]: speaker=Syner
#. speaking of Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1128
msgid "Are you mad? That woman is a necromancer!"
msgstr "Você está louco? Esta mulher é uma necromante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1132
msgid ""
"...you might as well. They think I’m a traitor. I’m as good as dead already."
msgstr ""
"...pode me matar. Eles pensam que sou uma traidora. Já estou praticamente "
"morta agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1136
msgid ""
"Then the choice is yours. Flee and face the world alone, or forswear your "
"dark arts and join me to protect all that yet remains holy in this good "
"world."
msgstr ""
"Então a escolha é sua. Fuja e encare o mundo sozinha, ou renuncie às suas "
"artes sombrias e se junte a mim para proteger tudo o que ainda existe de "
"sagrado neste mundo bom."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1148
msgid "Okay. No more necromancy. I’ll join you."
msgstr "Certo. Sem mais necromancia. Me juntarei a você."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. speaking to Syner, who has just killed Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1193
msgid "And so justice has been served! Such is the fate of all evildoers."
msgstr "E assim a justiça foi feita! Tal é o destino de todos os malfeitores."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1213
msgid "Scyla"
msgstr "Scyla"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1230
msgid "Mame"
msgstr "Mame"

#. [message]: speaker=Gaoler_Merfolk
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1259
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1281
msgid "March. Faster."
msgstr "Marche. Mais. Rápido."

#. [message]: speaker=Mame
#. a Mermaid Priestess as prisoner, the line ends with the jailer hitting her
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1264
msgid "We’re going as fast as we can! Maybe if you’d let us swim-"
msgstr ""
"Nós estamos indo o mais rápido que podemos! Talvez se você nos deixar nada-"

#. [message]: speaker=Mame
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1294
msgid ""
"Thanks stranger! I do not recognize these lands, but I do recognize a kind "
"heart when I meet one. Should I ever find my way home to the coast, I will "
"be sure to tell my kinsmen of your actions here."
msgstr ""
"Obrigado, estranho! Não reconheço estas terras, mas reconheço um coração "
"gentil quando vejo um. Se eu algum dia encontrar meu caminho de volta para a "
"minha casa, explorarei para os membros do meu povo sobre suas ações aqui."

#. [message]: id=Owaec,Terraent
#. "we" being the speaker and the prisoners that they've rescued
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1305
msgid "Now we come for you, necromancer!"
msgstr "Agora vamos atrás em você, necromante!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. each bat-summoning event is triggered by the player rescuing prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1354
msgid ""
"Of course, just because I said I wouldn’t summon bats doesn’t mean I can’t..."
msgstr ""
"É claro, só porque eu disse que não invocaria morcegos não significa que eu "
"não consiga..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. each bat-summoning event is triggered by the player rescuing prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1362
msgid "My prisoners!! You’ll pay for that..."
msgstr "Meus prisioneiros!! Vocês pagarão por isto..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. this is a common misquote from the wizard of oz, she's talking to her bats
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1372
msgid "Fly, my pretties, fly!"
msgstr "Voem, meus lindinhos, voem!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. to Terraent. She's summoning bats.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1399
msgid "Not again! Do not test me, paladin of Wesnoth..."
msgstr "De novo não! Não me teste, paladino de Wesnoth..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. to Owaec. She's summoning bats.
#. The text is an allusion to drowned plains, which the next scenario will reveal to be the current state of the Horse Clans' beloved plains.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1408
msgid "Not again! Do not test me, lord of the swamps..."
msgstr "De novo não! Não me teste, lorde dos pântanos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. More prisoners rescued, more bats get summoned.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1432
msgid "You are starting to become rather irritating."
msgstr "Você está começando a me irritar."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1454
msgid "Enough! My bats will feast on your blood!"
msgstr "Chega! Meus morcegos festejarão em seu sangue!"

# Nanomachines, son!
# They harden in response to physical trauma
#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1477
msgid "Why won’t you just die?!"
msgstr "Por que você não morre?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. victory event, and the rest of the player's units catch up
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1561
msgid ""
"Hail, Terraent! We feared the worst when you did not return, yet here I find "
"you alive and well!"
msgstr ""
"Salve, Terraent! Nós tememos pelo o pior quando você não retornou, mas agora "
"eu o vejo são e salvo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. victory event, and the rest of the player's units catch up
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1569
msgid ""
"Hail, Owaec! We feared the worst when you did not return, yet here I find "
"you alive and well!"
msgstr ""
"Salve, Owaec! Nós tememos pelo o pior quando você não retornou, mas agora eu "
"o vejo são e salvo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1582
msgid ""
"Indeed! The Light blessed me with an opportunity to save many souls and I "
"could not decline! Now the crossing is clear, and we may return to see what "
"has become of our homeland."
msgstr ""
"De fato! A Luz me abençoou com a oportunidade de salvar muitas almas "
"diferentes e eu não pude recusar! Agora a travessia está livre, e podemos "
"retornar para ver o que se tornou da nossa terra natal."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1589
msgid ""
"Huzzah! Today has been a great victory! I have rescued a great many "
"prisoners and defeated a foul necromancer! Now the crossing is clear, and we "
"may return to see what has become of our homeland."
msgstr ""
"Viva! Hoje tivemos uma grande vitória! Eu resgatei muitos prisioneiros e "
"derrotei uma necromante terrível! Agora a travessia está livre, e podemos "
"retornar para ver o que se fez da nossa terra natal."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1596
msgid "You’re too late! Wesnoth is... already..."
msgstr "Vocês estão muito atrasados! Wesnoth já... está..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1647
msgid ""
"Hail, Terraent! We feared the worst when you did not return, yet here I find "
"you alive and well! But who is this you are fighting?"
msgstr ""
"Salve, Terraent! Nós tememos pelo o pior quando você não retornou, mas agora "
"eu o vejo são e salvo! Mas quem é essa com quem você está lutando?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1654
msgid ""
"Hail, Owaec! We feared the worst when you did not return, yet here I find "
"you alive and well! But who is this you are fighting?"
msgstr ""
"Salve, Owaec! Nós tememos pelo o pior quando você não retornou, mas agora eu "
"o vejo são e salvo! Mas quem é essa com quem você está lutando?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Yrna
#. she dispatches a messenger bat after this, leading to Dacyn saying all is lost
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1661
msgid ""
"Can it be? Dacyn the mage? We thought you perished in the wild northlands, "
"but now I find you alive and isolated from Wesnoth! I must inform Mal-"
"Ravanal!"
msgstr ""
"É isso mesmo? Dacyn, o mago? Pensávamos que você tinha morrido nas terras "
"selvagens do norte, mas agora encontro você vivo e isolado de Wesnoth! Eu "
"preciso informar Mal-Ravanal!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/13_Spoils_of_War.cfg:1687
msgid ""
"Even if we triumph at this crossing, Mal-Ravanal will surely find and "
"destroy us before we can reunite with Wesnoth..."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo que triunfemos nesta travessia, Mal-Ravanal com certeza nos encontrará "
"e destruirá antes de chegarmos em Wesnoth..."

#. [scenario]: id=14_The_Drowned_Plains
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:18
msgid "The Drowned Plains"
msgstr "As Planícies Inundadas"

#. [part]
#. In this scenario, there's circa 18 ghosts, each with a single line of speech, you'll recognise them because most start and end with ellipsis. The WML would need to be restructured to put po hints on those lines themselves.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:37
msgid ""
"Anxious to rendezvous with the Wesnothian army, Gweddry, Owaec, and Dacyn "
"pressed hurriedly westward. Their hearts sank as they passed battlefield "
"after battlefield, in the ruins of what used to be Wesnoth’s thriving "
"eastern provinces."
msgstr ""
"Ansiosos para se encontrarem com o exército Wesnothiano, Gweddry, Owaec e "
"Dacyn seguiram apressadamente para o oeste. O coração deles apertou enquanto "
"passaram por campo de batalha após campo de batalha, nas ruínas do que "
"costumava ser as prósperas províncias orientais de Wesnoth."

#. [leader]: type=Barrow Wight, id=Sir Seoraery
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:109
msgid "Sir Seoraery"
msgstr "Sir Seoraery"

#. [leader]: type=Pyre Wight, id=Sir Efran
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:128
msgid "Sir Efran"
msgstr "Sir Efran"

#. [leader]: type=Skeletal Dragon, id=Khrakrahs
#. Date of death unknown, seen alive in 40 YW during the Sceptre of Fire campaign.
#. Male; he's been canon in many versions of Wesnoth that only had male drakes, thus will surely have been male in any translation that needed to know his gender.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:149
msgid "Khrakrahs"
msgstr "Khrakrahs"

#. [side]
#. neutral side, is only horses (although the user_team_name is vaguer than that)
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:325
msgid "Animals"
msgstr "Animais"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:479
msgid "... I failed you all..."
msgstr "... Eu falhei com todos vocês..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:480
msgid "... my daughter... what has happened to my daughter?"
msgstr "... minha filha... o que aconteceu com minha filha?"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:481
msgid ""
"... they don’t know pain... they don’t know fatigue... there was nothing we "
"could have done..."
msgstr ""
"... eles não conhecem a dor... eles não conhecem a fadiga... não tinha nada "
"que poderíamos ter feito..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:482
msgid "Lords of Light... what affront did I commit to deserve this fate..."
msgstr "Senhores da Luz... que afronta eu cometi para merecer este destino..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:483
msgid "I fought the undead with everything... I gave everything..."
msgstr ""
"Eu lutei contra os mortos-vivos com tudo o que tinha... eu dei tudo de mim..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:484
msgid ""
"... it came from the shadows. A gust of wind, then a claw through my chest..."
msgstr ""
"...veio das sombras. Uma rajada de vento, e então uma garra aravessando meu "
"peito..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:485
msgid "... please, find my wife... tell her my story."
msgstr "... por favor, encontre minha esposa... diga a ela minha história."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:486
msgid "... honor, glory, wealth... none of it saved us in the end."
msgstr "... honra, glória, riqueza... nada disso nos salvou no fim."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:487
msgid "... they won’t let me die... why won’t they let me die?"
msgstr "... eles não me deixam morrer... por que eles não me deixam morrer?"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:488
msgid ""
"... they tore the ribs out from my friends... then fashioned them into "
"arrows."
msgstr ""
"... eles arrancaram as costelas dos meus amigos... e então transformaram "
"elas em flechas."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:489
msgid ""
"... I could not hurt him... my own father... his corpse risen to fight me."
msgstr ""
"... Eu não tive coragem de machucar ele... meu próprio pai... o corpo dele "
"se levantou para lutar contra mim."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:490
msgid "... Lord Gaelyc, I have failed you."
msgstr "... Lorde Gaelyc, eu falhei com você."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:491
msgid "... the Clans were not prepared... I was not prepared."
msgstr "... os Clãs não estava preparados... eu não estava preparado."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:492
msgid "... how could we have known? What could we have done?"
msgstr "... como nós poderíamos saber? O que poderíamos ter feito?"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:493
msgid "... my family, where is my family?"
msgstr "... minha família, onde está minha família?"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:494
msgid "... what good was my lance... against a creature... without flesh?"
msgstr ""
"... de que me adiantava minha lança... contra uma criatura... sem carne?"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:495
msgid ""
"At first I thought he was one of ours... then he waved his hand and my blood "
"ran cold..."
msgstr ""
"No começo pensei que ele fosse um de nós... e então ele acenou sua mão e meu "
"sangue gelou..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:496
msgid "... so cold... so dark..."
msgstr "... tão frio... tão escuro..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. Player's unit has just been ambushed. Some other nearby corpses have awoken too, but the player will find that out during the enemy turn.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:578
msgid ""
"Gah, undead! This one was mired face-first in the swamp, dormant until I "
"stumbled upon it. They must be lying everywhere in this muck."
msgstr ""
"Gah, morto-vivo! Este estava atolado de cara para baixo no pântano, "
"adormecido até eu tropeçar nele. Eles devem estar por todas as partes nesta "
"lama."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:582
msgid ""
"Perhaps their leaders are dormant as well. I suspect we will not have to "
"contend with them until we sight them. We can afford some time to capture "
"villages and build our forces."
msgstr ""
"Talvez os seus líderes também estejam adormecidos. Eu suspeito que nós não "
"precisaremos lutar contra eles até os vermos. Nós podemos gastar algum tempo "
"capturando aldeias e construindo nossas forças."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. Player's unit trigger an ambush last turn. During the enemy turn, some other nearby corpses started moving too.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:589
msgid ""
"Whenever we stumble upon a corpse, it awakens its nearby allies! What will "
"happen when we wake their leaders?"
msgstr ""
"Sempre que esbarramos com um corpo, ele acorda os seus aliados próximos! O "
"que acontecerá quando acordarmos os seus líderes?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. The keeps are visible, so the player can guess where the leaders themselves are.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:594
msgid ""
"It may be prudent to clear the swamp near the undead leaders before we sight "
"them."
msgstr ""
"Talvez seja prudente limparmos o pântano perto dos líderes morto-vivos antes "
"de vermos eles."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:723
msgid "Their leader is waking nearby allies out from the swamp!"
msgstr "O líder deles está levantando mais aliados do próprio pântano!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:727
msgid "Just more abominations for us to slay!!"
msgstr "São só mais abominações para nós matarmos!!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:800
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "10 gold"
msgid "105 gold"
msgstr "10 de ouro"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:801
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:805
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "10 gold"
msgid "80 gold"
msgstr "10 de ouro"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:802
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "115 gold"
msgid "175 gold"
msgstr "115 de ouro"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:803
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "25 gold"
msgid "55 gold"
msgstr "25 peças de ouro"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:804
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "10 gold"
msgid "150 gold"
msgstr "10 de ouro"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:807
msgid "Lord Alric’s Palace"
msgstr "Palácio de Lorde Alric"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:808
msgid "Sir Efran’s Castle"
msgstr "Castelo do Sir Efran"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:809
msgid "Lord Gaelyc’s Citadel"
msgstr "Cidadela do Lorde Gaelyc"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:810
msgid "Sir Seoraery’s Keep"
msgstr "Fortaleza do Sir Seoraery"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:811
msgid "Clearwater Lake"
msgstr "Lago da Água Clara"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:864
msgid "Defeat the spirits"
msgstr "Derrote os espíritos"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. The player hasn't recruited yet, so listening are Gweddry, Dacyn, and the auto-recalled optional loyals (at most 8 people in total).
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:896
msgid ""
"At last we have reached the Horse Plains, the fair homeland of my people! "
"Here we can finally reunite with our comrades-in-arms and vanquish the "
"undead once and for all."
msgstr ""
"Finalmente chegamos às Planícies dos Cavalos, a bela terra natal de meu "
"povo! Aqui nós podemos finalmente nos reunir com nossos camaradas em armas e "
"acabar com os mortos-vivos de uma vez por todas."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. Shouted to the landscape, expecting to find living comrades. What will answer is walking corpses and ghosts.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:906
msgid "Hail, Clansmen! Come and greet one of your own!"
msgstr "Saudações, membros do Clã! Venham e cumprimentem um dos seus!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:910
msgid "Fallen Clansman"
msgstr "Membro do Clã Caído"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:930
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:828
msgid "No."
msgstr "Não."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:934
msgid ""
"No, NO! Why are there swamps here? Why are there undead here? How can this "
"be?! How can Mal-Ravanal have already advanced so far into the heartland of "
"Wesnoth?"
msgstr ""
"Não, NÃO! Por que tem pântanos aqui? Por que tem mortos-vivos aqui? Como "
"isso é possível?! Como pôde Mal-Ravanal já ter avançado tão para dentro de "
"Wesnoth?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:938
msgid ""
"I’m sorry Owaec. The undead armies must have defeated the Clansmen and "
"dammed the river to drown the plains. They must like the swamp, filled with "
"death and decay..."
msgstr ""
"Me desculpe, Owaec. O exército dos morto-vivo deve ter derrotado os membros "
"do Clã e represado o rio para afogar as planícies. Eles devem gostar do "
"pântano, cheio de morte e apodrecimento..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:942
msgid "My home... my people... how could this happen..."
msgstr "Minha casa... meu povo... como isso pôde acontecer..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:952
msgid ""
"YOU! MAGE!!! Had you not insisted we travel north, we might have arrived in "
"time to save these people! My friends, my family, dead from your neglect. "
"And all for what? Some necromancer’s trinket more likely to curse us than "
"save us?"
msgstr ""
"VOCÊ! MAGO!!! Se você não tivesse insistido em viajarmos para o norte, "
"talvez tivéssemos chegado a tempo de salvar essas pessoas! Meus amigos, "
"minha família, mortos pela sua negligência. E tudo em troca de quê? Uma "
"bugiganga de um necromante que provavelmente nos amaldiçoará em vez de nos "
"salvar?"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:956
msgid ""
"We trusted you. I trusted you! Instead, you sent us away from the war like "
"cowards, led our men to slaughter at the hand of orcs and drakes, and "
"deprived Wesnoth of her eastern guard when she needed it most sorely. And "
"now my homeland has paid the price for your misdeeds!!"
msgstr ""
"Nós confiamos em você. Eu confiei em você! E o que você fez? Você nos enviou "
"para longe da guerra como covardes, liderou nossos homens ao abate pelas "
"mãos de orcs e draconatos, e privou Wesnoth de sua guarda oriental quando "
"ela era mais necessária. E agora minha terra natal pagou o preço pelas suas "
"más ações!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. Dacyn is bleeding and about to take damage from an unknown source
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:966
msgid "Are you even listening?!?"
msgstr "Você sequer está ouvindo?!?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. Dacyn is bleeding and taking damage, from an unknown source
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:983
msgid "Dacyn, what’s wrong? Are you all right?"
msgstr "Dacyn, o que está errado? Você está bem?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. Dacyn steps away from the initial encampment, and is about take a lot of damage
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:995
msgid "...I can’t-"
msgstr "...Eu não consigo-"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. Dacyn stepped away from the castle, the six hexes around him have changed to chasms and he's down to 15 hp.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1042
msgid "I’ve lost control of the Amulet! I must-"
msgstr "Perdi o controle do amuleto! Eu devo-"

#. [message]
#. up to 6 ghosts or wraiths come out of the chasms, depending on difficulty and how many auto-recalled loyals the player has
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1067
msgid "And most importantly..."
msgstr ""

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1074
msgid "Lord Alric"
msgstr "Lorde Alric"

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Alric
#. speaker is a wraith, he's emerged from the chasms around Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1080
msgid "Owaec, my son..."
msgstr "Owaec, meu filho..."

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Alric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1084
msgid "Why did you abandon us? I am dead... thanks to you..."
msgstr "Por que você nos abandonou? Eu estou morto... graças a você..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1088
msgid "No, it’s not true! You’re not dead! I don’t believe you!"
msgstr "Não, isto não é verdade! Você não está morto! Eu não acredito em você!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. Owaec rides off to the south, into the shroud, and disappears
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1093
msgid "Owaec, wait!"
msgstr "Owaec, espere!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1112
msgid "What do I do now?"
msgstr "O que eu faço agora?"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. The chasms are filled with sand, so all terrain near the keep is walkable again.
#. Dacyn has healed back to full HP, although that's for gameplay reasons because he needs to fight the ghosts, there isn't a story reason for it.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1135
msgid "(gasping) I have regained control!"
msgstr "(ofegante) Recuperei o controle!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1139
msgid "What happened? I did not know this Amulet could act of its own accord."
msgstr ""
"O que aconteceu? Eu não sabia que este amuleto poderia agir por vontade "
"própria."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1143
msgid ""
"Neither did I. I should have sensed it, but the darkness is nearly "
"overwhelming. Even with my inner light, the best I can do is cancel out this "
"dark energy. Such is the price of power..."
msgstr ""
"E nem eu. Eu deveria ter pressentido isto, mas a escuridão é quase "
"insuportável. Mesmo com minha luz interior, o melhor que consigo fazer é "
"cancelar esta energia obscura. Tal é o preço do poder..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. loses his halo and advances to an L4 Twilight Mage (liminal, heals +4, does not illuminate, melee attack gains "drain")
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1148
msgid ""
"... but it is a necessary price to pay. I will not let up until Mal-Ravanal "
"is defeated, whatever the cost may be."
msgstr ""
"... mas é um preço necessário a se pagar. Não irei parar até que Mal-Ravanal "
"seja derrotado, custe o que custar."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. Owaec is near his father's castle, and there's a dead (not undead) skeleton on the keep
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1229
msgid "...so it is true. My lord and father is dead."
msgstr "... então é verdade. Meu lorde e pai está morto."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. today is when he learns the news of that, not when it happened
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1238
msgid ""
"Today truly is a day of ill fortune. My family is slain, my kinsmen "
"scattered, my homeland defiled."
msgstr ""
"Hoje realmente é um dia de muito infortuno. Minha família assassinada, os "
"membros do meu clã dispersos, minha terra profanada."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1242
msgid ""
"But I will not despair! This damning destruction will not be the lasting "
"legacy of the Clans!! These undead will pay for the death they have "
"brought!!!"
msgstr ""
"Mas eu não me entregarei ao desespero! Esta maldita destruição não será o "
"último legado dos Clãs!! Estes mortos-vivos pagarão pela morte que "
"trouxeram!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1279
msgid ""
"Owaec, do not be so hasty. Much of the horde that conquered this place now "
"marches on Weldyn, but even what little lingers is surely more than a match "
"for our weary band."
msgstr ""
"Owaec, não seja tão imprudente. Boa parte da horda que conquistou este lugar "
"agora marcha para Weldyn, mas até mesmo os poucos que continuam aqui sem "
"dúvida alguma são mais do que páreos para o nosso grupo exausto."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1283
msgid ""
"I agree, yet all is strangely quiet. Perhaps the remaining undead lie "
"dormant?\n"
"\n"
"Even if we lack the strength to truly reclaim this place, we should still "
"take the opportunity to gather what supplies remain. When finally we meet "
"the shambling hordes responsible for all this destruction, we must not find "
"our armories wanting."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1291
msgid "Gather as much gold as you can before turns run out."
msgstr ""

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1296
msgid "Loot Addogin’s smugglers’ caches."
msgstr "Saqueie os caches dos contrabandistas de Addogin."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1311
msgid ""
"Enemy leaders are idle until first sighted, but will then abandon their keep "
"and attack you."
msgstr ""
"Líderes inimigos estão inativos até serem avistados pela primeira vez, mas "
"então abandonarão suas torres de mensagem e atacarão você."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1319
msgid ""
"On a quest of searing vengeance? Owaec my friend, what you need is my elixir "
"of ulfserker fury! One taste of this bitter red ambrosia and you’ll fight "
"until you drop, with <b><i>unlimited melee attacks</i></b> and the "
"<b><i>berserk</i></b> melee special!"
msgstr ""
"Em busca de vingança? Owaec, meu amigo, o que você precisa é do meu elixir "
"de fúria de um ulfserker! Um gole desta amarga ambrosia vermelha e você "
"lutará até cair, com <b><i>ataques corpo-a-corpo ilimitados</i></b> e o "
"especial <b><i>berserk</i></b>!"

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#. player bought the elixir of ulfserker fury
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1333
msgid "Try not to die too quickly!"
msgstr "Tente não morrer muito rápido!"

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#. player declined the elixir of ulfserker fury
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1342
msgid "Suit yourself! Don’t expect me to drink that though, I’m not suicidal!"
msgstr "Como queira! Só não espere que eu beba essa coisa, eu não sou suicida!"

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1347
msgid ""
"This offer expires as soon as your anger does! <i>(elixirs only last for 1 "
"scenario)</i>"
msgstr ""
"Esta oferta expira assim que sua raiva acabar! <i>(elixires duram apenas 1 "
"cenário)</i>"

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1349
msgid "Buy the elixir for Owaec (30 gold)."
msgstr "Compre o elixir para Owaec (30 peças de ouro)."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1359
msgid "Leave the elixir."
msgstr "Deixe o elixir."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#. Wait a moment... this landscape looks familiar.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1387
msgid ""
"Hol’ up... some of this place is lookin’ mighty familiar. Yeah, few years "
"back I used to work for a smuggler ’round these parts."
msgstr ""
"Pera aí... algumas partes daqui me parecem familiares. É, alguns anos atrás "
"eu costumava trabalhar pra um contrabandista por aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#. hint about the smuggler's hidden gold, will be followed by adding three "go here" markers to the map
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1392
msgid ""
"I’m sure the undead have burned down his storehouse, but there might still "
"be a cache or three hidden ’round here."
msgstr ""
"Eu tenho certeza que os mortos-vivos queimaram seu armazém. Porém, ainda "
"deve ter um ou três caches escondidos por aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1416
msgid ""
"We should retrieve as many as we can; I’m sure the extra gold will be useful."
msgstr ""
"Nós devemos pegar o máximo que pudermos; tenho certeza de que o ouro extra "
"será útil."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1420
msgid ""
"Just remember, I ain’t been here in years. Some of them caches might be "
"empty now."
msgstr ""
"Mas lembre-se, eu não venho aqui a anos. Alguns desses caches já devem estar "
"vazios agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#. although there are three map markers to explore, the first one that the player explores always has this gold, and the second is always empty
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1467
msgid ""
"That’s the first cache. Lookee here, my smuggler friend left us 45 gold "
"pieces."
msgstr ""
"Esse é o primeiro cache. Olhe aqui, meu amigo contrabandista deixou pra "
"gente 45 peças de ouro."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1481
msgid ""
"This be the second cache, but looks like some’un found it before us. Empty."
msgstr ""
"Esse é o segundo cache, mas parece que alguém achou ele antes da gente. "
"Vazio."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1487
msgid "Third ’n last cache, and it’s loaded! A clean 100 gold pieces."
msgstr "Terceiro e último cache, e tá lotado! Exatas 100 peças de ouro."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1499
msgid "Excellent! The gold from these caches will be very helpful."
msgstr "Excelente! O ouro desses caches será bastante útil."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#. this is probably grug's first time fighting squishy undead (though there were a few in S10)
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1550
msgid "Squishy fun to squash! Squash squish squash!"
msgstr "Mole, divertido de esmagar! Esmague esprema esmague!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. "odd that his body didn't become undead"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1572
msgid ""
"This man looks to have been dead for about a month. Odd that his body yet "
"lies still."
msgstr ""
"Este homem parece estar morto já tem um mês. Estranho que seu corpo ainda "
"esteja imóvel."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1585
msgid "There is a journal here, still intact despite the swamp."
msgstr "Tem um diário aqui, e ainda está intacto apesar do pântano."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. Reading from a dead horseman's journal. This is a warning to the player that there's a Skeletal Dragon in the scenario.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1590
msgid ""
"<i>... we thought the enemy had erred, that the battle could yet be won. "
"Taking advantage of the gap, our swiftest riders drove toward the exposed "
"heart of the skeletal formation. But even as they wrought destruction within "
"the necromancers’ ranks, from out of the water came a great tremor, as if "
"Irdya herself shivered in morbid anticipation.\n"
"\n"
"For a moment, I espied a great bony figure, a shambling mass of tooth and "
"claw and wing. Then it fell upon us from behind, and the enemy closed their "
"ranks, and we were encircled by death.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>... nós pensamos que o inimigo tinha errado, que a batalha ainda podia "
"ser ganha. Aproveitando a brecha, nossos cavaleiros mais rápidos cavalgaram "
"para o coração exposto da formação esquelética. Porém, mesmo com eles "
"levando destruição a para dentro das fileiras dos necromantes, da água "
"surgiu um grande tremor, como se a própria Irdya estremecesse em mórbida "
"antecipação.\n"
"\n"
"Por um momento, eu vi uma grande figura de ossos, uma massa cambaleante de "
"dentes, garras e asas. Então ele nos atacou por trás, e o inimigo fechou as "
"fileiras pela frente, e então nós estávamos cercados pela morte</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. Reading more from the dead horseman's journal, whose corpse prompted the "odd that his body didn't become undead" comment.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1597
msgid ""
"<i>I fled, coward that I am, riding breakneck through the night before my "
"injuries overcame my strength. And so it comes that I have earned no "
"honorable death in battle, only the slow fatigue and fever borne by rot and "
"poison.\n"
"\n"
"I offer one final prayer to the Light, that at least my family may be spared "
"and that my soul may be kept from undeath...</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Eu fugi, covarde como sou, cavalgando a toda velocidade pela noite antes "
"que meus machucados sobrepusessem minha força. E foi assim que eu não obtive "
"uma morte honrada em batalha, e sim a lenta fatiga e febre pela podridão e "
"veneno.\n"
"\n"
"Ofereço uma última oração à Luz, que pelo menos minha família possa ser "
"poupada e que minha alma seja livrada da vida-em-morte...</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Seoraery
#. no-one sends a messenger, he's talking about memories from before he died
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1646
msgid "... we need... reinforcements... send a messenger..."
msgstr "... nós precisamos... de reforços... envie um mensageiro..."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1650
msgid "I’m not your enemy!"
msgstr "Eu não sou seu inimigo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Seoraery
#. he's talking of a memory, not the current situation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1655
msgid "...must... hold... the line."
msgstr "... preciso... manter... a posição."

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Efran
#. he's talking of a memory, not the current situation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1707
msgid "... there’s... too many."
msgstr "... eles... são muitos."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1711
msgid ""
"You and your men have been turned to undeath! Let us put you out of your "
"misery."
msgstr ""
"Você e seus homens foram transformados em mortos-vivos! Nos deixe acabar com "
"a sua miséria."

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Efran
#. he's talking to a memory, not the unit that triggered the event
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1716
msgid "... I would sooner... die... than yield to you... necromancer."
msgstr "... Eu prefiro... morrer... do que me render a você... necromante."

#. [effect]: type=impact
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1786
msgid "tail"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. undead dragon, talking to a memory rather than the unit that triggered him
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1817
msgid "... Lich, you do not belong here... leave, or I shall... rend you..."
msgstr ""
"... Lich, você não pertence a este lugar... saia, ou eu irei... rasgar "
"você..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1821
msgid ""
"Is that... an undead dragon? Dear Light! Raising such a powerful thrall must "
"have been no small feat, even for a necromancer such as Mal-Ravanal."
msgstr ""
"Isso é... um dragão morto-vivo? Pela Luz! Reanimar um escravo tão poderoso "
"não deve ter sido uma tarefa fácil, mesmo para um necromante como Mal-"
"Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1825
msgid ""
"Even a living dragon is nothing but flesh. This feeble imitation lacks even "
"that. Smash it to pieces."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo um dragão vivo não é nada além de carne. Esta débil imitação carece "
"até isso. Faça-o em pedaços."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. undead dragon, again talking to a memory rather than anyone currently on the map
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1830
msgid "... I warned you... Ravanal... now <b>burn</b>."
msgstr "... Eu avisei você... Ravanal... agora <b>queime</b>."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. speaker is one of the undead leaders, in an [event]name=attack
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1921
msgid ""
"... Owaec... why do you fight me? Join us... ride alongside your father... "
"defend the plains..."
msgstr ""
"... Owaec... por que você luta contra mim? Se junte a nós.. cavalgue ao lado "
"de seu pai... defenda as planícies..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. speaking to one of the undead leaders, in an [event]name=attack
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1926
msgid ""
"Abomination!! Clansmen though you once were, I have no choice but to grind "
"you into dust now."
msgstr ""
"Abominação!! Embora você já tenha sido um membros dos Clãs, eu não tenho "
"escolha a não ser acabar com tigo agora."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. speaking to Khrakrahs in an [event]name=attack, although the anger seems misdirected
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1943
msgid ""
"You! You are the cause of this destruction!! Vengeance for my fallen people!"
msgstr "Você! Você causou está destruição!! Vingança ao meus irmãos mortos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#. speaking to one of the undead leaders (horseman, not dragon) in an [event]name=attack
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1960
msgid ""
"All things deserve redemption, but I fear the undead will never find it. May "
"this place be cleansed in holy fire!"
msgstr ""
"Todas as coisas merecem redenção, mas temo que os morto-vivos nunca a "
"encontrarão. Que este lugar seja purificado pelo fogo sagrado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#. speaking to Khrakrahs in an [event]name=attack
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1977
msgid ""
"I have faced worse terrors than you, lizard! Through piety and the holy "
"Light, this place will be sanctified once more."
msgstr ""
"Eu enfrentei terrores piores que você, lagarto! Através da piedade e da Luz "
"sagrada, este lugar será santificado mais uma vez."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. speaker is an undead horseman, who's fighting Gaennell. Unclear whether this is to a memory, or because Gaennell is a Shadow Mage
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1994
msgid "... Necromancer... you are a blight..."
msgstr "... Necromante... você é uma praga..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#. to an undead horseman in an [event]name=attack
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:1999
msgid ""
"Not sure what you’d call me anymore, but definitely not more of a blight "
"than you."
msgstr ""
"Não sei mais do que você deveria me chamar, mas definitivamente não sou mais "
"uma praga do que você."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. Attacked with a fireball from an L2 or higher mage.
#. Shek’kahan was Khrakrahs' brother, but died during TRoW, 6 centuries ago.
#. The date of Khrakrahs' own death isn't canon, he was still alive in 40 YW (he appears in SoF).
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2018
msgid "... Shek’kahan, your fire grows weak... you are hardly... a rival."
msgstr "... Shek’kahan, seu fogo está mais fraco... você mal é... um rival."

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#. speaker is Khrakrahs when attacked by a dwarf, but remembering one he met in 40 YW.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2035
msgid "... Thursagan... I warned you not... to enter my lair."
msgstr "... Thursagan... Eu o avisei para não... entrar em meu lar."

#. [message]: speaker=Lord Alric
#. last breath request from the ghost of Lord Alric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2052
msgid "... please, watch over my son for me."
msgstr "... por favor, cuide de meu filho por mim."

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Seoraery
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2064
msgid "... I may die... but the Clans... will never fall."
msgstr "... Eu posso morrer... mas os Clãs... nunca cairão."

#. [message]: speaker=Sir Efran
#. last breath, but still talking to a memory rather than the unit currently fighting him
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2077
msgid "... Necromancer... Wesnoth will defeat you... in the end."
msgstr "... Necromante... no final... Wesnoth irá derrotar você."

#. [message]: speaker=Khrakrahs
#. last breath
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2090
msgid "I am... ...<i>cold</i>."
msgstr "Estou com... ...<i>frio</i>."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. spoken at the start of a new turn after killing the first undead leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2102
msgid ""
"Dacyn, I’ve been thinking. This artifact has had such a draining effect on "
"you. Perhaps you should rest and take a moment to regain your strength? I "
"could carry the Amulet for a while, or we could store it away."
msgstr ""
"Dacyn, eu tenho pensado. Este artefato tem drenado você. Talvez você devesse "
"descansar e recuperar suas forças? Eu poderia carregar o amuleto por um "
"tempo, ou poderíamos guardá-lo em algum lugar."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2106
msgid ""
"Hmm... I suppose there would be no harm in locking it up somewhere safe."
msgstr ""
"Hmm... eu suponho que não teria problema trancá-lo em algum lugar seguro."

#. [message]
#. voices from the amulet talking to Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2113
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<span size='small' font-style='italic'>You have a great weapon... and you "
#| "would simply lock it away?</span>"
msgid "You have a great weapon... and you would simply lock it away?"
msgstr ""
"<span size='small' font-style='italic'>Você tem uma arma incrível... e você "
"vai simplesmente deixa-la trancada?</span>"

#. [message]
#. voices from the amulet talking to Dacyn, speaking of Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2120
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<span size='small' font-style='italic'>His intent is good, but his spirit "
#| "is weak... he would be corrupted...</span>"
msgid "His intent is good, but his spirit is weak... he would be corrupted..."
msgstr ""
"<span size='small' font-style='italic'>A intenção dele é boa, mas seu "
"espírito é fraco... ele seria corrompido...</span>"

#. [message]
#. voices from the amulet talking to Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2127
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<span size='small' font-style='italic'>Only you can be trusted with this "
#| "responsibility.</span>"
msgid "Only you can be trusted with this responsibility."
msgstr ""
"<span size='small' font-style='italic'>Apenas você pode ser confiado com "
"esta responsabilidade.</span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2131
msgid ""
"But on the other hand... this is a dangerous artifact. I fear that only I "
"can withstand its energies."
msgstr ""
"Mas por outro lado... este é um artefato perigoso. Temo que apenas eu possa "
"aguentar suas energias."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2135
msgid "Well, you’re the magic expert."
msgstr "Bem, você é o perito em magia."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2147
msgid ""
"If the Horse Clans have fallen so completely, I fear for Weldyn and the rest "
"of Wesnoth. We must make the most of our time here; we cannot afford to "
"tarry too long."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2155
msgid ""
"So much death. So many of my kinsmen left unavenged. If only we had more "
"time..."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2159
msgid "We have done all we could here."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2184
msgid "It is done. My kinsmen have been avenged."
msgstr "Está feito. Meus parentes foram vingados."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2203
msgid ""
"Mage... I owe you an apology. This destruction... even had we journeyed here "
"instead of questing north, we would most assuredly have made no difference. "
"Of that I am now certain.\n"
"\n"
"The fates may yet reveal that our journey north was necessary, even at such "
"a steep cost. I will stand by you in this fight."
msgstr ""
"Mago... Eu devo desculpas a você. Essa destruição... mesmo que tivéssemos "
"vindo para cá ao invés de ir para o norte, não teríamos feito diferença "
"alguma. Agora estou certo disso.\n"
"\n"
"O destino ainda pode revelar que nossa jornada para o norte foi necessária, "
"mesmo tendo pagado um preço alto. Eu ficarei ao seu lado nesta luta."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2209
msgid "Apology accepted."
msgstr "Desculpas aceitas."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2216
msgid ""
"And I too must admit, I underestimated the power in this Amulet. Even now, "
"voices gnaw at the edges of my mind..."
msgstr ""
"E eu devo admitir que subestimei o poder deste amuleto. Mesmo agora, vozes "
"corroem os cantos da minha mente..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. to Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2221
msgid ""
"Make no mistake, I still do not approve of your plan! It will lead you only "
"to ruin and death! Yet, at least now I believe that your intentions are good "
"despite your questionable methods."
msgstr ""
"Não se engane, eu ainda não aprovo o seu plano! Isso o levara apenas à ruína "
"e à morte! Dito isso, pelo menos agora eu acredito que suas intenções são "
"boas, apesar de seus métodos questionáveis."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/14_The_Drowned_Plains.cfg:2225
msgid ""
"I’m glad we have prevailed here, but I fear greatly for Wesnoth if the Clans "
"have been defeated so thoroughly so quickly. It has scant been a year since "
"their invasion first began. Owaec, Dacyn, if you are prepared to travel, we "
"must press toward Weldyn at once."
msgstr ""
"Estou feliz que prevalecemos aqui, mas eu temo muito por Wesnoth, se os Clãs "
"foram derrotados tão completamente e tão rapidamente. Não deve fazer nem um "
"ano desde que a invasão começou. Owaec, Dacyn, se vocês estão preparados "
"para viajar, nós precisamos seguir imediatamente para Weldyn."

#. [scenario]: id=15_Return_to_Wesnoth
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:4
msgid "Return to Wesnoth"
msgstr "Retorno a Wesnoth"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:17
msgid ""
"Leaving the rotting Horse Plains far behind, Gweddry, Owaec, and Dacyn "
"marched hurriedly towards Weldyn, capital of Wesnoth. They dreaded what they "
"might find there..."
msgstr ""
"Deixando as pútridas Planícies dos Cavalos muito para trás, Gweddry, Owaec, "
"e Dacyn marcharam apressadamente para Weldyn, capital de Wesnoth. Eles "
"temiam o que poderiam encontrar lá..."

#. [side]: type=General, id=Halrad
#. [unit]: type=General, id=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:44
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:859
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:64
msgid "Halrad"
msgstr "Halrad"

#. [side]: type=General, id=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:79
msgid "Shield of Ana’sar"
msgstr "Escudo de Ana’sar"

#. [side]: type=General, id=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:87
msgid "Carcyn’s Pride"
msgstr "Orgulho de Carcyn"

#. [side]: type=Necromancer, id=Mal-un-Darak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:176
msgid "Mal-un-Darak"
msgstr "Mal-un-Darak"

#. [side]: type=Dark Sorcerer, id=Mal-un-Zanrad, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:222
msgid "Mal-un-Zanrad"
msgstr "Mal-un-Zanrad"

#. [side]: type=Necromancer, id=Mal-un-Xadrux
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:266
msgid "Mal-un-Xadrux"
msgstr "Mal-un-Xadrux"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:471
msgid ""
"Lo and behold, the great city of Weldyn! Its walls still stand, thank the "
"Light."
msgstr ""
"Aí está a grande cidade de Weldyn! Suas muralhas ainda estão de pé, graças à "
"Luz."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:526
msgid ""
"But look, the undead are laying siege and have built fortifications "
"completely surrounding the city! The defenders must be grievously "
"outnumbered."
msgstr ""
"Mas, olhem, os mortos-vivos estão sitiando-na e construíram fortificações "
"cercando-a por completo! Os defensores devem estar em grande desvantagem "
"numérica."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:577
msgid ""
"Even this undead force appears to be (cough) but a small fraction of Mal-"
"Ravanal’s greater host. (cough)(cough) I must meet with the king. Weldyn "
"will fall if we do not act."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo essa força de mortos-vivos parece ser (tosse) só uma pequena fração do "
"grande exército de Mal-Ravanal. (tosse)(tosse) Preciso me encontrar com o "
"rei. Weldyn cairá se não agirmos."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:628
msgid ""
"Then we must reinforce the city at once. There is a relief tunnel nearby, "
"its entrance still hidden from the dead. Come on men, follow me!"
msgstr ""

#. [time]: id=indoors
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:721
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:917
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:12
msgid "Indoors"
msgstr "Ambiente interno"

#. [unit]: id=Aeraeka, type=Arch Mage, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:755
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:101
msgid "Aeraeka"
msgstr "Aeraeka"

#. [unit]: id=Halric, type=General
#. [side]: type=General, id=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:767
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:93
msgid "Halric"
msgstr "Halric"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:777
msgid "Denogyc"
msgstr "Denogyc"

#. [message]: speaker=Aeraeka
#. the council discusses the northern alliance
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:815
msgid ""
"Well try again! It is absolutely imperative that we get a response from the "
"Northerners."
msgstr ""
"Bem, tente novamente! É absolutamente obrigatório que consigamos uma "
"resposta dos Nortenhos."

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:819
msgid ""
"If help was coming, we would have heard about it by now. They’re either "
"unwilling or unable to march. What we need to consider is-"
msgstr ""
"Se ajuda estivesse vindo, já teríamos ouvido falar dela. Eles ou estão "
"relutantes ou sem condições de marchar. O que precisamos considerar é-"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:823
msgid "Mefel"
msgstr "Mefel"

#. [message]: speaker=Mefel
#. the speaker, a male Silver Mage, has just teleported in
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:833
msgid "Urgent report from the south, Sire! I’m afraid it can’t wait."
msgstr "Reporte urgente do sul, Majestade! Temo que isto não possa esperar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. Denogyc is a male Lancer.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:839
msgid ""
"Denogyc, you’re excused. Get some rest. Minister Mefel, what news of Kerlath?"
msgstr ""
"Denogyc, você está dispensado. Vá descansar. Ministro Mefel, quais são as "
"notícias de Kerlath?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mefel
#. Kerlath Province is the area around Westin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:851
msgid ""
"The siege around Westin has been broken, but Kerlath’s forces are badly "
"depleted. I’m afraid we won’t be able to mount a counter-offensive in time "
"to support you, especially with Mal-Xlana still holding Fort Tahn."
msgstr ""
"O cerco ao redor de Westin foi quebrado, mas as forças de Kerlath estão "
"completamente esgotadas. Temo que não poderemos montar uma contraofensiva a "
"tempo de ajudá-los, especialmente com Mal-Xlana ainda segurando o forte Tahn."

#. [message]: speaker=Aeraeka
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:872
msgid "Oh, what now..."
msgstr "Ah, o que foi agora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:877
msgid ""
"My Liege, your former High Advisor Dacyn is here, and he says he has vital "
"information on how to defeat the undead."
msgstr ""
"Meu senhor, seu ex-Alto Conselheiro Dacyn está aqui, e ele diz que tem uma "
"informação vital sobre como derrotar os mortos-vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:898
msgid "Dacyn?! At last some good news! I thought you were long dead."
msgstr ""
"Dacyn?! Finalmente uma boa nova! Eu achei que você tinha morrido já fazia "
"tempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:902
msgid ""
"He certainly looks half-dead. Dacyn, there is an unholy pall over your skin. "
"Where have you been all this time? We’ve sorely needed your help."
msgstr ""
"Ele certamente parece meio morto. Dacyn, há uma aura profana sobre sua pele. "
"Onde você esteve esse tempo todo? Nós realmente precisávamos de sua ajuda."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:906
msgid ""
"My story and appearance are irrelevant. What matters is that I know how to "
"defeat these invaders. The only path to victory is cutting off the head of "
"the snake. Mal-Ravanal, who you once knew as the mage Ravan, must be "
"destroyed."
msgstr ""
"Minha história e aparência são irrelevantes. O que importa é que sei como "
"derrotar estes invasores. A única forma de vencermos é cortando a cabeça da "
"cobra. Mal-Ravanal, quem um dia você conheceu como mago Ravan, precisa ser "
"destruído."

#. [message]: speaker=Aeraeka
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:910
msgid ""
"You think we haven’t tried?! Our best mages struck down that infernal lich "
"at great cost to their number, but within seconds, Mal-Ravanal had already "
"taken a new body and returned the favor on our ranks. I myself barely made "
"it out alive!"
msgstr ""
"Você pensa que nós não tentamos?! Nossos melhores magos destruíram aquele "
"lich infernal depois de sofrermos pesadas perdas. Mas, em segundos, Mal-"
"Ravanal já tinha conseguido um novo corpo e retornado o favor às nossas "
"fileiras. Eu mesma mal saí viva de lá!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:914
msgid ""
"And that is why my companions and I have spent the past year traveling far "
"to the northeast, seeking (cough) a potent magical amulet that I now "
"possess. If we can destroy the skeletal body, I wield the power to banish "
"the lich’s long-tortured soul. This destruction will be permanent."
msgstr ""
"E é por isso que eu e meus companheiros passamos o ano passado viajando até "
"o extremo nordeste, procurando (tosse) um poderoso amuleto mágico que eu "
"agora possuo. Se conseguirmos destruir o corpo esquelético, poderei banir a "
"alma a muito torturada do lich. Esta destruição será permanente."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:918
msgid ""
"Your Majesty, I have seen this amulet used before. While I cannot attest to "
"its reliability, it is certainly powerful enough to do what Dacyn claims."
msgstr ""
"Vossa Majestade, eu vi este amuleto sendo usado antes. Embora eu não possa "
"corroborar que ele seja confiável, ele certamente é poderoso o suficiente "
"para fazer o que Dacyn diz."

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:922
msgid ""
"Even assuming this magical voodoo works, how do you mean to destroy Mal-"
"Ravanal’s body? The one chance we had was out of the lich’s own arrogance, "
"and even that cost us four of our elite magi under better conditions. Now "
"we’ve been cut off from Dan’Tonk and barely have enough men to hold the "
"walls, much less sortie against the undead."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo que esse vodu mágico funcione, como você pretende destruir o corpo de "
"Mal-Ravanal? A única chance que conseguimos foi causada pela própria "
"arrogância do lich, e mesmo isso custou a vida de quatro dos nossos magos de "
"elite. Agora estamos isolados de Dan'Tonk e mal temos homens o suficiente "
"para defendermos as muralhas, muito menos para atacar os mortos-vivos."

#. [message]: speaker=Aeraeka
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:926
msgid ""
"Truly, have you three not seen the might of the armies encircling Weldyn? It "
"is as if all of the dead warriors from all ages past have come back to "
"attack us. There is no end to the columns of marching skeletons, the wailing "
"ghosts, the infernal bats, the necromancers who raised them..."
msgstr ""
"Sério, vocês três não viram os exércitos cercando Weldyn? É como se todos os "
"guerreiros mortos de todas as épocas tivessem voltado para nos atacar. São "
"intermináveis colunas de esqueletos em marcha, fantasmas agonizantes, "
"morcegos infernais, os necromantes que os reanimaram..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:930
msgid ""
"I pay no heed to the odds! I say we strike at Mal-Ravanal with all the might "
"of Wesnoth. If we assault in force, we can punch through the enemy lines, "
"isolate Mal-Ravanal in the chaos of battle, and blast the lich to oblivion!\n"
"\n"
"I will not let the devastation at the plains be the final legacy of the "
"Clans. We must attack and win back our glory!"
msgstr ""
"Eu não me importo com as chances! Eu digo para atacarmos Mal-Ravanal com "
"tudo que Wesnoth possui. Se atacarmos com força, nós podemos romper as "
"linhas inimigas, isolar Mal-Ravanal no caos da batalha, e mandar o lich ao "
"esquecimento!\n"
"\n"
"Eu não deixarei a devastação das planícies ser o legado final dos Clãs. Nós "
"precisamos atacar e recuperar a nossa glória!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:940
msgid ""
"I have a (cough) superior suggestion. Mal-Ravanal’s armies are vast and "
"unconquerable. Yet the lich alone is not. As a human, Ravan was "
"overconfident to the point of arrogance. I still believe this to be true, if "
"not more so after gaining lichdom. (cough)(cough) If I were to challenge Mal-"
"Ravanal to a duel, I believe they would choose to face me. That would be our "
"opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Tenho uma (tosse) sugestão melhor. Os exércitos de Mal-Ravanal são vastos e "
"inconquistáveis. Porém o lich sozinho não é. Como humano, Ravan era "
"excessivamente confiante ao ponto da arrogância. Ainda acredito que isso "
"seja verdade, se não mais depois de se tornar um lich. (tosse)(tosse) Se eu "
"desafiar Mal-Ravanal para um duelo, acredito que ele tentará me encarar. "
"Esta seria a nossa oportunidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:944
msgid ""
"You call Mal-Ravanal arrogant, yet you seek to face such an overwhelming "
"power in single combat? Even if you could claim victory with that foul "
"amulet of yours, we cannot trust that lich to honor the terms of such a "
"challenge. You would likely find yourself facing their entire army!"
msgstr ""
"Você chama Mal-Ravanal de arrogante, mas você pretende enfrentar alguém tão "
"poderoso em um duelo? Mesmo que você obtenha a vitória com esse seu amuleto "
"maligno, nós não podemos confiar que o lich honraria os termos de tal "
"desafio. Você provavelmente acabaria tendo que enfrentar todo o exército "
"dele!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:948
msgid ""
"We face their entire army regardless. (cough)(cough) The only difference is "
"whether Mal-Ravanal is commanding in the back or gloating in the front."
msgstr ""
"Somos obrigados a enfrentar todo o exército dele de qualquer forma. (tosse)"
"(tosse) A única diferença é se Mal-Ravanal está comandando da retaguarda ou "
"se vangloriando na vanguarda."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:956
msgid ""
"Two risky plans. But the armies surrounding Weldyn grow each day, and we are "
"hard-pressed for options."
msgstr ""
"Dois planos arriscados. Mas os exércitos cercando Weldyn crescem a cada dia, "
"e temos poucas opções."

#. [unit]: id=Halrod, type=General
#. [side]: type=General, id=Halrod
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:963
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:123
msgid "Halrod"
msgstr "Halrod"

#. [unit]: id=Escort, type=Swordsman
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:974
msgid "Escort"
msgstr "Escolta"

#. [message]: speaker=Halrod
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:990
msgid ""
"Sire, we’re under attack! Undead have breached the perimeter earthworks and "
"are massing around the outer villages. I think they mean to storm the moat "
"at nightfall."
msgstr ""
"Meu Senhor, estamos sob ataque! Mortos-vivos romperam o perímetro de "
"fortificações de terra e estão se aglomerando ao redor das aldeias externas. "
"Eu acho que pretendem atacar o fosso ao anoitecer."

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:994
msgid ""
"They attack again so soon?! The few men we have left are in no position to "
"repel a concentrated assault!"
msgstr ""
"Eles já vão atacar novamente?! Os poucos homens que nos restam não estão em "
"condição de repelir um ataque concentrado!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/15_Return_to_Wesnoth.cfg:999
msgid ""
"This is ill news indeed. We will have to cut our council short; Generals, "
"Lieutenant, ready your men!"
msgstr ""
"Essas são más notícias. Teremos que dar por encerrado o concelho por aqui; "
"Generais, Tenente, preparem os seus homens!"

#. [scenario]: id=16_Eleventh_Hour
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:18
msgid "Eleventh Hour"
msgstr "Hora Decisiva"

#. [side]: type=Lich, id=Mal-Xakralan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:715
msgid "Mal-Xakralan"
msgstr "Mal-Xakralan"

#. [unit]: type=Death Knight, id=Nalu-alvan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:723
msgid "Nalu-alvan"
msgstr "Nalu-alvan"

#. [side]: type=Necromancer, id=Mal-Analla, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:755
msgid "Mal-Analla"
msgstr "Mal-Analla"

#. [unit]: type=Necromancer, id=Mal-Saerav
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:863
msgid "Mal-Saerav"
msgstr "Mal-Saerav"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Skraat
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:878
msgid ""
"Gweddry, do you recognize me? Do you remember in the Estmarks, when you "
"mercilessly cut down my defenseless sister? You escaped me once before, but "
"now I will have my revenge!"
msgstr ""
"Gweddry, você me reconhece? Você se lembra das Marcas Orientas, quando você "
"matou sem misericórdia minha irmã indefesa? Você já escapou de mim uma, mas "
"agora eu terei a minha vingança!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Kallat
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:882
msgid ""
"Gweddry, do you recognize me? Do you remember in the Estmarks, when you "
"mercilessly cut down my defenseless brother? I will kill you for what you "
"have done."
msgstr ""
"Gweddry, você me reconhece? Você se lembra das Marcas Orientas, quando você "
"matou sem misericórdia meu irmão indefeso? Eu te matarei pelo que fizeste."

#. [message]: speaker=sibling_corpse
#. Mal-Skraat or Mal-Kallat is still alive, this is their dead brother/sister reanimated as a Soulless
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:887
msgid "Rev... enge..."
msgstr "Vin... gança..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:972
msgid "Garard’s Hold"
msgstr "Forte de Garard"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:973
msgid "Merchants’ Guildhall"
msgstr "Salão da guilda de mercadores"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:974
msgid "Basilica of Li’sar"
msgstr "Basílica de Li'sar"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:975
msgid "Hall of Warriors"
msgstr "Salão dos Guerreiros"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:998
msgid "Survive the undead assault"
msgstr "Sobreviva ao ataque dos mortos-vivos"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1003
msgid "Protect generals Halrad, Halric, and Halrod"
msgstr "Proteja os generais Halrad, Halric e Halrod"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1013
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:134
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:632
msgid "Death of Dacyn"
msgstr "Morte de Dacyn"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1017
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:636
msgid "Death of Konrad II"
msgstr "Morte de Konrad II"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1022
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:641
msgid "Konrad II will not leave the center island."
msgstr "Konrad II não deixará a ilha central."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1025
msgid ""
"Generals will reinforce each bridgehead while they/you have defenders there, "
"falling back to their castle otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Generais irão reforçar cada uma das cabeças de ponte se houverem defensores "
"lá. Caso contrário, retornarão para seus castelos."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1028
msgid ""
"If you decide not to duel Mal-Ravanal, surviving generals will aid you in "
"the next scenario."
msgstr ""
"Se você decidir não duelar com Mal-Ravanal, os generais sobreviventes irão "
"se juntar a você no próximo cenário."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1052
msgid ""
"Undead approach at the northern crossings. My forces are in position to "
"engage the invaders."
msgstr ""
"Mortos-vivos se aproximam das travessias do norte. Minhas forças estão em "
"posição para interceptar os invasores."

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1057
msgid "The southeastern bridges are secure; hostiles inbound."
msgstr "As pontes ao sudeste estão seguras; inimigos se aproximam."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrod
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1062
msgid ""
"My fortifications are manned and ready. Brace for attack from the southwest."
msgstr ""
"Minhas fortificações estão guarnecidas e prontas. Preparem-se para um ataque "
"chegando do sudoeste."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1095
msgid "Night approaches, and with it the undead hordes. I stand ready."
msgstr ""
"A noite se aproxima, e com ela as horas de mortos-vivos. Eu estou pronto."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1099
msgid "Let us show these undead the might of Wesnoth!"
msgstr "Vamos mostrar a estes mortos-vivos o poder de Wesnoth!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1103
msgid ""
"And so it comes to this, here at what seems the end of days. Prepare for "
"battle!"
msgstr ""
"E então é chegada a hora, aqui onde parece ser o final dos tempos. Preparem-"
"se para a batalha!"

#. [message]: speaker=Yannic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1149
msgid ""
"So it is true, Owaec and Gweddry survived! When your forces had not returned "
"to Wesnoth by winter I feared the worst. I am relieved to see you alive and "
"well! This is the first good news I’ve heard of the war in quite some time."
msgstr ""
"Então é verdade, Owaec e Gweddry sobreviveram! Quando suas forças não "
"retornaram para Wesnoth no inverno, eu temi o pior. Estou aliviado em vê-los "
"sãos e salvos! Esta é a primeira boa notícia que ouço sobre a guerra em "
"algum tempo."

#. [message]: speaker=Yannic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1153
msgid ""
"I’m afraid my Soradoc company was nearly wiped out in the massacre at the "
"Plains, but the few of us who remain place ourselves at your service!"
msgstr ""
"Temo que minha companhia de Soradoc foi quase exterminada por completo no "
"massacre das Planícies, mas os poucos de nós que sobraram estão ao seu "
"serviço!"

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1257
msgid ""
"So this is Weldyn? Didn’t know cities got this big. Never thought I’d end up "
"fightin’ here, of all places."
msgstr ""
"Então, esta é Weldyn? Não sabia que cidades podiam ser tão grandes. Nunca "
"pensei que acabaria lutando aqui, de todos os lugares."

#. [message]: speaker=Mel Guthrak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1269
msgid ""
"Gaennell, you traitor! <b>I</b> am your master, not some petty king of men. "
"Return to me and face your punishment."
msgstr ""
"Gaennell, seu traidor! <b>Eu</b> sou seu mestre, não um insignificante rei "
"de humanos. Retorne a mim e enfrente sua punição."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1273
msgid ""
"You tried to have me killed over a petty accident! I’m not going to grovel "
"at your feet and suffer your abuse any more."
msgstr ""
"Você tentou me matar por causa de um pequeno acidente! Eu não vou mais me "
"humilhar aos seus pés e nem suportar os seus abusos."

#. [message]: speaker=Yannic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1285
msgid "For my fallen brothers at Soradoc and the Plains!"
msgstr "Pelos meus irmãos caídos em Soradoc e nas Planícies!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1307
msgid ""
"My legacy will not be one of failure! With all the might of the throne of "
"Wesnoth, I will strike you down!"
msgstr ""
"Meu legado não será um de falha! Com todo o poder do trono de Wesnoth, eu "
"aniquilarei você!"

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#. one of the AI generals when the player takes their village
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1334
msgid ""
"Sire, you are of course welcome to capture any of my villages if you need "
"them, but please know that it will make it more difficult to heal my injured "
"soldiers."
msgstr ""
"Senhor, você certamente é bem vindo para capturar qualquer aldeia minha que "
"precise, mas, por favor, saiba que isso dificultará que os meus soldados "
"feridos sejam curados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. "light of dawn" is merely because it's that time of day
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1357
msgid ""
"Stand strong, men of Wesnoth! Rally under the light of dawn, and drive the "
"undead back!"
msgstr ""
"Permaneçam fortes, homens de Wesnoth! Reúnam-se sob a luz da aurora e "
"expulsem os mortos-vivos!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1369
msgid "Oh hello, am I interrupting something?"
msgstr "Olá, estou interrompendo algo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#. according to the turn counter, it's dawn; Mal-Ravanal is claiming to be able to control that
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1374
msgid ""
"It’s been fun watching this little squabble unfold, but it’s time to move "
"things along. Night will now fall, and the city with it."
msgstr ""
"Foi divertido ver essa brincadeira, mas está na hora de avançarmos para o "
"próximo ato. Agora a noite cai, e com ela a cidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1380
msgid "Not if I stop you first! I defeated you before, and I will do so again!"
msgstr ""
"Não se eu te parar primeiro! Eu te derrotei antes, e eu farei novamente!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1406
msgid ""
"Ah Dacyn, picked up a few tricks, have we? But your understanding is a bit "
"shallow. Observe how it is done."
msgstr ""
"Ah Dacyn, você aprendeu alguns truques novos, não é? Mas seu entendimento é "
"um tanto raso. Observe como se faz."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1410
msgid ""
"Bleed black, the fabric of firmament.\n"
"Open wide, the maw of the darkness between worlds.\n"
"Swallow the day and swallow the sun,\n"
"And leave eternal night to remain."
msgstr ""
"Sangre escuro, o tecido do firmamento.\n"
"Abra grande, a boca da escuridão entre mundos.\n"
"Engula o dia e engula o sol,\n"
"E deixa a eterna noite permanecer."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1491
msgid "Dark scary! Not like!"
msgstr "Escuro dá medo! Não gostei!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1495
msgid "What manner o’ dark sorcery be this?"
msgstr "Que tipo de maxia negra é esta?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. as well as changing the time-of-day schedule, fog of war has just been enabled
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1506
msgid ""
"I’m nearly blind in this fog, but I think the undead have been reinforced!"
msgstr ""
"Estou quase cego nesta névoa, mas acho que os mortos-vivos foram reforçados!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1518
msgid ""
"This cursed fog has clouded my sight, but I think I hear the sounds of "
"reinforcing undead!"
msgstr ""
"Esta névoa amaldiçoada atrapalha minha visão, mas acho que ouvi o som de "
"mortos-vivos se aproximando!"

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1525
msgid "Look sharp; they’re reinforcing under the cover of fog."
msgstr "Fiquem atentos; eles estão se reforçando sob a cobertura do nevoeiro."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1533
msgid "By the light of all that is holy, we must not fail!"
msgstr "Pela luz de tudo que é sagrado, nós não devemos falhar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. speaker is one of the voices from the amulet, speaking to Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1558
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<span size='small' font-style='italic'>You see? Mal-Ravanal has grown too "
#| "powerful. Wesnoth is helpless!</span>"
msgid "You see? Mal-Ravanal has grown too powerful. Wesnoth is helpless!"
msgstr ""
"<span size='small' font-style='italic'>Vê só? Mal-Ravanal se tornou poderoso "
"demais. Wesnoth está acabada!</span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. speaker is one of the voices from the amulet, speaking to Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1566
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "<span size='small' font-style='italic'>Use the Amulet. There is no other "
#| "way! Use us!</span>"
msgid "Use the Amulet. There is no other way! Use us!"
msgstr ""
"<span size='small' font-style='italic'>Use o amuleto. Não há outro jeito! "
"Nos use!</span>"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. after this, Dacyn gets unpoisonable, undrainable, unplagueable and changes to a Fallen Mage
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1571
msgid ""
"I must... defeat Ravan! I must be strong enough to stand alone... I alone "
"must wield this fullness of power!"
msgstr ""
"Eu preciso... derrotar Ravan! Eu preciso ser forte o suficiente para lutar "
"sozinho... Apenas eu posso utilizar todo esse poder!"

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1630
msgid "Careful! They’re regrouping for another wave."
msgstr "Cuidado! Eles estão se reagrupando para outro ataque."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1671
msgid ""
"The first rays of the blessed dawn pierce through the fog! The lich’s foul "
"spell begins to fail!"
msgstr ""
"Os primeiros raios da aurora abençoada perfuraram a névoa! O feitiço maligno "
"do lich começa a falhar!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1683
msgid ""
"Take heart, for victory is near at hand! The first rays of sunlight have "
"pierced through Mal-Ravanal’s night fog."
msgstr ""
"Tenham coragem, pois a vitória está próxima! Os primeiros raios de sol "
"perfuraram a névoa noturna de Mal-Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1695
msgid ""
"Look, the first rays of sunlight have pierced through the fog! Mal-Ravanal’s "
"spell has begun to fail. I only wish Owaec were here to see it..."
msgstr ""
"Vejam, os primeiros raios do sol perfuram a neblina! O feitiço de Mal-"
"Ravanal começou a enfraquecer. Eu apenas queria que Owaec estivesse aqui "
"para ver isso..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. Gweddry and Owaec are dead during this scenario, and Terraent isn't here either
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1702
msgid ""
"The sun has pierced through the night’s fog; Mal-Ravanal’s spell begins to "
"wane. I need neither Gweddry nor Owaec. I will finish this battle on my own."
msgstr ""
"O sol perfurou as névoa da noite; o feitiço de Mal-Ravanal começou a "
"enfraquecer. Não preciso nem de Gweddry nem de Owaec. Finalizarei está "
"batalha por conta própria."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#. any undead unit from side 5 (except the leader) that was within 3 hexes of a living unit has died
#. followed immediately after this line by similar for sides 6 and 7.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1740
msgid ""
"Mal-Ravanal’s necromancers have overexerted themselves. They are struggling "
"to maintain all their minions."
msgstr ""
"Os necromantes de Mal-Ravanal se esforçaram demais. Eles estão com "
"dificuldade para manter todos os seus lacaios."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1781
msgid "The undead are falling back! Thank the Light; it’s finally over."
msgstr "Os mortos-vivos estão recuando! Graças à Luz; finalmente acabou."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1793
msgid "Gweddry has not died in vain; the undead resolve is broken!"
msgstr ""
"Gweddry não morreu em vão; a determinação dos mortos-vivos foi quebrada!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1799
msgid "At last, the undead end their assault."
msgstr "Finalmente, os mortos-vivos terminaram seu ataque."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. the scenario doesn't let the player move Konrad away from his castle
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1835
msgid "I will not abandon my post!"
msgstr "Eu não abandonarei meu posto!"

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. plaque on a statue
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1852
msgid "<i>Haldric the First, Dragonslayer, first king of Wesnoth.</i>"
msgstr ""
"<i>Haldric o Primeiro, Matador de Dragões, primeiro rei de Wesnoth.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1857
msgid ""
"My father was named after him, and the royal sceptre hails from his line. "
"Sadly, the histories say that he became paranoid in his old age."
msgstr ""
"Meu pai foi nomeado em homenagem a ele, e o cetro real vem de sua linhagem. "
"Infelizmente, as histórias dizem que ele se tornou paranoico quando velho."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#. plaque on a statue
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1869
msgid "<i>Delfador the Great, sage of Wesnoth, restorer of the throne.</i>"
msgstr "<i>Delfador o Grande, sábio de Wesnoth, restaurador do trono.</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1874
msgid "My predecessor, ‘the Great’. I intend to be greater."
msgstr "Meu antecessor, \"o Grande\". Pretendo ser maior."

#. [message]: speaker=Mel Guthrak
#. last breath of Mel Guthrak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1887
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Wha- but how?"
msgid "Wha— but how?"
msgstr "O qu- mas como?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#. last breath of Mel Guthrak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1892
msgid "Good riddance..."
msgstr "Já vai tarde..."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrod
#. [message]: speaker=Halrad
#. last breath of Mel Guthrak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1897
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1939
msgid "Impressive tactics! I’ll begin redeploying towards other threats."
msgstr ""
"Táticas impressionantes! Eu começarei a enviar as tropas para outras ameaças."

#. [message]: speaker=Nakeg-alvan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1907
msgid "You waste... your effort..."
msgstr "Você desperdiça... o seu esforço..."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrod
#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1911
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1949
msgid ""
"Well done! This will free my soldiers to defend other sectors of the city."
msgstr ""
"Bom trabalho! Isto liberará meus soldados para defender outras partes da "
"cidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Nalu-alvan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1921
msgid "Your victory... is meaningless..."
msgstr "Sua vitória... não importa..."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrad
#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1925
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1963
msgid "Excellent work! I’ll send my soldiers to the other fronts."
msgstr "Ótimo trabalho! Eu enviarei meus soldados para outras frentes."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Xakralan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1935
msgid "Mal-Ravanal will make you suffer for this!"
msgstr "Mal-Ravanal fará você sofrer por conta disso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Analla
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1959
msgid "No! I was supposed to... become immortal..."
msgstr "Não! Era para eu... me tornar imortal..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1975
msgid "No! Now I will never have my revenge..."
msgstr "Não! Agora eu nunca terei minha vingança..."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. last breath of the reanimated (Soulless) Mal-Skraat or Mal-Kallat
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:1986
msgid "Gruhhh..."
msgstr "Gruhhh..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2032
msgid ""
"Huzzah! Even Mal-Ravanal’s infernal darkness could not dim the spirits of "
"our men! My friends, we have won a great victory today."
msgstr ""
"Viva! Mesmo a escuridão infernal de Mal-Ravanal não pôde apagar o ânimo dos "
"nossos homens! Meus amigos, conseguimos uma grande vitória hoje."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2036
msgid ""
"Now we must press our advantage! Let us strike the undead while they are in "
"disarray and banish Mal-Ravanal’s dark soul once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"Agora devemos usar nossa vantagem! Vamos atacar os mortos-vivos enquanto "
"eles estão desorganizados e banir a alma sombria de Mal-Ravanal de uma vez "
"por todas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2040
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2098
msgid ""
"I will not put the fate of all Irdya in the hands of a vengeful Clansman and "
"Weldyn’s tattered armies. I must face Mal-Ravanal in a duel, and I must be "
"the one to strike the infernal lich down! I will trust none other than "
"myself with such responsibility."
msgstr ""
"Eu não colocarei o destino de toda Irdya nas mãos de um membro do Clã "
"vingativo e dos exércitos maltrapilhos de Weldyn. Devo enfrentar Mal-Ravanal "
"em um duelo, e devo ser quem derrotará o lich infernal! Eu não confiarei em "
"mais ninguém além de mim mesmo com tamanha responsabilidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2044
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2165
msgid ""
"Both of you alike speak wisdom. This is a difficult decision, and I have "
"little time in which to make it."
msgstr ""
"Ambos falam com sabedoria. Esta é uma decisão difícil, e eu tenho pouco "
"tempo para tomá-la."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2048
msgid ""
"Lieutenant Gweddry, you are familiar with the situation, and you know both "
"Owaec and Dacyn well. Whose plan do you suggest I follow?"
msgstr ""
"Tenente Gweddry, você é familiar com essta situação, e conheces bem tanto "
"Owaec quanto Dacyn. Qual plano sugeres que eu siga?"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2052
msgid "I think we should..."
msgstr "Acho que devemos..."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2054
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2108
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2171
msgid "challenge Mal-Ravanal to a duel. <i>(normal)</i>"
msgstr "desafiar Mal-Ravanal para um duelo. <i>(normal)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2058
msgid "I agree. Dacyn, send the message at once."
msgstr "Eu concordo. Dacyn, envie a mensagem de imediato."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2068
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2122
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2185
msgid "defeat Mal-Ravanal in pitched battle. <i>(challenging)</i>"
msgstr "derrotar Mal-Ravanal em uma batalha campal. <i>(desafiador)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2072
msgid "I agree. Owaec, begin preparing our armies."
msgstr "Eu concordo. Owaec, comece a preparar nosso exército."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2090
msgid ""
"Huzzah! Even Mal-Ravanal’s infernal darkness could not dim the spirits of "
"our men! My friends, we have won a great victory today. Alas, if only "
"Gweddry were here..."
msgstr ""
"Viva! Mesmo a escuridão infernal de Mal-Ravanal não pôde apagar o ânimo dos "
"nossos homens! Meus amigos, conseguimos uma grande vitória hoje. Ah, se ao "
"menos Gweddry estivesse aqui..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2094
msgid ""
"... I am certain he would tell us to muster our resolve and regroup to press "
"our advantage! Let us strike the undead while they are in disarray and "
"banish Mal-Ravanal’s dark soul once and for all!"
msgstr ""
"... Eu tenho certeza que ele diria para nós reunirmos nossa determinação e "
"nos reagrupar para fazer uso de nossa vantagem! Vamos atacar os mortos-vivos "
"enquanto eles estão desorganizados e banir a alma sombria de Mal-Ravanal de "
"uma vez por todas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2102
msgid ""
"Both of you alike speak wisdom. This is a difficult decision, and I have "
"little time in which to make it. I wish that Gweddry still lived to advise "
"me, but it seems I must decide on my own."
msgstr ""
"Ambos falam com sabedoria. Esta é uma decisão difícil, e eu tenho pouco "
"tempo para tomá-la. Eu gostaria que Gweddry ainda estivesse vivo para me "
"ajudar, mas parece que tenho que decidir por conta própria."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2106
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2169
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2223
msgid "By my command, we will..."
msgstr "Pelo meu comando, nós iremos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2112
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2175
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2229
msgid "Excellent, I will send the message at once."
msgstr "Excelente, enviarei a mensagem de imediato."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2126
msgid "Excellent, I will begin preparing our armies!"
msgstr "Excelente, irei começar a preparar as tropas!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. although there's a lot of dead troops, this is mainly "to mourn for Owaec"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2153
msgid ""
"The city grows still at last. I wish there was time to mourn, but we still "
"must decide how to deal with Mal-Ravanal."
msgstr ""
"A cidade finalmente caiu em silêncio. Eu gostaria que houvesse tempo para "
"lamentar pelos que se foram, mas ainda tenho que decidir como lidar com Mal-"
"Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2157
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2211
msgid ""
"Owaec had wished for us to strike at the undead and isolate Mal-Ravanal by "
"force of arms. With their armies in disarray after the failed attack on "
"Weldyn, this may be our best opportunity."
msgstr ""
"Owaec desejava que atacássemos os mortos-vivos e isolássemos Mal-Ravanal "
"pela força das armas. Com seus exércitos desorganizados após falharem no "
"ataque contra Weldyn, essa talvez seja nossa melhor oportunidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2161
msgid ""
"I will not put the fate of all Irdya in the hands of Weldyn’s feeble "
"defenders! I must face Mal-Ravanal in a duel, and I must be the one to "
"strike the infernal lich down! I will trust none other than myself with such "
"responsibility."
msgstr ""
"Eu não colocarei o destino de toda Irdya nas mãos dos débeis defensores de "
"Weldyn! Eu devo enfrentar Mal-Ravanal em um duelo, e será eu quem derrotará "
"o lich infernal! Eu não confiarei em mais ninguém com tamanha "
"responsabilidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2189
msgid "I will begin preparing our armies."
msgstr "Irei preparar as tropas."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2207
msgid ""
"The city grows still at last. This battle is won, but with our best "
"commanders dead we have little hope of surviving another attack."
msgstr ""
"A cidade finalmente caiu em silêncio. Esta batalha foi ganha, mas com nossos "
"melhores comandantes mortos as chances são baixas de sobrevivermos a outro "
"ataque."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2215
msgid ""
"We cannot put the fate of all Irdya in the hands of Weldyn’s feeble "
"defenders! I must face Mal-Ravanal in a duel, and I must be the one to "
"strike the infernal lich down! I will trust none other than myself with such "
"responsibility."
msgstr ""
"Nós não podemos colocar o destino de toda Irdya nas mãos dos débeis "
"defensores de Weldyn! Devo enfrentar Mal-Ravanal em um duelo, e deve ser "
"quem derrotará o lich infernal! Eu não confiarei em ninguém além de mim "
"mesmo com tamanha responsabilidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2219
msgid ""
"This is a difficult decision, and I have little time in which to make it. I "
"wish that Gweddry or Owaec still lived to advise me, but it seems I must "
"decide on my own."
msgstr ""
"Essa é uma decisão difícil, e eu tenho pouco tempo para tomá-la. Eu gostaria "
"que Gweddry ou Owaec ainda estivessem vivos para me aconselhar, mas parece "
"que tenho que decidir por conta própria."

#. [option]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2225
msgid "challenge Mal-Ravanal to a duel. <i>(regular)</i>"
msgstr "desafiar Mal-Ravanal para um duelo. <i>(regular)</i>"

#. [option]
#. both Gweddry and Owaec are dead, so this goes from "challenging" to "very hard"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2240
msgid "defeat Mal-Ravanal in pitched battle. <i>(very hard)</i>"
msgstr "derrotar Mal-Ravanal para uma batalha campal. <i>(muito difícil)</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/16_Eleventh_Hour.cfg:2244
msgid "This is an unwise decision, but I will aid our armies as best I can."
msgstr ""
"Esta decisão não é sábia, mas eu ajudarei nossos exércitos o melhor que "
"posso."

#. [scenario]: id=17a_The_Duel
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:4
msgid "The Duel"
msgstr "O Duelo"

#. [part]
#. a human messenger
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:25
msgid ""
"As the messenger passed out of the city gates, silence settled over the "
"valley of the Weldyn. Children buried their fathers, mothers entombed their "
"sons; soldiers slept where they stood, spears still clutched behind pale "
"knuckles. The only sound was the incessant drum-march of skeletal feet, ever-"
"growing outside the walls."
msgstr ""
"Assim que o mensageiro saiu pelos portões da cidade, o silêncio se instalou "
"no vale de Weldyn. Crianças enterravam seus pais, mães sepultavam seus "
"filhos; soldados dormiram onde estavam, lanças ainda agarradas atrás dos nós "
"dos dedos pálidos. O único som era a incessante marcha de pés esqueléticos, "
"sempre aumentando de intensidade do lado de fora das muralhas."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Finally, the gates creaked open once again. Eyes looked on, eager, anxious, "
"terrified, as the messenger rode toward the castle..."
msgstr ""
"Finalmente, os portões rangeram ao serem abertos novamente. Olhos observaram "
"ansiosos, apreensivos e aterrorizados, enquanto o mensageiro se dirigia em "
"direção ao castelo..."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:33
msgid ""
"News spread quickly. Mal-Ravanal had accepted the challenge. Dacyn and six "
"of Weldyn’s finest were to duel the lich in the abandoned catacombs under "
"the city..."
msgstr ""
"As novidades se espalharam depressa. Mal-Ravanal aceitou o desafio. Dacyn e "
"seis dos melhores de Weldyn iriam duelar com o lich nas catacumbas "
"abandonadas debaixo da cidade..."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:130
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:623
msgid "Defeat Mal-Ravanal"
msgstr "Derrote Mal-Ravanal"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:169
msgid "Dacyn, I’m surprised you came. I remember you being smarter than that!"
msgstr ""
"Dacyn, estou surpreso que veio. Me lembrava de você ser mais esperto do que "
"isso!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:173
msgid ""
"I and I alone will put an end to your foul machinations! You have grown "
"strong in the darkness, but I have become stronger (cough)(cough) still!"
msgstr ""
"Eu, e somente eu, botarei um fim nas suas maquinações diabólicas! Você ficou "
"mais forte nas trevas, mas eu me tornei ainda (tosse)(tosse) mais forte!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:177
msgid ""
"A-ha haha! And how exactly do you plan to do that? Come now, you must know "
"that you’re outmatched."
msgstr ""
"A-ha haha! E como exatamente você planeja fazer isso? Vamos, você deve saber "
"que está em desvantagem."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:191
msgid ""
"The rules of the duel are these:\n"
"You may recruit or recall up to 6 units.\n"
"At the end of your first turn, your keep will disappear, and you must battle "
"with whatever troops you have at that time."
msgstr ""
"Estas são as regras do duelo:\n"
"Você pode recrutar ou convocar até 6 unidades.\n"
"No final do seu primeiro turno, sua torre de menagem desaparecerá e você "
"lutará com quaisquer tropas que tiver quando isto acontecer."

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:294
msgid ""
"Wait — what just happened? More undead creatures just came out of the "
"ground! That’s not allowed!"
msgstr ""
"Espere — O que é isso? Mais mortos-vivos saíram do chão! Isso é contra as "
"regras!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:298
msgid ""
"The rules say nothing about bringing up warriors who were already here. Feel "
"free to reanimate some too, if you can."
msgstr ""
"As regras não dizem nada sobre trazer de volta a vida soldados que já "
"estavam aqui. Fique a vontade para reanimar alguns também, se for capaz."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:306
msgid "Tsk, tsk, I begin to tire of this."
msgstr "Tsc, tsc, estou começando a me cansar disto."

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17a_The_Duel.cfg:311
msgid "More reinforcements come every time!"
msgstr "Mais reforços continuando vindo!"

#. [scenario]: id=17b_All-In
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:11
msgid "All-In"
msgstr "Tudo ou Nada"

#. [part]
#. the river has the same name as the city
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:28
msgid ""
"The morning sun shone bright upon the valley of the Weldyn, glinting off "
"swords and lances innumerable, arrayed in tight formation inside the city "
"walls."
msgstr ""
"O sol da manhã brilhava forte sobre o vale de Weldyn, brilhando sobre "
"inumeráveis espadas e lanças, dispostas em formação cerrada dentro das "
"muralhas da cidade."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:32
msgid ""
"From the ranks of Wesnoth’s finest arose a cry, soft at first but then "
"mounting in volume, a cry of desperate hope, a cry of fiery purpose and icy "
"will."
msgstr ""
"Das fileiras dos melhores de Wesnoth surgiu um grito, suave a princípio, mas "
"que logo aumentou de volume, um grito de esperança, um grito de propósito "
"ardente e vontade gélida."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:37
msgid ""
"The horns sounded, the gates swung open, and from inside the city spilled "
"forth Weldyn’s last gasp."
msgstr ""
"As trombetas soaram, os portões foram abertos, e de dentro da cidade saiu o "
"último suspiro de Weldyn."

#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich2
#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich3
#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich4
#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich5
#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich6
#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich7
#. [leader]: type=Lich, id=Lich8
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:99
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:117
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:138
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:158
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:178
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:200
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:219
msgid "?"
msgstr "?"

#. [side]: type=Dark Adept, id=Lethin
#. in the unlikely event that Mal-Tar survived S03, Lethin gets renamed and has dialogue as Mal-Tar
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:315
msgid "Lethin"
msgstr "Lethin"

#. [unit]: type=Dark Adept, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:335
msgid "Rerivyan"
msgstr "Rerivyan"

#. [unit]: type=Dark Adept, gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:346
msgid "Vowyn"
msgstr "Vowyn"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. last breath for Mal-Tar
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:375
msgid "Wait, wait, stop, I surrender! I know your leader Gweddry!"
msgstr "Espere, espere, pare, eu me rendo! Eu conheço o seu líder Gweddry!"

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#. last breath for Mal-Tar
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:380
msgid ""
"He defeated me back in the Estmarks but still let me live! Let me go and I "
"promise you’ll never see me again!"
msgstr ""
"Ele me derrotou lá nas Marcas Orientais e ainda assim me deixou viver! Me "
"deixe ir e eu prometo que vocês nunca mais me verão!"

#. [message]: speaker=second_unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:384
msgid "Well, okay I guess..."
msgstr "Bem, ok eu acho..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. speaking of Mal-Tar
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:391
msgid ""
"It’s been an entire war, and that guy still hasn’t improved his magic..."
msgstr ""
"Estamos no final de uma guerra, e aquele garoto ainda não melhorou sua "
"mágica..."

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:612
msgid "Kill $liches_to_kill liches to reveal Mal-Ravanal"
msgstr "Mate $liches_to_kill liches para revelar Mal-Ravanal"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:719
msgid "150 gold remains in my war-chest. I place it at your service, my Liege."
msgstr ""
"150 peças de ouro permanecem no meu fundo de batalha. Eu as coloco a seu "
"serviço, meu Soberano."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:755
msgid ""
"My Liege, I’ve managed to conserve 150 gold from the previous battle. I "
"place it at your disposal."
msgstr ""
"Meu Soberano, eu consegui preservar 150 peças de ouro da batalha anterior. "
"Eu as coloco à sua disposição."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:793
msgid ""
"For you, my Liege: my men have salvaged 150 gold from the ruins of the city "
"outskirts."
msgstr ""
"Para você, meu Soberano: meus homens recuperaram 150 peças de ouro das "
"ruínas ao redor da cidade."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:843
msgid "My forces are in position at the northern wall; awaiting your orders."
msgstr ""
"Minhas forças estão em posição na muralha norte; esperando por suas ordens."

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:847
msgid "Eastern flank reclaimed. I stand ready to launch the assault."
msgstr "Flanco leste reconquistado. Estou pronto para lançar o ataque."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrod
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:851
msgid "The western barricades are manned and ready — it’s payback time."
msgstr ""
"As barricadas ocidentais estão guarnecidas e prontas — está na hora do "
"acerto de contas."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:861
msgid ""
"Now is the time to strike! In the name of the Clans, Mal-Ravanal will be "
"ended this day!"
msgstr ""
"Agora é a hora de atacar! Em nome dos Clãs, Mal-Ravanal cairá neste dia!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:868
msgid ""
"Now is the time to strike! By the might of all Wesnoth, Mal-Ravanal shall be "
"ended this day!"
msgstr ""
"Agora é a hora de atacar! Pelo poder de toda a Wesnoth, Mal-Ravanal cairá "
"neste dia!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:895
msgid ""
"These liches are channeling some dark magic to hide themselves. (cough)"
"(cough) Even if Mal-Ravanal is here, I will not be able to (cough) reveal "
"them until we have killed enough of these liches to break their spell. "
"(cough)"
msgstr ""
"Esses liches estão canalizando algum tipo de magia negra para se esconderem. "
"(tosse)(tosse) Mesmo que Mal-Ravanal esteja aqui, eu não serei capaz de "
"(tosse) revelar ele até termos matado o suficiente destes liches para "
"quebrar o seu feitiço. (tosse)"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:906
msgid ""
"Then that’s what we’ll have to do. And we will have to do it quickly, before "
"Mal-Ravanal’s reinforcing armies overwhelm us."
msgstr ""
"Então isto é o que temos que fazer. E teremos que fazer rápido, antes que os "
"reforços de Mal-Ravanal nos sobrepujem."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:910
msgid ""
"Stride fearless upon the plain of battle, for today we reclaim our legacy! "
"For Wesnoth!!"
msgstr ""
"Ataquem sem medo sobre o campo de batalha, pois hoje reivindicamos o nosso "
"legado! Por Wesnoth!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:917
msgid ""
"Then kill them we shall. Stride fearless upon the plain of battle, for today "
"we reclaim our legacy! For Wesnoth!!"
msgstr ""
"Então mataremos todos eles. Ataquem sem medo sobre o campo de batalha, pois "
"hoje reivindicamos o nosso legado! Por Wesnoth!!"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:926
msgid "Mal-Hadanak"
msgstr "Mal-Hadanak"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:927
msgid "You dare to attack me?"
msgstr "Você ousa me atacar?"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:930
msgid "Mal-Katklagad"
msgstr "Mal-Katklagad"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:931
msgid "I will enjoy watching you suffer!"
msgstr "Terei prazer em ver você sofrer!"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:934
msgid "Mal-Xaskanat"
msgstr "Mal-Xaskanat"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:935
msgid "Death will only be the beginning of your torment!"
msgstr "A morte será apenas o começo do seu tormento!"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:938
msgid "Mal-Akranbral"
msgstr "Mal-Akranbral"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:939
msgid "You will serve me in death!"
msgstr "Você me servirá em morte!"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:942
msgid "Mal-Larakan"
msgstr "Mal-Larakan"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:943
msgid "Allow me to free you from your wretched existence!"
msgstr "Eu te libertarei de sua miserável existência!"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:946
msgid "Mal-Drakanal"
msgstr "Mal-Drakanal"

#. [value]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:947
msgid "I am merely toying with you!"
msgstr "Você não passa de um brinquedo para mim!"

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:992
msgid ""
"The River Weldyn used to be so beautiful, before the undead dammed it and "
"flooded the shores..."
msgstr ""
"O Rio Weldyn costumava ser tão bonito, antes de os mortos-vivos o "
"represassem e inundarem suas margens..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1016
msgid ""
"My legacy will not be one of failure! With all the might of the throne of "
"Wesnoth, I shall strike you down!"
msgstr ""
"Meu legado não será um de fracasso! Como todo o poder do trono de Wesnoth, "
"eu acabarei com você!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. killed a lich
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1037
msgid ""
"That’s one down! The undead must still be in disarray after their failed "
"attack during the long night."
msgstr ""
"Um foi derrubado! Os mortos-vivos ainda devem estar desorganizados depois do "
"fracasso que foi o seu ataque durante a longa noite."

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#. speaker is a random lich
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1051
msgid ""
"Night falls on Weldyn! Your counterattack may have caught us by surprise, "
"but this hour is our domain."
msgstr ""
"A noite cai sobre Weldyn! Seu contra-ataque pode nos ter pego de surpresa, "
"mas essa hora é o nosso domínio."

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#. speaker is a random lich, almost certainly a different one than the previous speaker
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1060
msgid "Now you will pay for your arrogance!"
msgstr "Você pagará pela sua arrogância!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. the player is trying to move him away
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1082
msgid "A king belongs in his capital! I will not abandon my post!"
msgstr "Um rei deve permanecer na sua capital! Eu não abandonarei meu posto!"

#. [floating_text]
#. the parts to translate here are "gold refunded" and "per side"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1214
msgid ""
"<span color='#FFD700' size='x-small'>gold refunded</span>\n"
"<span color='#FFFFFF' size='xx-small'>  (1/$side_count per side)</span>"
msgstr ""
"<span color='#FFD700' size='x-small'>ouro reembolsado</span>\n"
"<span color='#FFFFFF' size='xx-small'>  (1/$side_count por lado)</span>"

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1243
msgid ""
"Fools, you have already lost! For each minion you strike down, another shall "
"rise to take its place."
msgstr ""
"Tolos, vocês já perderam! Para cada lacaio que vocês derrubam, outro se "
"levanta para ocupar o seu lugar."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1385
msgid "Their spell is broken!"
msgstr "A magia dele foi desfeita!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/17b_All-In.cfg:1677
msgid "Enough of this farce! I shall end this personally."
msgstr "Chega desta farsa! Eu acabarei com isto pessoalmente."

#. [scenario]: id=18_Epilogue
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:4
msgid "Epilogue"
msgstr "Epílogo"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:18
msgid ""
"When Mal-Ravanal fell, the undead army collapsed like puppets with cut "
"strings. The invading necromancers looked on in horror, unable to comprehend "
"what had happened."
msgstr ""
"Quando Mal-Ravanal caiu, os exércitos mortos-vivos caíram como bonecos que "
"tem seus fios cortados. Os necromantes invasores olharam com horror, "
"incapazes de compreender o que tinha acontecido."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:21
msgid ""
"Yet even as the lich’s body crumbled, for a moment’s breath, the onlookers "
"saw a vast and louring column of shadow arise like smoke from an unclean "
"fire. It divided fivefold at its height, reaching for the heavens like a "
"clutching hand. Men let weapons fall from nerveless fingers and horses "
"reared in terror as that great dark pall obscured the sun..."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo enquanto o corpo do lich se desfazia, momentaneamente, os espectadores "
"viram uma vasta e ameaçadora coluna de sombras emergir como fumaça de um "
"fogo impuro. Ela então se dividiu em cinco partes na sua parte mais alta, "
"esticando-se para cima como uma mão em forma de garra. Soldados deixavam as "
"armas tombarem de suas mãos sem força e cavalos empinavam de terror enquanto "
"aquela grande mortalha negra obscurecia o sol..."

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:24
msgid ""
"... and then it thinned, and paled, and a breeze from the west dissolved it "
"in tatters, and the light of day shone once again undiminished on Weldyn."
msgstr ""
"... e então ela tornou-se mais fina, e pálida, e uma brisa vinda do oeste "
"dissolveu-a por completo, e a luz do dia brilhou novamente tão forte quanto "
"sempre sobre Weldyn."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:113
msgid "Renaerawan"
msgstr "Renaerawan"

#. [message]: speaker=Renaerawan
#. the speaker is a white mage who first appears in this epilogue
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:198
msgid ""
"We are gathered here today in remembrance of our dear colleague and friend, "
"Dacyn, who fell even as he vanquished the arch-lich Mal-Ravanal."
msgstr ""
"Nós estamos reunidos aqui hoje em memória de nosso querido colega e amigo, "
"Dacyn, que caiu em batalha ao derrotar o Arquilich Mal-Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Renaerawan
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:202
msgid ""
"I knew Dacyn as a complicated man: ambitious yet loyal, proud yet wise. But "
"above all, Dacyn sought to act for the good of Wesnoth, and today we honor "
"him for that."
msgstr ""
"Eu conhecia Dacyn como um homem complicado: ambicioso, porém leal; "
"orgulhoso, porém sábio. Mas, acima de tudo, Dacyn buscou agir pelo bem de "
"Wesnoth, e hoje nós o honramos por isso."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:208
msgid "Today we have won a great victory, yet it comes at great cost."
msgstr ""
"Hoje nós conquistamos uma grande vitória, ainda que ela tenha custado caro."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:212
msgid "Grug sad! Magic man kind."
msgstr "Grug triste! Homem mágico gentil."

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:216
msgid ""
"Ay. Too many ha’ died in this war, both my kinsmen at Knalga and yours here."
msgstr ""
"Si, moitos morreron nesta guerra, tanto os meus parentes en Knalga como os "
"teus aquí."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:220
msgid ""
"So many months of fighting... I feel as though I am awakening from a long "
"nightmare."
msgstr ""
"Tantos meses lutando... Sinto como se estivesse acordando de um longo "
"pesadelo."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#. he's alive, this isn't a plaque on a tomb
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:225
msgid ""
"My duty is done; the Clans have been avenged. At last, I can rest in peace."
msgstr ""
"Cumpri com meu dever; os Clãs foram vingados. Finalmente, posso descansar em "
"paz."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Alas, our work is not yet complete. Mal-Ravanal’s host has been broken, but "
"in its wake, chaos and disorder prevail throughout the countryside. We will "
"be years... decades... recovering from the ill wrought here."
msgstr ""
"Infelizmente, nosso trabalho ainda não terminou. As legiões de Mal-Ravanal "
"foram destruídas, mas em seu rastro, caos e desordem prevalecem por todos os "
"cantos. Serão necessário anos... décadas... de trabalho para rnos "
"recuperarmos do mal causado aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=Aeraeka
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:235
msgid ""
"Even now we should be sending what’s left of our armies to restore order "
"throughout the land."
msgstr ""
"Deveríamos enviar imediatamente o restante de nossas tropas para restaurar a "
"ordem por toda a terra."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. TODO for 1.19? Make clear who this is addressing, and make variations depending on whether it's to one person or two.
#. To Owaec, Gweddry or both; but I only know that because I can see the condition and the alternative line if they're both dead.
#. The "we" could be the royal pronoun (first person singular), but "we" as in "everyone in the Kingdom" fits too.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:249
msgid ""
"It shall be so. But first, know that you have served Us, and Our Kingdom, "
"full well. We are minded to reward you."
msgstr ""
"E assim será. Mas antes, saibam que vocês prestaram um serviço inestimável "
"para Nós, e para o nosso Reino. Temos a intenção de recompensá-los."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. All three heroes are dead.
#. The "we" could be the royal pronoun (first person singular), but "we" as in "everyone in the Kingdom" fits too.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:259
msgid ""
"I had a mind to share this victory with those who made it possible, yet so "
"many of them now lie dead. Lieutenant Gweddry, Lord Owaec, Advisor Dacyn, we "
"thank you for your sacrifice."
msgstr ""
"Eu tinha em mente compartilhar essa vitória com aqueles que a fizeram "
"possível, mas muitos deles agora estão mortos. Tenente Gweddry, Lorde Owaec, "
"Conselheiro Dacyn, nós agradecemos vocês pelos seus sacrifícios."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. the player chose to give Grug the plague staff
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:284
msgid ""
"Grug, a necromancer ogre is something wholly new to Us, but know that "
"Wesnoth will never tolerate your kind. You shall surrender that accursed "
"stave to be destroyed, you shall foreswear the practice of all magic on "
"penalty of death, and are hereby exiled from Wesnoth. Be grateful for Our "
"mercy."
msgstr ""
"Grug, um ogro necromante é algo completamente novo para Nós, mas saiba que "
"Wesnoth nunca tolerará o seu tipo. Você deve entregar este cajado "
"amaldiçoado para ser destruído, você deverá renunciar à prática de toda "
"magia sob a pena de morte, e está agora exilado de Wesnoth. Seja grato pela "
"Nossa misericórdia."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:288
msgid "Guh... Grug say no magic yes ok."
msgstr "Guh... Grug diz nenhuma magia ok."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:297
msgid ""
"Grug, Gweddry has told me of the help you and your tribe provided his men. "
"We wish to offer you a new home in the Estmark Hills along with Our thanks."
msgstr ""
"Grug, Gweddry me contou como você e sua tribo ajudaram os homens dele. Nós "
"queremos lhe oferecer um novo lar nas Colinas das Marcas Orientais e lhe "
"oferecemos Nossos agradecimentos."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:301
msgid "(bowing clumsily) Grug say new home will make thanks with."
msgstr "(curvando desajeitadamente) Grug diz que novo lar dá agradecimento."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:321
msgid ""
"Dolburras, Owaec has told me of the help you provided his men; both your "
"skill at arms and your tenacious spirit. We wish to offer you this finely "
"crafted shield — an heirloom of my line — and an honor guard as you return "
"to Knalga."
msgstr ""
"Dolburras, Owaec me falou da ajuda que você providenciou para seus homens; "
"tanto sua habilidade com armas quanto seu espírito tenaz. Nós gostaríamos de "
"lhe oferecer este escudo finamente trabalhado — uma herança da minha "
"linhagem — e uma guarda de honra para lhe escoltar até Knalga."

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#. "Aye, I am honored. You have my sincerest thanks, your Majesty."
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:332
msgid "Aye, I be honored. Ye have my sincerest thanks, yer Majesty."
msgstr "Si, síntome honrado. Tens o meu máis sincero agradecemento, Maxestade."

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#. Owaec's dead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:340
msgid "Aye, I be honored. I only wish he were here to see the Clans avenged."
msgstr ""
"Si, síntome honrado. Só gostaria que ele estivesse aquí para ver os Clans "
"vingados."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. the player chose to give Addogin the plague staff
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:367
msgid ""
"Mercenary, <i>necromancer</i>, know that Wesnoth will never tolerate your "
"kind. You shall surrender that accursed stave to be destroyed, you shall "
"foreswear the practice of all magic on penalty of death, and you are hereby "
"exiled from Wesnoth. Be grateful for Our mercy."
msgstr ""
"Mercenário, <i>necromante</i>, saiba que Wesnoth nunca tolerará o seu tipo. "
"Você deve entregar este cajado amaldiçoado para ser destruído, deverá "
"renunciar à prática de toda magia sob a pena de morte, e está agora exilado "
"de Wesnoth. Seja grato pela Nossa misericórdia."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:371
msgid ""
"Yeah, figures. How did I let myself get caught up in all this anyways? "
"Suppose I can always head north to those farmlands we passed by..."
msgstr ""
"É, foi como imaginei. Como que eu fui parar nessa enrascada? Acho que posso "
"ir ao norte, para aquelas fazendas que passamos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:380
msgid ""
"Addogin, mercenary captain from the Estmarks. I have heard the story of how "
"you entered Gweddry’s service against your will, but I have also heard that "
"you honored your word to see this invasion through to its end. The palace "
"could use a warrior of such caliber. We would offer you a position in the "
"Royal Guard."
msgstr ""
"Addogin, capitão mercenário das Marcas Orientais. Eu ouvi a história de como "
"você entrou a serviço de Gweddry contra sua vontade, mas também ouvi sobre "
"como você honrou sua palavra de lutar ao nosso lado até o fim dessa invasão. "
"O palácio poderia usar um guerreiro do seu calibre. Nós iremos lhe oferecer "
"uma posição na Guarda Real."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:384
msgid ""
"Sir, uh, milord, uh, King sir, I’m honored, really am, but I just wanna go "
"home. If it’s alright with you, this old geezer will be haulin’ himself back "
"east, to an overdue retirement."
msgstr ""
"Sir, uh, milorde, uh, senhor Rei, estou honrado, realmente estou, mas eu só "
"quero ir para casa. Se estiver tudo bem para você, este velho gagá já vai "
"indo de volta para o leste, já passou o tempo deu me aposentar."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:389
msgid ""
"As you wish. Then take this chest of silver, that you may never again need "
"raise sword for coin."
msgstr ""
"Como você desejar. Então pegue este baú de prata, para que você nunca mais "
"precise levantar sua espada por dinheiro."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:409
msgid ""
"Hahid al-Ali, We know of your far-off people, but great distance has caused "
"little contact between us. May it be thus no longer. If you accept, We would "
"appoint you as ambassador between our two realms."
msgstr ""
"Hahid al-Ali, Nós sabemos do seu povo distante, mas a grande distância levou "
"a pouco contanto entre nós. Que isso não seja mais o caso. Se você aceitar, "
"Nós apontaremos você como embaixador entre nossos dois reinos."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:413
msgid ""
"Me, ambassador to the barbarian kingdoms, what a thought! I am honored, and "
"would be even more honored to learn that the job comes with... excellent pay "
"I hope?"
msgstr ""
"Eu, embaixador dos reinos bárbaros, que coisa! Estou honrado, e estaria "
"ainda mais honrado de saber que o trabalho vem com... um excelente "
"pagamento, eu espero?"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:431
msgid ""
"Sir Terraent, your service to the Crown and your unfailing optimism has been "
"a beacon of light in these dark times. If you accept, we would appoint you "
"to command the River Guard in Estmark."
msgstr ""
"Sir Terraent, seu serviço à Coroa e seu otimismo inabalável tem sido um "
"farol de luz nestes tempos sombrios. Se você aceitar, nomearemos você para "
"comandar a Guarda do Rio nas Marcas Orientais."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:435
msgid ""
"It has been an honor to spread the holy Light in this kingdom, and I humbly "
"accept your commission. May the Light shine ever-bright upon the pious."
msgstr ""
"Foi uma honra espalhar a Luz sagrada por este reino, e eu humildemente "
"aceito o encargo. Que a Luz brilhe intensamente para os devotos."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. Gaennell’s previous crimes are held against her, regardless of whether or not she has the plague staff now.
#. Terraent is alive, "speaks well of you" meaning he's asked the King to pardon Gaennell.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:470
msgid ""
"As for you, <i>necromancer</i>. We are not as like as Terraent to show mercy "
"unto evil, but he speaks well of you, and so mercy shall be shown. Go from "
"here a free woman, but know that you are hereby forbidden to practice magic "
"in any form, at penalty of death."
msgstr ""
"E quanto a você, <i>necromante</i>. Nós não somos como Terraent para mostrar "
"misericórdia para o mal, mas ele falou bem de você, então haverá "
"misericórdia. Saia daqui como uma mulher livre, mas saiba que você esta "
"proibida de praticar magia de qualquer forma, sob a pena de morte."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. Gaennell’s previous crimes are held against her, regardless of whether or not she has the plague staff now.
#. Terraent is dead.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:480
msgid ""
"As for you, <i>necromancer</i>. We are not as like as Terraent to show mercy "
"unto evil, but in honor of his sacrifice We will show it now. Go from here a "
"free woman, but know that you are hereby forbidden to practice magic in any "
"form, at penalty of death."
msgstr ""
"E quanto a você, <i>necromante</i>. Nós não somos como Terraent para mostrar "
"misericórdia para o mal, mas em honra do seu sacrifício Nós a mostraremos "
"agora. Saia daqui como uma mulher livre, mas saiba que você esta proibida de "
"praticar magia de qualquer forma, sob a pena de morte."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:486
msgid "<i>Forbidden to-</i>"
msgstr "<i>Proibida de-</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:490
msgid ""
"... as an adept I’d dreamt of one day standing in this palace, though "
"under... different circumstances. Well, better that I get to keep my head, I "
"guess. I am grateful for Your leniency."
msgstr ""
"... como uma adepta, eu sonhei em um dia estar nesse palácio, mas sob... "
"outras circunstâncias. Bem, pelo menos eu não perdi a minha cabeça, eu acho. "
"Estou grata pela sua clemência."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. a unit has the plague staff, but they're not one of the loyals. This version of the line is used if Gaennell is here.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:515
msgid ""
"And the same goes for you, wielder of that accursed stave. You shall "
"surrender it to be destroyed, and leave here forbidden to practice magic. Be "
"grateful for Our mercy."
msgstr ""
"E o mesmo é válido para você, portador desse cajado amaldiçoado. Você deve "
"entrega-lo para ser destruído, e saia daqui proibido de praticar magia. Seja "
"grato pela Nossa misericórdia."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. a unit has the plague staff, but they're not one of the loyals, and the player doesn't have Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:524
msgid ""
"As for you, <i>necromancer</i>. You shall surrender that accursed stave to "
"be destroyed, and are hereby forbidden to practice magic in any form, at "
"penalty of death. Be grateful for Our mercy."
msgstr ""
"E quanto a você, <i>necromante</i>. Você deve entregar esse cajado "
"amaldiçoada para que seja destruído, e está proibido de praticar magia de "
"qualquer forma, sob pena de morte. Seja grato pela Nossa misericórdia."

#. [message]: speaker=$plague_staff_wielder_id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:530
msgid "As you command, your Majesty."
msgstr "Como queira, vossa Majestade."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:551
msgid ""
"Owaec, last Prince of the Plains. You and your people have suffered much."
msgstr "Owaec, último Príncipe das Planícies. Você e seu povo sofreram muito."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:555
msgid ""
"My Lord, the Clansmen gladly gave their lives for Wesnoth, and know that I "
"would do the same without hesitation."
msgstr ""
"Milorde, os membros do Clã deram suas vidas por Wesnoth de bom grado, e "
"saiba que eu faria o mesmo sem hesitação."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:560
msgid ""
"The true test is not to die for one’s King, but to live for Him... Kneel, "
"Owaec."
msgstr ""
"O verdadeiro teste não é morrer pelo seu Rei, mas sim viver por Ele... "
"Ajoelhe-se, Owaec."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:565
msgid ""
"And arise, Sir Owaec, High Lord of the Horse Clans! Your people have been "
"shattered, but We trust none more than you to make them whole again. Ride "
"from here, and recover in peace."
msgstr ""
"E levante-se, Sir Owaec, Grande Lorde dos Clãs dos Cavalos! Seu povo "
"estilhaçado, mas Nós não confiamos em ninguém mais do que você para restaurá-"
"lo. Cavalgue daqui, e restaure a paz."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#. Owaec is dead too
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:574
msgid ""
"But alas, what of the Clansmen? Their horses have been scattered, their "
"Lords were broken, and now the last prince has fallen defending the walls of "
"Weldyn. I fear that the Horse Clans will never again return to their former "
"glory."
msgstr ""
"Mas, por fim, o que será dos Clãs? Seus cavalos foram espalhados, seus "
"Lordes destruídos, e agora o último príncipe tombou defendendo as muralhas "
"de Weldyn. Eu temo que os Clãs dos Cavalos nunca retornarão à sua antiga "
"glória."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:592
msgid ""
"And now what of the humble Gweddry; still but a lieutenant. It seems you are "
"long-overdue for a promotion."
msgstr ""
"E agora, o que do humilde Gweddry; ainda apenas um tenente. Parece que você "
"a muito merece uma promoção."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:596
msgid "Sire, I but did my duty."
msgstr "Senhor, não fiz mais que minha obrigação."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:601
msgid ""
"Quite. Now do not interrupt while I am doing mine... Kneel, Gweddry, "
"lieutenant."
msgstr ""
"Realmente. Agora não me interrompa enquanto eu cumpro com a minha "
"obrigação... Ajoelhe-se, Gweddry, tenente."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:606
msgid ""
"And arise, Gweddry, Earl of Estmark! The land for which you shed your blood "
"shall be put under your hand to be made green again. May you ever prosper."
msgstr ""
"E levante-te, Gweddry, Conde da Marca Oriental. A terra pela qual você "
"derramou o seu sangue será posta sob seu comando para que a faça verde "
"novamente. Que você sempre prospere."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:614
msgid ""
"And what of Gweddry... He had survived long, sacrificed much, only to meet "
"his end here at the last. I wish he could have lived to see the peace he has "
"wrought."
msgstr ""
"E quanto a Gweddry... Ele sobreviveu por tanto tempo, sacrificou tanto, "
"apenas para conhecer seu fim aqui. Gostaria de que ele tivesse sobrevivido "
"para ver a paz que trouxe."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:626
msgid ""
"Wesnoth is bowed, but thanks to the efforts of many heroes we stand yet "
"unbroken. And now, at long last, the time has come to rebuild."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth está abatida, mas graças aos esforços de muitos heróis, nós "
"continuamos de pé. E agora, finalmente, é chegada a hora da reconstrução."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/18_Epilogue.cfg:631
msgid ""
"To each of you, take as Our first command to you your own wish! Go from "
"here; secure our borders. Show all that the might of Wesnoth will endure!"
msgstr ""
"Para cada um de vocês, a Nossa primeira ordem é que cumpram com seus "
"desejos! Vão, protejam nossas fronteiras. Mostrem a todos que Wesnoth "
"perdurará."

#. [scenario]: id=99_Empire
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:4
msgid "Empire"
msgstr "Império"

#. [part]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Congratulations! By sparing Dra-Nak in S11, ‘Captured’, sparing Mortic in "
"S12 ‘Evacuation’, and completing the difficult S17b ‘All-In’, you’ve "
"unlocked this bonus scenario!"
msgstr ""
"Parabéns! Por poupar Dra-Nak em S11, \"Capturado\", poupar Mortic em S12, "
"\"Evacuação\", e completar a difícil S17b \"Tudo ou Nada\", você desbloqueou "
"este cenário bônus!"

#. [side]: type=Drake Arbiter, id=Goag
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:103
msgid "Goag"
msgstr "Goag"

#. [side]: type=Drake Warrior, id=Gra'ritos
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:130
msgid "Gra’ritos"
msgstr "Gra’ritos"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:190
msgid "Survivors"
msgstr "Sobreviventes"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:224
msgid "Tribute"
msgstr "Tributo"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:232
msgid "Prison Guards"
msgstr "Guardas de Presídio"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:234
msgid "Tobo"
msgstr "Tobo"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:235
msgid "Unik"
msgstr "Unik"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:236
msgid "Shubru"
msgstr "Shubru"

#. [side]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:237
msgid "Grugnuk"
msgstr "Grugnuk"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:539
msgid "Filthy..."
msgstr "Imundos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:544
msgid "Stinking..."
msgstr "Fedorentos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:549
msgid "TRAITORS!!!"
msgstr "TRAIDORES!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:554
msgid ""
"Drakes, human, dwarves... vermin, all of them! I offered them a chance at "
"peace, at purpose! A chance to be part of something greater than themselves "
"— my great golden Empire!!! And this is the thanks I get?"
msgstr ""
"Draconatos, humanos, anões... vermes, todos eles! Eu ofereci a eles uma "
"chance de paz, de propósito! Uma chance de serem parte de algo maior do que "
"eles individualmente — meu grande Império dourado!!! E é assim que me "
"agradecem?"

#. [message]: type=Orcish Slayer
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:560
msgid ""
"Chief, more wyrms are attacking the east tunnels! There’s too many of them! "
"What do we do?"
msgstr ""
"Chefe, mais wyrms estão atacando os túneis ao leste! Eles são numerosos "
"demais! O que faremos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:564
msgid ""
"I’m not going to let everything I’ve worked for fall apart so easily! These "
"vermin are WEAK! We are STRONG!"
msgstr ""
"Eu não vou deixar tudo pelo que trabalhei desmoronar tão facilmente! Estes "
"vermes são FRACOS! Nós somos FORTES!"

#. [message]: type=Orcish Slayer
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:568
msgid "Okay, but that’s not really a battle pla-"
msgstr "Tá bom, mas isso não é realmente um plano de bat-"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:572
msgid ""
"Capture their warriors and sell them for gold. Break their leaders and bend "
"their followers to my will. I’ll slay anyone who resists and build a new "
"empire on top of their steaming corpses!"
msgstr ""
"Capturem os guerreiros deles e vendam eles por ouro. Destruam os líderes "
"deles e forcem os seus seguidores a me obdecerem. Eu matarei qualquer um que "
"resistir e construirei um novo império em cima de seus cadáveres fumegantes!"

#. [objective]: condition=win
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:578
msgid "Defeat all drake leaders"
msgstr "Derrote todos os líderes draconatos"

#. [objective]: condition=lose
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:582
msgid "Death of Chief Dra-Nak"
msgstr "Morte do Chefe Dra-Nak"

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:586
msgid "You are fighting in your home and therefore pay no upkeep."
msgstr "Você está lutando em seu lar, então não precisa pagar manutenção."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:589
msgid ""
"Reduce enemies to 0 hp to capture them and gain gold. The prisons have "
"limited space."
msgstr ""
"Reduza os inimigos a 0 hp para capturá-los e ganhar ouro. As prisões tem "
"espaço limitado."

#. [note]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:592
msgid "Surviving enemies will (mostly) join you when you defeat their leader."
msgstr ""
"Inimigos sobreviventes irão (de modo geral) se juntar a você assim que você "
"derrotar os líderes deles."

#. [message]: speaker=unit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:621
msgid ""
"I’ve emptied the last of our treasury! Only 31 pieces, but better than "
"nothing."
msgstr ""
"Eu esvaziei o resto de nosso tesouro! Apenas 31 peças, mas melhor do que "
"nada."

#. [then]
#. said by Dra-Nak as an insult to Mortic in the latter's last-breath event
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:636
msgid "Some ‘leader’."
msgstr "Mas que \"líder\"."

#. [then]
#. said by Dra-Nak as an insult to Goag in the latter's last-breath event
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:643
msgid "That’ll teach him. Where was that loyalty when he used to obey me?"
msgstr ""
"Isso ensinará ele. Onde estava aquela lealdade quando ele costumava me "
"servir?"

#. [then]
#. said by Dra-Nak as an insult to Gra’ritos in the latter's last-breath event
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:650
msgid "What happened to dying slow? So much for him."
msgstr "O que aconteceu com morrer devagar? Era uma vez ele."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:656
msgid "They really thought they could get away? Haw..."
msgstr "Eles realmente pensaram que poderiam fugir? Hah..."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:680
msgid ""
"He called himself your leader, but now you see him for the weakling he "
"really was. You can either join him or fight alongside me and pray I show "
"you mercy."
msgstr ""
"Ele se autoproclamou seu líder, mas agora você vê o quão fraco ele realmente "
"era. Você pode se juntar a ele ou lutar ao meu lado e rezar para que eu seja "
"misericordioso."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:686
msgid ""
"As for the rest of you — pledge yourselves to me, or die a slow painful "
"death!"
msgstr ""
"E quanto ao resto de vocês — jurem lealdade a mim, ou morram uma morte lenta "
"e dolorosa!"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:692
msgid "You might as well give it up! Resistance is pointless."
msgstr "Seria mais fácil para vocês desistirem agora! Não há porque resistir."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:698
msgid ""
"Nobody escapes me. Join me and I’ll treat you fairly, resist me and you’ll "
"die painfully."
msgstr ""
"Ninguém escapa de mim. Juntem-se a mim e eu tratarei vocês de maneira justa, "
"resistam e morrerão uma morte agonizante."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:709
msgid ""
"Mortic was strong.\n"
"Alone I am weak.\n"
"I will serve you."
msgstr ""
"Mortic era forte.\n"
"Sozinho eu sou fraco.\n"
"Eu servirei você."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:717
msgid ""
"I crave not death.\n"
"I will myself to you."
msgstr ""
"Eu não desejo morrer.\n"
"Eu me entrego a você."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:724
msgid ""
"These orcs enrage me,\n"
"But I possess no strength to resist.\n"
"I will serve you."
msgstr ""
"Estes orcs me enfurecem,\n"
"Mas não possuo forças para resistir.\n"
"Eu servirei a você."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:732
msgid "Yes, yes, just please don’t hurt me!"
msgstr "Sim, sim, só por favor, não me machuque!"

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:772
msgid ""
"I shall never again obey orc.\n"
"Mortic fought and died.\n"
"I shall fight as well."
msgstr ""
"Eu nunca servirei um orc novamente.\n"
"Mortic lutou e morreu.\n"
"Eu também lutarei."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:780
msgid ""
"I am always loyal,\n"
"but never to prey.\n"
"I fight until death."
msgstr ""
"Eu sempre sou leal,\n"
"mas nunca para a presa.\n"
"Eu lutarei até à morte."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:788
msgid ""
"I grieve.\n"
"May the end come swiftly."
msgstr ""
"Eu lamento.\n"
"Que o final venha rápido."

#. [then]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:795
msgid "You traitors, how could you! I’ll never betray Wesnoth!"
msgstr "Seus traidores, como podem! Eu jamais trairei Wesnoth!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:823
msgid "Surrender or die, your choice!"
msgstr "Renda-se ou morra. A escolha é sua!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:827
msgid ""
"Surrender brings certain death.\n"
"Battle may yet bring victory.\n"
"There is no choice."
msgstr ""
"Rendição traz morte certa.\n"
"Batalhar talvez traga vitória.\n"
"Não há escolha."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:833
msgid "Die it is then!"
msgstr "Então Morra!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mortic
#. Mortic's last breath
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:850
msgid ""
"Surrender brings death.\n"
"Battle brings death.\n"
"All is death..."
msgstr ""
"Rendição traz morte.\n"
"Batalha traz morte.\n"
"Tudo é morte..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:873
msgid ""
"The reaper’s knocking at your door, wyrm! Give up now and maybe I’ll kill "
"you quickly."
msgstr ""
"A morte está batendo na sua porta, wyrm! Desista agora e talvez eu te dê uma "
"morte rápida."

#. [message]: speaker=Goag
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:877
msgid ""
"Mortic commanded me to fight.\n"
"So the Aspirant ordered, so I will fight,\n"
"Until the end."
msgstr ""
"Mortic me ordenou lutar.\n"
"Assim ordenou o Aspirante, assim lutarei,\n"
"Até o fim."

#. [message]: speaker=Gra'ritos
#. to Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:913
msgid ""
"You are Prey.\n"
"I am Hunter.\n"
"I will not fall easily."
msgstr ""
"Você é a Presa.\n"
"Eu sou o Caçador.\n"
"Eu não cairei facilmente."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:919
msgid "Good, I’ll enjoy making it slow."
msgstr "Ótimo, vou me divertir te matando devagar."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. as the west bridge is broken, the Wesnothians who were left behind are trying to get though the orc's caves and out the east side
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:953
msgid ""
"Haw, back so soon? Too bad your ‘friends’ abandoned you on MY side of the "
"river. But it’s your lucky day, I’m a fair orc. Surrender now and I might be "
"merciful."
msgstr ""
"Hah, mas já voltaram? Uma pena que seus \"amigos\" os abandonaram no MEU "
"lado do rio. Mas hoje é o seu dia de sorte, eu sou um orc justo. Se rendam "
"agora e talvez eu seja misericordioso."

#. [message]: role=leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:957
msgid "We’ll never give in to you! For Wesnoth!!"
msgstr "Nós nunca nos renderemos! Por Wesnoth!!"

#. [message]: role=leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:969
msgid "This foolish plan was my idea... I’m so, so sorry everyone..."
msgstr ""
"Esse plano tolo foi minha ideia... Minhas mais sinceras desculpas a todos..."

#. [message]: role=leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:985
msgid "Keep pushing forward! Stick to the south tunnels! We can do this!"
msgstr "Continuem avançando! Para os túneis do sul! Estamos quase lá!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. the necromancers are apparently paying gold immediately when each prisoner is captured
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1010
msgid ""
"That’s right, bleed them down and lock them up! I need gold to win this "
"fight!"
msgstr ""
"Isso mesmo, façam eles sangrar e depois prendam eles! Eu preciso de ouro "
"para ganhar essa luta!"

#. [message]: speaker=Unik
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1020
msgid ""
"Chief, I only have space for so many prisoners. As cells get crowded, "
"prisoners will start to get sick and we won’t get paid as much."
msgstr ""
"Chefe, eu não tenho espaço para tantos prisioneiros. Conforme as celas ficam "
"cheias, os prisioneiros começam a ficar doentes e o nosso pagamento diminui."

#. [message]: speaker=Unik
#. the hole where the escape in S11 started
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1028
msgid ""
"Things are starting to get really crowded over here Chief. Shame the fourth "
"cell has a hole in the back..."
msgstr ""
"As coisas estão começando a ficar bem apertadas aqui, Chefe. É uma pena que "
"a quarta cela tenha um buraco na parte de trás..."

#. [message]: speaker=Unik
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1035
msgid ""
"That’s it boss, the prisoners are packed as tight as they’ll go! Hope you "
"got enough gold to finish off the drakes."
msgstr ""
"É isso chefe, os prisioneiros estão amontoados o máximo possível! Espero que "
"tenha conseguido ouro o suficiente para derrotar os draconatos."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1205
msgid "Get away from my jail cells! Filthy traitors, there goes my income..."
msgstr ""
"Saiam de perto das minhas celas! Traidores imundos, lá se vai minha fonte de "
"renda..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1209
msgid ""
"Fine then, I’m done taking prisoners. From here on out, you either submit or "
"die!"
msgstr ""
"Então está bem, não farei mais prisioneiros. De agora em diante, vocês se "
"rendem ou morrem!"

#. [message]: role=leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1336
msgid ""
"Come on, don’t give up! Owaec’s destroyed the bridge so we’ll have to fight "
"our way back through the orcish tunnels."
msgstr ""
"Vamos, não desistam! Owaec destruiu a ponte, então teremos que fazer nosso "
"caminho de volta pelos túneis dos orcs."

#. [message]: role=leader
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1352
msgid ""
"I know this looks grim, but we have to try. It’s our only chance. If we can "
"just get through to the eastern exit, we might be able to escape!"
msgstr ""
"Eu sei que a situação não parece boa, mas temos que tentar. Essa é a nossa "
"única chance. Se nós conseguirmos chegar à saída leste, talvez sejamos "
"capazes de escapar!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1414
msgid "Thank the Light, I’ve made it! Please please please don’t chase me..."
msgstr ""
"Graças à Luz, eu consegui! Por favor por favo por favor, não me persigam..."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1417
msgid "Yes, YES! Get me out of here."
msgstr "Sim, SIM! Me tire daqui."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1420
msgid "Ha ha, you’ll never catch me now!"
msgstr "Ha ha, vocês nunca me pegarão agora!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1423
msgid "Whew, that was a close one!"
msgstr "Fiu, esta foi por pouco!"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1427
msgid "I’ve escaped!"
msgstr "Eu escapei!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1483
msgid ""
"Well done, grunts. No more revolts, no more rebellion, and lots of "
"prisoners..."
msgstr ""
"Bem feito, soldados. Sem mais revoltas, sem mais rebelião, e muitos "
"prisioneiros..."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. all the prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1488
msgid "Now kill them all."
msgstr "Agora matem todos eles."

#. [message]: speaker=Unik
#. already paid them for the prisoners
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1604
msgid "But Chief, the necromancers already paid us! We can’t just-"
msgstr "Mas Chefe, os necromantes já nos pagaram! Nós não podemos simple-"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. all the necromancers
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1609
msgid "Then I’ll kill them all too! I’m done working with others!"
msgstr ""
"Então eu matarei todos eles também! Estou cansado de trabalhar com os outros!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1625
msgid ""
"I tried being merciful. I tried working toward peace. I tried building an "
"empire where all races could be a part of something great, and all I asked "
"in return was simple tribute."
msgstr ""
"Eu tentei ser misericordioso. Tentei trabalhar em busca da paz. Tentei "
"construir um império onde todas as raças pudessem ser parte de algo maior, e "
"tudo o que eu pedi em retorno foi um simples tributo."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1629
msgid ""
"Mercy no more. I’ll build a new empire on the smoking rubble of the old, an "
"empire for orcs and orcs alone, an empire to unite all the scattered tribes "
"under one banner!"
msgstr ""
"Sem mais misericórdia. Construirei um novo império sobre os escombros do "
"antigo, um império para orcs e orcs apenas, um império para unir todas as "
"tribos dispersas sobre um único estandarte!"

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1633
msgid "And when I’m ready, we will march across the world and make it ours."
msgstr ""
"E quando eu estiver pronto, nós marcharemos ao redor do mundo e faremos dele "
"nosso."

#. [message]: speaker=Chief Dra-Nak
#. the chief's last breath
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/scenarios/99_Empire.cfg:1649
msgid "FILTHY... Rotten... ...traitors... ..."
msgstr "IMUNDOS... Podres... ...traidores... ..."

#. [unit_type]: id=Ant Queen, gender=female, race=monster
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ant_Queen.cfg:4
msgid "Ant Queen"
msgstr "Formiga-rainha"

#. [unit_type]: id=Ant Queen, gender=female, race=monster
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ant_Queen.cfg:20
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "At the heart of each giant ant burrow lies a queen. Much like their "
#| "miniature cousins, a well-fed giant ant queen will continually lay eggs, "
#| "ensuring that the colony never lacks workers for scavenging or soldiers "
#| "for defense."
msgid ""
"At the heart of each giant ant burrow lies a queen. Much like their "
"miniature cousins, a well-fed giant Ant Queen will continually lay eggs, "
"ensuring that the colony never lacks workers for scavenging or soldiers for "
"defense."
msgstr ""
"No coração de cada ninho de formigas gigantes, encontra-se uma rainha. Assim "
"como suas primas em miniatura, uma formiga-rainha gigante bem alimentada põe "
"ovos continuamente, garantindo que a colônia nunca terá falta de "
"trabalhadores para catar alimentos ou soldados para defesa."

#. [dummy]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ant_Queen.cfg:26
msgid "royalty"
msgstr "realeza"

#. [dummy]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ant_Queen.cfg:27
msgid "If the ant queen is killed, all of her subjects die."
msgstr "Se a formiga-rainha for morta, todos os seus súditos morrem."

#. [unit_type]: id=Egg Sac, race=monster
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Egg_Sac.cfg:4
msgid "Egg Sac"
msgstr "Saco de ovos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Egg Sac, race=monster
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Egg_Sac.cfg:17
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Each of these enormous egg sacs contains up to a dozen ant larvae, "
#| "sheltering and nourishing them while they develop into worker drones. "
#| "When the burrow is threatened, an ant queen can release pheromones that "
#| "cause each sac to rapidly develop into a single large warrior ant."
msgid ""
"Each of these enormous Egg Sacs contains up to a dozen ant larvae, "
"sheltering and nourishing them while they develop into worker drones. When "
"the burrow is threatened, an ant queen can release pheromones that cause "
"each sac to rapidly develop into a single large warrior ant."
msgstr ""
"Cada um desses enormes sacos de ovos contém até uma dúzia de larvas "
"formigas, abrigando e nutrindo eles enquanto se desenvolvem em drones "
"trabalhadores. Quando o ninho é ameaçado, a formiga-rainha consegue lançar "
"feromônios que fazem com que cada saco se desenvolva rapidamente em um único "
"grande guerreiro formiga."

#. [dummy]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Egg_Sac.cfg:22
msgid "hatch"
msgstr "chocar"

#. [dummy]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Egg_Sac.cfg:23
msgid ""
"If an enemy unit is adjacent to this egg sac when it begins its turn, it "
"will hatch."
msgstr ""
"Se uma unidade inimiga estiver adjacente a este saco de ovo qno começo do "
"turno deleturno, ele chocará."

#. [unit_type]: id=Gate, race=mechanical
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Gate.cfg:5
msgid "Gate"
msgstr "Portão"

#. [unit_type]: id=Gate, race=mechanical
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Gate.cfg:9
msgid "An old gate, poorly maintained but of sturdy construction."
msgstr "Um portão velho, mal mantido, mas de robusta construção."

# É um título militar real, mas difícil de achar.
# Existe uma sub-classe de DnD 5.0 de guerreiro que carrega esse nome. Encontra-se no livro Costa da Espada guia de aventureiro... Depois de pesquisar no livro o tradutor escolheu o camino mais fácil (ignorar o original inglês e traduzir um outro título da classe)
# Depois de mais pesquisa, existe uma palavra perfeira em português mas que ninguém associa a esa ideia: Bandeirante. Originalmente era o termo empregado em Portugal para membros de ordens de cavalaria que lutavam sobre uma bandeira em particular, ou seja, a mando de umc avaleiro!
#. [unit_type]: id=Banneret, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Banneret.cfg:4
msgid "Banneret"
msgstr "Bandeirante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Banneret, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Banneret.cfg:19
msgid ""
"The few lancers who survive for long enough invariably find themselves "
"commanding companies of their own. Still clad in minimal armor, they ride "
"with even greater speed, charging into battle and leading from the forefront "
"of any conflict."
msgstr ""
"Os poucos lanceiros que sobrevivem por tempo o suficiente invariavelmente "
"acabam comandando suas próprias companhias. Ainda revestidos com o mínimo de "
"armadura possível, eles cavalgam ainda mais velozmente, lançando-se à "
"batalha e liderando qualquer conflito das linhas de frente."

#. [unit_type]: id=Fallen Mage, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Dacyn_Fallen_Mage.cfg:10
msgid "Fallen Mage"
msgstr "Mago Caído"

#. [unit_type]: id=Fallen Mage, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Dacyn_Fallen_Mage.cfg:25
msgid ""
"There are dark powers in this world which humankind was not meant to "
"understand. Even the greatest and wisest can be bound in service of such a "
"darkness."
msgstr ""
"Existem poderes sombrios neste mundo que a humanidade não foi feita para "
"entender. Mesmo os maiores e mais sábios podem ser obrigados a servir tal "
"escuridão."

#. [dummy]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Dacyn_Fallen_Mage.cfg:63
msgid "rotting"
msgstr "apodrecendo"

#. [dummy]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Dacyn_Fallen_Mage.cfg:64
msgid "Immune to poison, drain, and plague."
msgstr "Imunidade a veneno, dreno e praga."

#. [unit_type]: id=Twilight Mage, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Dacyn_Twilight_Mage.cfg:4
msgid "Twilight Mage"
msgstr "Mago do Crepúsculo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Twilight Mage, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Dacyn_Twilight_Mage.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Even the most devout of white magi can have their light tainted by the power "
"of darkness. Though not extinguished, their faltering inner light can become "
"muted."
msgstr ""
"Mesmo os mais devotos magos brancos podem ter sua luz contaminada pelo poder "
"das trevas. Embora não extinta, sua vacilante luz interior pode ser abafada."

#. [unit_type]: id=Frontier Lieutenant, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Frontier_Lieutenant.cfg:4
msgid "Frontier Lieutenant"
msgstr "Tenente da Fronteira"

#. [unit_type]: id=Frontier Lieutenant, race=human
#. same as regular Lieutenant's description
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Frontier_Lieutenant.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Lieutenants are some of the more respected commanding officers among humans "
"and are often seen leading smaller-scale incursions and managing the "
"battlefield. Trained both with sword and crossbow, they excel at neither, "
"and are somewhat less resilient than the warlords of other races — this is "
"more than made up for by their superior knowledge and training in military "
"strategy."
msgstr ""
"Os Tenentes estão entre os oficiais mais respeitados entre os humanos e "
"geralmente podem ser vistos liderando pequenas incursões e gerenciando o "
"campo de batalha. Treinados tanto com a espada quanto com a besta, eles não "
"se destacam com nenhuma das duas armas, e são um pouco menos resistentes do "
"que os comandantes das outras raças — o que é mais do que compensado por seu "
"superior conhecimento e treino em estratégias militares."

#. [unit_type]: id=Frontier Sergeant, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Frontier_Sergeant.cfg:4
msgid "Frontier Sergeant"
msgstr "Sargento da Fronteira"

#. [unit_type]: id=Frontier Sergeant, race=human
#. same as regular Sergeant's description
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Frontier_Sergeant.cfg:19
msgid ""
"Sergeants are low-ranking officers of human armies. Though academically "
"trained, they need some experience in the field before their leadership is "
"sound and acknowledged. Still, their diligent bearing and basic insight of "
"combat means they can more effectively rouse civilians and peasants in "
"trying situations."
msgstr ""
"Sargentos são oficiais de baixa patente dos exércitos humanos. Apesar de "
"terem treinamento acadêmico, eles precisam de um pouco de experiência "
"prática antes que o seu comando seja bom e aceito pelas tropas. Ainda assim, "
"sua diligência e conhecimento básico de combate fazem com que eles sejam "
"efetivos em instigar os ânimos de civis e camponeses em momentos difíceis."

#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Commander, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Veteran_Commander.cfg:4
msgid "Veteran Commander"
msgstr "Comandante Veterano"

#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Commander, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Veteran_Commander.cfg:30
msgid ""
"Despite his lack of formal rank, Gweddry radiates more leadership and "
"experience than many commanders twice his age. His cunning and tactical "
"skill have been honed over countless battles, enabling him to direct even "
"the freshest of recruits to strike strategically against impossible odds and "
"emerge victorious."
msgstr ""
"Apesar de sua falta de patente formal, Gweddry irradia mais liderança e "
"experiência do que muitos comandantes com o dobro de sua idade. Suas astúcia "
"e habilidades táticas foram aprimoradas após inúmeras batalhas, permitindo-o "
"direcionar mesmo os mais inexperientes recrutas a atacar estrategicamente "
"contra probabilidades impossíveis e saírem vitoriosos."

#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Lieutenant, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Veteran_Lieutenant.cfg:4
msgid "Veteran Lieutenant"
msgstr "Tenente Veterano"

#. [unit_type]: id=Veteran Lieutenant, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Gweddry_Veteran_Lieutenant.cfg:29
msgid ""
"Once inexperienced, Gweddry is now a veteran of many battles. His cunning "
"and tactical skill enable him to direct even the freshest of recruits to "
"strike strategically and emerge victorious. His skill with the longsword and "
"crossbow is not to be underestimated either, nor is the speed with which he "
"can move despite his heavy armor."
msgstr ""
"Uma vez inexperiente, Gweddry é agora um veterano de muitas batalhas. Sua "
"astúcia e habilidade táctica permitem que ele direcione o mais novo recruta "
"para atacar estrategicamente e sair vitorioso. Suas habilidades com a espada "
"longa e a besta também não devem ser subestimadas, nem a velocidade com que "
"ele pode se mover, apesar de sua armadura pesada."

#. [unit_type]: id=King of Wesnoth, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Konrad_King_of_Wesnoth.cfg:4
msgid "King of Wesnoth"
msgstr "Rei de Wesnoth"

#. [unit_type]: id=King of Wesnoth, race=human, gender=male
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Konrad_King_of_Wesnoth.cfg:23
msgid ""
"Kings are trained rigorously in the combat arts, sometimes out of necessity, "
"more often out of tradition from when their priors made their wealth in war. "
"Fitted in armor so skillfully made as to incite envy even from many dwarvish "
"smiths, these sovereigns are well conditioned to their heavy armor and can "
"maneuver across the battlefield much faster than their gilded plate would "
"suggest."
msgstr ""
"Reis são treinados rigorosamente nas artes de combate, as vezes por "
"necessidade, mas mais comumente por conta de que seus antecessores "
"construíram suas riquezas por meio de guerras. Vestindo armaduras tão bem "
"forjadas ao ponto de causar inveja em muitos ferreiros anões, esses "
"soberanos estão bem acostumados ao tremendo peso da armadura e são capazes "
"de se mover pelo campo de batalha muito mais rápido do que seria de se "
"esperar."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Konrad_King_of_Wesnoth.cfg:39
msgid "sceptre of fire"
msgstr "cetro de fogo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Mounted Warrior  # use the old id so we don't break old saves, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Clan_Captain.cfg:4
msgid "Clan Captain"
msgstr "Capitão do Clã"

#. [unit_type]: id=Mounted Warrior  # use the old id so we don't break old saves, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Clan_Captain.cfg:26
msgid ""
"The leaders-to-be of the Horse Clans, each of these proud nobles is skilled "
"in combat and adheres to a strict code of honor. Even the most tenacious of "
"opponents will quake at the sight of a horse charge spearheaded by one of "
"these fearless riders."
msgstr ""
"Futuros líderes dos Clãs dos Cavalos, cada um desses orgulhosos nobres é "
"qualificado em combate e adere a um estrito código de honra. Mesmo o mais "
"tenaz dos oponentes tremerá ao ver uma carga de cavalaria liderada por um "
"desses destemidos cavaleiros."

#. [attack]: type=impact
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Clan_Captain.cfg:46
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Horse_Lord.cfg:47
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Princeling.cfg:46
msgid "greathammer"
msgstr "martelo grande"

#. [unit_type]: id=Horse Lord, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Horse_Lord.cfg:4
msgid "Horse Lord"
msgstr "Lorde dos Cavalos"

#. [unit_type]: id=Horse Lord, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Horse_Lord.cfg:27
msgid ""
"The greatest of the men of the plains, Horse Lords are heads of their houses "
"and are respected by all, friend or foe. These lords lead by example, "
"dominating the battlefield from the head of a cavalry charge."
msgstr ""
"Os maiores entre os homens das planícies, os Lordes dos Cavalos são os "
"chefes de suas casas e são respeitados por todos, sejam amigos ou inimigos. "
"Esses lordes lideram das linhas de frente, dominando o campo de batalha à "
"frente de uma carga de cavalaria."

#. [unit_type]: id=Mounted Fighter  # use the old id so we don't break old saves, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Princeling.cfg:4
msgid "Princeling"
msgstr "Príncipinho"

#. [unit_type]: id=Mounted Fighter  # use the old id so we don't break old saves, race=human
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Owaec_Princeling.cfg:26
msgid ""
"From early age, the nobles of the plains train vigorously in both combat and "
"governance, preparing to someday become captains of the Clans. Though young "
"and brash, these fighters have the potential to become great warriors one "
"day."
msgstr ""
"Desde jovens, os nobres das planícies treinam vigorosamente tanto em combate "
"quanto em governança, preparando-se para um dia se tornarem capitães dos "
"Clãs. Embora jovens e impetuosos, esses lutadores tem o potencial para se "
"tornarem grandes guerreiros um dia."

#. [attack]: type=fire
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Terraent_Paladin.cfg:48
msgid "blessed lance"
msgstr "lança abençoada"

#. [unit_type]: id=Townsfolk, race=human, gender=male,female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Townsfolk.cfg:4
msgid "Townsfolk"
msgstr "Citadino"

#. [unit_type]: id=Townsfolk, race=human, gender=male,female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Human_Townsfolk.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Townsfolk are city-dwellers who try to make their fortune in a non-violent "
"manner, be they traders, craftsmen, or servants of a noble house. They "
"almost universally lack the strength that comes from a life of physical "
"labour, and thus are not conscripted as often as peasants."
msgstr ""
"Citadinos são os indivíduos que moram em cidades que tentam fazer sua "
"fortuna de uma maneira não violenta; sejam eles comerciantes, artesãos ou "
"servos de uma casa nobre. Eles quase que universalmente carecem da força que "
"vem de uma vida de trabalho físico, e portanto não são recrutados com tanta "
"frequência quanto os camponeses."

#. [unit_type]: id=Naga Centurion, race=naga, gender=male,female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Naga_Centurion.cfg:4
msgid "Naga Centurion"
msgstr "Centurião Naga"

#. [unit_type]: id=Naga Centurion, race=naga, gender=male,female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Naga_Centurion.cfg:20
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The leaders of the naga have mastered the serpentine arts of their kind, "
#| "striking faster than a lightning bolt and dancing away more gracefully "
#| "than a forest brook. Undisputed masters of both swordsmanship and "
#| "leadership, these Naga are honored by their clutch and bestowed the rare "
#| "title of Centurion."
msgid ""
"The leaders of the naga have mastered the serpentine arts of their kind, "
"striking faster than a lightning bolt and dancing away more gracefully than "
"a forest brook. Undisputed masters of both swordsmanship and leadership, "
"these naga are honored by their clutch and bestowed the rare title of "
"Centurion."
msgstr ""
"Os líderes dos Naga chegaram ao ápice das artes serpentinas de sua raça, "
"atacando mais rápido que um raio e dançando para longe do perigo com mais "
"graça que um riacho na floresta. Mestres incontestáveis tanto em esgrima "
"quanto em liderança, estes Naga são honrados pela sua ninhada e agraciados "
"com o raro título de Centurião."

#. [attack]: type=blade
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Naga_Centurion.cfg:32
msgid "blade"
msgstr "lâmina"

#. [attack]: type=blade
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Naga_Centurion.cfg:41
msgid "speed strike"
msgstr "ataque rápido"

#. [female]: gender=female
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Naga_Centurion.cfg:72
msgid "Nagini Centurion"
msgstr "Centurião Nagini"

#. [unit_type]: id=Ancient Ogre, race=ogre
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ogre_Ancient.cfg:4
msgid "Ancient Ogre"
msgstr "Ogro Ancião"

#. [unit_type]: id=Ancient Ogre, race=ogre
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ogre_Ancient.cfg:30
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "Ancient ogres possess legendary strength and stand taller than even many "
#| "woses. They usually live among their own kind in the wilderness, but can "
#| "be highly loyal to those few they trust."
msgid ""
"Ancient Ogres possess legendary strength and stand taller than even many "
"woses. They usually live among their own kind in the wilderness, but can be "
"highly loyal to those few they trust."
msgstr ""
"Ogros Anciãos possuem uma força lendária e chegam a ser mais altos que "
"muitos woses. Eles geralmente vivem entre os outros membros de sua raça nas "
"regiões selvagens, mas podem ser altamente leais àqueles poucos em quem "
"confiam."

#. [unit_type]: id=Great Ogre, race=ogre
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ogre_Great.cfg:4
msgid "Great Ogre"
msgstr "Grande Ogro"

#. [unit_type]: id=Great Ogre, race=ogre
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Ogre_Great.cfg:27
msgid ""
"Great Ogres are giant creatures that usually live alone in the wilderness. "
"While they can be easily outrun or outsmarted, their strength is not to be "
"underestimated."
msgstr ""
"Grandes Ogros são criaturas gigantes que geralmente vivem sozinhos em "
"regiões selvagens. Embora seja fácil de escapar deles ou passar a perna "
"neles, a sua força não deve ser subestimada."

# https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cultura_dos_T%C3%BAmulos
#. [unit_type]: id=Barrow Wight, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Horse_Barrow_Wight.cfg:4
msgid "Barrow Wight"
msgstr "Alma do Túmulo"

#. [unit_type]: id=Barrow Wight, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Horse_Barrow_Wight.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Perpetually haunted by the fading memory of its former life, a Barrow Wight "
"wanders aimlessly in a delirium of darkness and despair. Their chill essence "
"is shrouded behind cloak and bone, shielding them from most magic."
msgstr ""
"Perpetuamente assombrada pela sua cada vez mais fraca memória de sua vida "
"anterior, uma Alma do Túmulo vaga sem rumo em um delírio de escuridão e "
"desespero. Sua essência gélida é rodeada por um manto e ossos, protegendo-a "
"da maioria das magias."

# Pyre = Pira
#. [unit_type]: id=Pyre Wight, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Horse_Pyre_Wight.cfg:4
msgid "Pyre Wight"
msgstr "Alma da Pira"

#. [unit_type]: id=Pyre Wight, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Horse_Pyre_Wight.cfg:18
msgid ""
"Risen from a funeral’s ashes and newly bathed in fire, a Pyre Wight’s soul "
"burns with a desire for vengeance. They single-mindedly seek out those who "
"wronged them in their past life, but undeath has robbed their memories of "
"friend and foe."
msgstr ""
"Ressurgida das cinzas funerárias e recentemente banhadas em fogo, as almas "
"penadas nascidas das piras queimam com o desejo de vingança. Elas buscam "
"obstinadamente aqueles que as prejudicaram em sua vida passada, mas a não-"
"morte roubou-lhes as memórias de amigos e inimigos."

#. [unit_type]: id=Dread Lich, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Ravanal_Dread_Lich.cfg:17
msgid "Dread Lich"
msgstr "Lich Aterrorizante"

#. [unit_type]: id=Dread Lich, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Ravanal_Dread_Lich.cfg:31
msgid ""
"Named thusly for the abject terror they awaken in their enemies, a so-called "
"Dread Lich is an artisan of necromantic power, a consummate master of the "
"dark magics they wield.\n"
"\n"
"Invariably in command of a nigh limitless horde of risen warriors and undead "
"monsters, a lich of this order has a mastery of dark sorcery that can bring "
"dread to the most storied magi of human and elven kind. Such a figure "
"usually marks a dark and bloody chapter in history, and in those times of "
"need, it is only through the tireless efforts of the most valiant heroes "
"that the rise of an Dread Lich has not led to the shadows ruling the world "
"for the rest of time."
msgstr ""
"Assim nomeado por conta do terror que gera em seus inimigos, um assim "
"chamado lich Aterrorizante é um artesão do poder necromântico, um mestre "
"consumado dos poderes sombrios por eles empunhado.\n"
"\n"
"Invariavelmente no comandao de uma horda quase ilimitada de guerreiros "
"ressurgidos e de monstros mortos-vivos, um lich dessa ordem possui um "
"domínio da feitiçaria sombria capaz de trazer pavor até aos mais renomados "
"magos da humanidade e dos elfos. Tal figura normalmente marca um capítulo "
"sombrio e sangrento na história, e em tempos de necessidade, é apenas pelo "
"incansáveis esforços dos mais valentes heróis que a ascenção de um Lich "
"Aterrorizante não levou as sombras a governar o mundo até os fins dos tempos."

#. [dummy]: id=reanimation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Ravanal_Dread_Lich.cfg:74
msgid "reanimation"
msgstr "reanimação"

#. [dummy]: id=reanimation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Ravanal_Dread_Lich.cfg:75
msgid ""
"This unit can reanimate its defeated allies and enemies.\n"
"\n"
"When any of Mal-Ravanal’s recruits die, that unit will be reanimated as a "
"weaker undead version of itself. Enemies killed by Mal-Ravanal will rise "
"again as ghosts."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade consegue reanimar seus aliados e inimigos derrotados.\n"
"\n"
"Quando qualquer um do recrutas de Mal-Ravanal morrer, esta unidade será "
"reanimada como uma versão morta-viva mais fraca de si mesmo. Inimigos mortos "
"por Mal-Ravanal se levantarão novamente como fantasmas."

#. [unit_type]: id=Skeletal Corpse, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Skeletal_Corpse.cfg:5
msgid "Skeletal Corpse"
msgstr "Corpo Esquelético"

#. [unit_type]: id=Skeletal Corpse, race=undead
#. [unit_type]: id=Skeletal Soulless, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Skeletal_Corpse.cfg:14
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Skeletal_Soulless.cfg:16
msgid ""
"When a skeletal warrior is defeated, their animating energies are sometimes "
"not wholly destroyed. A particularly skilled lich can recapture what remains "
"of their servants’ necromantic energy, reanimating a new — albeit weaker — "
"minion."
msgstr ""
"Quando um guerreiro esquelético é derrotado, suas energias reanimadoras as "
"vezes não são completamente destruídas. Um lich particularmente habilidoso "
"consegue recapturar o que sobra da energia necrótica de seus servos, "
"reanimando um novo — embora mais fraco — lacaio."

#. [unit_type]: id=Skeletal Soulless, race=undead
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/units/Undead_Skeletal_Soulless.cfg:5
msgid "Skeletal Soulless"
msgstr "Desalmado Esquelético"

#. [drains]: id=greater drains
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:6
msgid "greater drains"
msgstr "dreno maior"

#. [drains]: id=greater drains
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:7
msgid ""
"This unit drains health from living units, healing itself for the full "
"amount of damage it deals."
msgstr ""
"Está unidade drena a vida de unidades vivas, curando-se pela quantidade "
"total de dano causado."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:54
msgid "Your soul is mine!!"
msgstr "Sua alma é minha!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:133
msgid ""
"Funny thing about the undead. If you know what you’re doing, they’re really "
"very easy to put back together."
msgstr ""
"Coisa engraçada sobre os mortos-vivos. Se você sabe o que está fazendo, eles "
"são realmente muito fáceis de remontar."

#. [attacks]: id=swift
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:141
msgid "swift"
msgstr "rápido"

#. [attacks]: id=swift
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:142
msgid ""
"This attack is exceptionally swift. When this attack is used on offense, the "
"opponent will be unable to retaliate."
msgstr ""
"Este ataque é excepcionalmente rápido. Quando este ataque é usado "
"ofensivamente, o oponente não será capaz de retaliar."

#. [attacks]: id=stagger
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:152
msgid "stagger"
msgstr ""

#. [attacks]: id=stagger
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:153
msgid ""
"The crushing power of this attack overwhelms enemies. When used on offense, "
"the opponent can only retaliate with one strike."
msgstr ""
"O poder esmagador deste ataque sobrepuja os inimigos. Quando usado "
"ofensivamente, o oponente só consegue retaliar com um ataque."

#. [attacks]: id=stagger
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:154
msgid ""
"This unit’s melee attack can overwhelm enemies’ defenses, preventing them "
"from retaliating as effectively."
msgstr ""
"Os ataques corpo-a-corpo desta unidade conseguem sobrepujar as defesas dos "
"seus inimigos, fazendo com que eles não consigam contra-atacar direito."

#. [dummy]: id=vanguard
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:164
msgid "vanguard"
msgstr "vanguarda"

#. [dummy]: id=vanguard
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:165
msgid ""
"This unit fights best in the heart of battle, surrounded by friends and foes "
"alike.\n"
"\n"
"Deals an additional 25% damage for each adjacent ally and/or enemy after the "
"first."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade luta melhor no coração da batalha, cercada por amigos e "
"inimigos.\n"
"\n"
"Causo 25% de dano adicional para cada aliado e/ou inimigo adjacente após o "
"primeiro."

#. [dummy]: id=vanguard
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:168
msgid "This unit gains increased damage for each adjacent ally and/or enemy."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade ganha dano adicional para cada aliado e/ou inimigo adjacente."

#. [illuminates]: id=darkens
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:233
msgid "darkens"
msgstr "escurece"

#. [illuminates]: id=darkens
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:234
msgid ""
"This unit darkens the surrounding area, making chaotic units fight better, "
"and lawful units fight worse.\n"
"\n"
"Any units adjacent to this unit will fight as if it were dusk when it is "
"day, and as if it were night when it is dusk."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade escurece a área ao seu redor, fazendo unidades caóticas lutarem "
"melhor e unidades ordeiras lutarem pior.\n"
"\n"
"Qualquer unidade adjacente a esta lutará como se fosse anoitecer durante o "
"dia e como se fosse noite quando é anoitecer."

#. [illuminates]: id=obfuscation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:247
msgid "obfuscates"
msgstr "obscurece"

#. [illuminates]: id=obfuscation
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:248
msgid ""
"This unit obfuscates the surrounding area, making chaotic units fight much "
"better, and lawful units fight much worse."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade obscurece a área ao seu redor, fazendo unidades caóticas "
"lutarem muito melhor, e unidades ordeiras lutarem muito pior."

#. [skirmisher]: id=nightskirmish
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:257
msgid "nightskirmish"
msgstr "escaramuçador noturno"

#. [skirmisher]: id=nightskirmish
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:258
msgid "female^nightskirmish"
msgstr "escaramuçadora noturna"

#. [skirmisher]: id=nightskirmish
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:259
msgid ""
"This unit is skilled in moving past enemies quickly and ignores all enemy "
"Zones of Control, but only at night."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade é habilidosa em passar por entre inimigos rapidamente e ignora "
"todas as zonas de controle inimigas, mas apenas à noite."

#. [dummy]: id=terror
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:273
msgid "terror"
msgstr "terror"

#. [dummy]: id=terror
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:274
msgid ""
"This unit can frighten enemies in a 2 hex radius, making them fight worse. "
"Units with the fearless trait are unaffected.\n"
"\n"
"When an enemy unit of lower level within a 2 hex radius engages in combat, "
"its attacks do 25% less damage times the difference in their levels."
msgstr ""
"Esta unidade consegue amedrontar inimigos em um raio de 2 hexágonos, fazendo "
"com que lutem pior. Unidades com a característica destemido não são "
"afetadas.\n"
"\n"
"Quando uma unidade inimiga de nível inferior dentro de um raio de 2 "
"hexágonos entra em combate, seus ataques causam 25% vezes a diferença de "
"nível entre eles a menos de dano."

#. [resistance]: id=shroud
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:511
msgid "shroud"
msgstr "encoberto"

#. [resistance]: id=shroud
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:512
msgid "While defending, this unit has 50% fire and arcane resistance."
msgstr ""
"Ao defender, esta unidade tem 50% de resistência contra dano arcano e de "
"fogo."

#. [damage_type]: id=arcane_damage_blessing
#. [damage_type]: id=arcane_damage_ranged_blessing
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:524
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:536
msgid "arcane blessing"
msgstr ""

#. [damage_type]: id=arcane_damage_blessing
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:525
msgid ""
"All attacks combine the arcane type with the type of the weapon used, so "
"that resistance to arcane does not penalize the user."
msgstr ""

#. [damage_type]: id=arcane_damage_blessing
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:526
msgid ""
"This unit’s weapons are treated as arcane instead of the declared damage "
"type if that would increase the damage."
msgstr ""

#. [damage_type]: id=arcane_damage_ranged_blessing
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:537
msgid ""
"All bow or crossbow attacks combine the arcane type with the type of the "
"weapon used, so that resistance to arcane does not penalize the user."
msgstr ""

#. [damage_type]: id=arcane_damage_ranged_blessing
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/abilities.cfg:538
msgid ""
"This unit’s bow or crossbow attacks are treated as arcane instead of the "
"declared damage type if that would increase the damage."
msgstr ""

#. [trait]: id=loyal_dummy
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/character-definitions.cfg:16
msgid "loyal"
msgstr "leal"

#. [trait]: id=loyal_dummy
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/character-definitions.cfg:17
msgid "Zero upkeep"
msgstr "Manutenção zero"

#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/character-definitions.cfg:27
msgid "Gweddry"
msgstr "Gweddry"

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/character-definitions.cfg:46
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:825
msgid "Dacyn"
msgstr "Dacyn"

#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/character-definitions.cfg:61
msgid "Owaec"
msgstr "Owaec"

#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/character-definitions.cfg:93
msgid "Konrad II"
msgstr "Konrad II"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:13
msgid "No! I... die..."
msgstr "Não! Eu... morro..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:30
msgid "I... must— Argh...!"
msgstr "Eu... devo— Argh...!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:47
msgid "The light fades... We are doomed..."
msgstr "A luz se apaga... Estamos perdidos..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:65
msgid "So much death... so much senseless destruction..."
msgstr "Tanta morte... tanta destruição sem sentido..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:69
msgid ""
"Unfortunate. Gweddry has fought with me since the very beginning, only to "
"fall so close to the end."
msgstr ""
"Mas que pena. Gweddry lutou comigo desde o começo, apenas para cair tão "
"perto do final."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:84
msgid "Alas, I fall! The clans will never truly be avenged..."
msgstr "Ah, eu morro! Os clãs nunca serão verdadeiramente vingados..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:88
msgid "Owaec! We’ve been through so much together! You can’t die now..."
msgstr "Owaec! Passamos por tanta coisa juntos! Você não pode morrer agora..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:102
msgid "The light fades... Wesnoth, I have failed you..."
msgstr "A luz se apaga... Wesnoth, eu falhei com você..."

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:121
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Watch out behind ye- ach!"
msgid "Watch out behind ye— ach!"
msgstr "Olhe atrás de vo- ach!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#. [message]: id=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:125
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:144
msgid ""
"Though he was not one of us, he served bravely alongside Wesnoth’s best. We "
"must carry on the good fight."
msgstr ""
"Embora não fosse um de nós, ele serviu bravamente ao lado dos melhores de "
"Wesnoth. Devemos continuar nossa luta justa."

#. [message]: speaker=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:139
msgid "Hurt... grarrgghh..."
msgstr "Dói... grarrgghh..."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:158
msgid "How did I get dragged into this mess..."
msgstr "Como que eu fui arrastado para essa confusão..."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:172
msgid ""
"Alas, my long, storied, and exceedingly profitable career has at last come "
"to an end, so far from home! I only... wish I could have died on the soft "
"sands... instead of among these primitive barbarians..."
msgstr ""
"Ai de mim, minha longa, celebrada, e extremamente rentável carreira "
"finalmente chegou ao fim, tão longe de casa! Eu apenas... queria ter morrido "
"nas areias macias... ao invés de morrer entre esses bárbaros primitivos..."

#. [message]: id=Grug
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:177
msgid "Bar... ber... bears? Die why?"
msgstr "Bar... ber... ursos? Morreu por quê?"

#. [message]: id=Dolburras
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:182
msgid ""
"Aye, ‘tis a sad place for one o’ us foreigners to fall. We’ll miss ye, "
"that’s for sure."
msgstr ""
"Si, este é un lugar triste para un de nós, os estranxeiros, cair. Iremos "
"sentir falta de você, isto é certo."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:196
msgid "Oh, I knew drinking all those elixirs was a bad idea..."
msgstr "Ah, eu sabia que beber todos esses elixires era uma péssima ideia..."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:210
msgid ""
"And so, I give... the last thing I have to give... in service of the Light..."
msgstr ""
"E então, eu sacrifico... a última coisa que eu tenho para sacrificar... em "
"serviço da Luz..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:214
msgid ""
"You shall be gravely missed, paladin of the Light! May you long live on in "
"song and tale."
msgstr ""
"Nós sentiremos muito sua falta, paladino da Luz! Que você tenha uma vida "
"longa em músicas e contos."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:227
msgid "Death is coming for me..."
msgstr "A morte está vindo para mim..."

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:231
msgid ""
"Truly, you have proven that there is goodness within all of us. I pledge "
"that your sacrifice will not be in vain!"
msgstr ""
"De fato, você provou que há bondade em todos nós. Garanto que seu sacrifício "
"não será em vão!"

#. [message]: speaker=Yannic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:246
msgid "Alas, I fall..."
msgstr "Eu morro..."

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:258
msgid "Yannic! The Clans have lost another brave soul this day..."
msgstr "Yannic! Os clãs perderam outra brava alma neste dia..."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:274
msgid "I may die, but Wesnoth will never fall!"
msgstr "Eu posso morrer, mas Wesnoth nunca cairá!"

#. [message]: speaker=Halric
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:288
msgid "There’s too many! Must... keep fighting..."
msgstr "São numerosos demais! Preciso... continuar lutando..."

#. [message]: speaker=Halrod
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:302
msgid ""
"Ack! Curse these undead! I should have listened to my mother and been a "
"dentist..."
msgstr ""
"Ack! Malditos mortos-vivos! Eu deveria ter escutado minha mãe e me tornado "
"um dentista..."

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:316
msgid "Alas, I perish! The kingdom is lost without its king."
msgstr "Ai de mim, pereço! O reino está perdido sem seu rei."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:330
msgid ""
"It was perhaps as well for the men of Gweddry’s troop that they did not live "
"to witness the fullness of the grim tide of undead sweeping westward into "
"Wesnoth, laying waste to all in its path."
msgstr ""
"Talvez tenha sido melhor para os homens sob o comande de Gweddry não terem "
"vivido para ver a totalidade da maré sombria de mortos-vivos devastando tudo "
"em direção ao oeste até Wesnoth, aniquilando tudo em seu caminho."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:341
msgid ""
"Wesnoth never learned the fate of Gweddry’s band, but they would soon learn "
"the full measure of the power of Mal-Ravanal in a war that would end only in "
"misery and death."
msgstr ""
"Wesnoth nunca descobriu o destino do grupo de Gweddry, mas eles logo "
"descobririam o completo poder de Mal-Ravanal em uma guerra que terminaria em "
"miséria e morte."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:351
msgid ""
"Their home country had proved to be no refuge for Gweddry’s weary men, and "
"no more would it for the inhabitants of Wesnoth as foes pressed them on all "
"sides to a final defense of the doomed kingdom."
msgstr ""
"Sua terra natal provou não ser um refúgio para os homens cansados de "
"Gweddry, e muito menos para os habitantes de Wesnoth conforme seus oponentes "
"lhes pressionavam de todos os lados até o reino condenado ser forçado a "
"fazer uma última defesa."

#. [message]: speaker=narrator
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:361
msgid ""
"With the staunchest defenders of Wesnoth bested on their home ground, the "
"once-great kingdom was plunged into final darkness under the hand of Mal-"
"Ravanal."
msgstr ""
"Com os melhores defensores de Wesnoth derrotados em seu próprio território, "
"o outrora grandioso reino foi mergulhado nas trevas eternas pelas mãos de "
"Mal-Ravanal."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Mana
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:376
msgid "My beautiful bats, why didn’t you protect me..."
msgstr "Meus lindos morcegos, porquê vocês não me protegeram..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Talar
#. death of a male Necromancer. Mal-Talar survived in S01 but the player has now killed him.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:393
msgid "No! Once again you escape me..."
msgstr "Não! Mais uma vez você escapou de mim..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Talar
#. death of a male Necromancer. Mal-Talar died in S01 and the player has now killed his renamed clone too.
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:401
msgid "No! How am I defeated so easily..."
msgstr "Não! Como que eu fui derrotado tão facilmente..."

#. [message]: speaker=Naken-alvak
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/deaths.cfg:429
msgid "You... waste... your effort..."
msgstr "Você... desperdiça... seu esforço..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:27
msgid "A-ha, what’s this? The white mage resorts to wielding black magic?"
msgstr "A-ha, o que é isso?Om mago branco recorrendo a magia negra?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:45
msgid ""
"Ah, the feeling of my flesh burned away by your nauseating radiance... this "
"takes me back to when I still thought of you as my friend."
msgstr ""
"Ah, a sensação da minha carne queimando pelo seu brilho nauseante... isso me "
"lembra de quando eu ainda considerava você como um amigo."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:49
msgid ""
"I only did what I had to do. Your mad quest for power has corrupted you and "
"turned you into a tormented creature of darkness! It is high time I ended "
"your existence!"
msgstr ""
"Eu apenas fiz o que tinha que fazer. Sua insana busca por poder te corrompeu "
"e tornou-o uma criatura atormentada pelas trevas! Já passou da hora de eu "
"acabar com a sua existência!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:70
msgid "For King and country!"
msgstr "Pelo Rei e pela nação!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gweddry
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:86
msgid "So much death, so much destruction... this has to end, now!"
msgstr "Tanta morte, tanta destruição... isto tem que acabar, agora!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:105
msgid "I shall avenge my fallen people!"
msgstr "Eu vingarei meu povo morto!"

#. [message]: speaker=Owaec
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:121
msgid ""
"Mal-Ravanal, at last I face you. I will have my vengeance for the "
"destruction you wrought on my people!"
msgstr ""
"Mal-Ravanal, finalmente eu estou enfrentando você. Eu terei minha vingança "
"pela destruição que você causou ao meu povo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:140
msgid "Aye, I love the sound o’ bones crunching beneath me hammer!"
msgstr "Si, encanta-me o som dos ósos que se rompen embaixo d' meu martelo!"

# Resolvi usar um provérbio Brasileiro similar "quanto maior a altura, maior a queda"  (me parece mais raciocínio lógico do que provérbio, mas é usado como se fosse provérbio)
#. [message]: speaker=Dolburras
#. in regular English, "So you are the big one, aren't you? Well, the bigger they are"
#. there is a colloquial expression, "the bigger they are, the harder they fall"
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:158
msgid "Ooch, so you be the big ’un, aren’t ye? Well, the bigger they are..."
msgstr "Ouu, tu és o grandão, non é? Pois quanto maior a altura..."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:177
msgid ""
"Never thought I’d be seeing this in my lifetime. The whole blasted "
"apocalypse came early, didn’t it."
msgstr ""
"Nunca pensei que veria isso durante a minha vida. O maldito apocalipse veio "
"mais cedo do que eu esperava."

#. [message]: speaker=Addogin
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:193
msgid "Aww hell. If I live through this, I’m never pickin’ up a sword again."
msgstr "Arg inferno. Se eu sobreviver a isso, nunca mais pego numa espada."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:212
msgid ""
"How in the sands did I get caught up in all this mess? I’m an herbalist, not "
"a warrior!"
msgstr ""
"Pelas areias como que eu fui me meter em toda essa confusão? Eu sou um "
"herbalista, não um guerreiro!"

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:228
msgid "No, no no, no, what am I even doing here!"
msgstr "Não, não não não, o que é que eu estou fazendo aqui!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:247
msgid ""
"Ashes to ashes, dust to dust. The undead have no place in this bright world!"
msgstr ""
"Cinzas às cinzas, pó ao pó. Os mortos-vivos não tem lugar neste mundo de luz!"

#. [message]: speaker=Terraent
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:263
msgid ""
"Foul lich, no longer shall you toy with me for your amusement! No longer "
"shall I watch your armies slaughter the innocent! No longer shall your evil "
"darken this world!"
msgstr ""
"Lich imundo, você não mais brincará comigo para o seu próprio prazer! Não "
"mais verei seus exércitos massacrarem inocentes! Não mais sua maldade "
"escurecerá esse mundo!"

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:282
msgid "I remember when I used to raise creatures like you..."
msgstr "Eu me lembro de quando eu costumava reanimar criaturas como você..."

#. [message]: speaker=Gaennell
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:298
msgid ""
"I loyally served you, once. Look at what that got me. A whole lot of nothing."
msgstr ""
"Eu servi você com lealdade no passado. Veja aonde isso me levou. Um monte de "
"nada."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:303
msgid "I don’t even know who you are."
msgstr "Eu nem sequer sei quem você é."

#. [message]: speaker=Yannic
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:321
msgid ""
"So you are the lich behind this madness! Enough is enough. Vengeance for "
"Soradoc; vengeance for the Plains!"
msgstr ""
"Então você é o lich por detrás dessa loucura! Já chega. Vingança por "
"Soradoc; vingança pelas Planícies!"

#. [message]: speaker=Konrad
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:339
msgid ""
"You are no savior of Man! Naught but a pile of bones, a dead mage too "
"stubborn to fall. Wesnoth will suffer you no longer!"
msgstr ""
"Você não é um salvador da humanidade! És nada além de uma pilha de ossos, um "
"mago morto teimoso demais para morrer. Wesnoth não sofrerá por conta de você "
"mais!"

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:372
msgid ""
"<i>*gulp*</i> Well, it’s now or never. I’d better not think too hard about "
"the fortune in elixirs that I’m about to drink away."
msgstr ""
"<i>*gulp*</i> Bom, é agora ou nunca. É melhor não pensar muito sobre os "
"elixires que eu estou para beber."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:380
msgid "Agility in swamp and shallow water..."
msgstr "Agilidade em pântanos e em águas rasas..."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:385
msgid "Resistance to fire and cold..."
msgstr "Resistência ao fogo e ao frio..."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:390
msgid "Speed and defense..."
msgstr "Velocidade e defesa..."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:395
msgid "And berserker fury. Oh sands, what am I doing..."
msgstr "E fúria do berserker. Ah areias, o que eu estou fazendo..."

#. [message]: speaker=Hahid al-Ali
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:404
msgid "Ugh, I feel queasy..."
msgstr "Ugh, eu me sinto enjoado..."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:421
msgid "What?! How could this happen?!"
msgstr "O quê?! Como isso pôde acontecer?!"

#. [message]: speaker=$found_unit.id
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:480
msgid "Is it over? We’ve won?"
msgstr "Acabou? Nós ganhamos?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:494
msgid "A-ha haha! You really thought you had a chance there, didn’t you?"
msgstr "A-ha haha! Você realmente pensou que tinha uma chance, não é?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:498
msgid ""
"Well, coming to the battlefield myself has been entertaining, but that’s "
"enough for now."
msgstr ""
"Bem, vir ao campo de batalha pessoalmente foi divertido, mas por hora isso é "
"o suficiente."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:502
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "You escaped me once before-"
msgid "You escaped me once before—"
msgstr "Você escapou de mim uma vez antes-"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:550
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "-but NEVER AGAIN!!!"
msgid "—but NEVER AGAIN!!!"
msgstr "-mas NUNCA MAIS!!!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:561
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Wha- what is this?!"
msgid "Wha— what is this?!"
msgstr "O- o que é isso?!"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:568
msgid "Do you even know where that gate you’re opening leads to?"
msgstr "Você sequer sabe para onde leva este portão que estás abrindo?"

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:585
msgid ""
"...you think you’re better than me, don’t you? You must think of yourself as "
"some kind of hero."
msgstr ""
"...você pensa que é melhor do que eu, não é? Você deve achar que é algum "
"tipo de herói."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:592
msgid ""
"You think that a stiff old codger like yourself has what it takes to use "
"that amulet to destroy me? I doubt you even know what you’re doing."
msgstr ""
"Você pensa que um velho excêntrico como você tem o que é necessário para "
"usar esse amuleto para me destruir? Eu duvido que você sequer sabe o que "
"está fazendo."

#. [message]: speaker=Mal-Ravanal
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:603
msgid "Ha. Ah-ha, haha. Have it your way. I’ll be seeing you soon."
msgstr "Ha. Ah-ha, haha. Faça do seu jeito. Eu verei você em breve."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:651
msgid "It is done."
msgstr "Está feito."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:747
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:748
msgid "Fallen Soul"
msgstr "Alma Caída"

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:763
msgid ""
"Well done! Who else but Dacyn the Magnificent could have defeated such a "
"rival? You truly are the greatest of heroes."
msgstr ""
"Parabéns! Mas quem além de Dacyn o Magnífico poderia ter derrotado tal "
"rival? Você realmente é o maior dos heróis."

#. [message]: speaker=spirit2
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:767
msgid "Now, embrace our power! You shall live on as the champion of Irdya!"
msgstr ""
"Agora, aceite o nosso poder! Você viverá para sempre como o campeão de Irdya!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:771
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Wha- where am I? What’s happening to me?"
msgid "Wha— where am I? What’s happening to me?"
msgstr "O qu- onde estou? O que está acontecendo comigo?"

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:775
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "The mage called Dacyn is dying! It is time for you to be reborn!"
msgid ""
"The mage called Dacyn is dying! It is time for you to be reborn under a new "
"name: Mal-Dak‘an."
msgstr "O mago chamado Dacyn está morrendo! É chegada a hora de você renascer!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:779
msgid ""
"—I... —I am no necromancer! Everything I have done is for the good of "
"Wesnoth."
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:783
msgid ""
"Was it? Was it for the good of all Wesnoth when you took Iliah-Malal’s "
"Amulet of the Veil, turning to the darkness and letting us into your soul?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:787
msgid ""
"Was it for the good of Wesnoth when you enslaved the seer Eryssa’s senile "
"mind, so the King would choose you as his advisor over Ravan?"
msgstr ""

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:791
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I... I needed this power! I had to safeguard Irdya!"
msgid ""
"I... I needed that power! I was the only one who could be trusted to "
"safeguard Irdya!"
msgstr "Eu... eu precisava deste poder! Eu tinha que proteger Irdya!"

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:795
msgid ""
"And now you can, for all eternity! Leave your mortal coil behind. Live on as "
"an undying spirit of mighty power, and do unto this world as you will!"
msgstr ""
"E agora você pode, por toda a eternidade! Deixe o ciclo mortal para trás. "
"Viva como um espírito imortal de grande poder, e faça com este mundo o que "
"quiseres!"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:799
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "I... but... I could never choose to-"
msgid "I... but... I could never choose to—"
msgstr "Eu... mas... eu nunca conseguiria escolher-"

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:812
msgid ""
"You misunderstand. This is no choice of yours.\n"
"\n"
"The stone bleeds your flesh. The darkness consumes your soul. Rebirth into "
"undeath is the only path forward to escape the Maw, else ye embrace oblivion."
msgstr ""
"Você entendeu errado. Não há escolha para você.\n"
"\n"
"A pedra sangra sua carne. A escuridão consome sua alma. Renascer para a vida-"
"em-morte é o único caminho para escapar da Boca, senão abraçarás a perdição."

#. [event]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:816
#, fuzzy
#| msgid "Mak-Dak’an"
msgid "Mal-Dak’an"
msgstr "Mak-Dak’an"

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:836
msgid ""
"No. For too long, I have allowed my pride to overrule my wisdom. I have been "
"arrogant. I have been the fool in this story. I believed I and only I was "
"destined for greatness. But I can see it clearly now. I have been no "
"different than my dear friend Ravan. We have been the same all along."
msgstr ""
"Não. Eu deixei meu orgulho sobrepor minha sabedoria por tempo demais. Tenho "
"sido arrogante. Tenho sido o tolo nessa história. Acreditei que eu e apenas "
"eu estava destinado à grandeza. Mas agora vejo claramente. Eu tenho agido da "
"mesma maneira que meu caro amigo Ravan. Nós fomos iguais desde sempre."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:840
msgid "But no longer. My will is my own."
msgstr "Mas não mais. Eu que decido o meu próprio destino."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:844
msgid ""
"I will not be tempted by undeath. I will pass unto the Land of the Dead, and "
"if I am to be damned there then so be it."
msgstr ""
"Não serei tentado pela vida-em-morte. Eu irei para a Terra dos Mortos, e se "
"lá eu tiver que pagar o preço pelo que fiz em vida, que assim seja."

#. [message]: speaker=Dacyn
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:848
msgid "My story ends here."
msgstr "Minha história termina aqui."

#. [message]: speaker=spirit2
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:860
msgid "So be it."
msgstr "Que assim seja."

#. [message]: speaker=spirit
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:864
msgid "<i>THE MAW OPENS ITS JAWS.</i>"
msgstr "<i>A BOCA ABRE SUAS MANDÍBULAS</i>"

#. [message]: speaker=spirit2
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/final_battle/final_battle.cfg:880
msgid "<i>DARKNESS CONSUMES THE SOUL.</i>"
msgstr "<i>A ESCURIDÃO CONSOME A ALMA</i>"

