"frio."

#. [item_dialog_musttake]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1256
msgid "Elixir of Haste"
msgstr "Elixir da Pressa"

#. [item_dialog_musttake]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1258
msgid ""
"This saccharine green liquid grants +1 movement and +10% defense on all "
"terrain. You may have difficulty standing still."
msgstr ""
"Este líquido verde açucarado garante +1 de movimento e +10% de defesa em "
"todos os terrenos. Você pode ter dificuldade para ficar parado."

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1281
msgid "<span color='#0BDA51' size='x-small'>haste</span>"
msgstr "<span color='#0BDA51' size='x-small'>pressa</span>"

#. [trait]: id=TRAIT_haste
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1293
msgid "haste"
msgstr "pressa"

#. [trait]: id=TRAIT_haste
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1294
msgid ""
"An elixir of haste has given this unit +1 movement and +10% defense on all "
"terrain."
msgstr ""
"Um elixir da pressa deu a esta unidade +1 de movimento e +10% de defesa em "
"todos os terrenos."

#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1332
msgid "Elixir of Fury"
msgstr "Elixir da Fúria"

#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1333
msgid ""
"The red liquid in this vial sloshes violently, as though trying to escape. "
"Drinking it grants <b><i>unlimited melee attacks</i></b> and the "
"<b><i>berserk</i></b> melee special."
msgstr ""
"O líquido vermelho neste frasco se agita violentamente, parecendo tentar "
"escapar. Bebê-lo garante <b><i>ataques corpo-a-corpo ilimitados</i></b> e o "
"especial corpo-a-corpo <b><i>frenesi</i></b>."

#. [floating_text]
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1353
msgid "<span color='#FF0000' size='x-small'>berserker fury</span>"
msgstr "<span color='#FF0000' size='x-small'>fúria berserker</span>"

#. [trait]: id=TRAIT_fury
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1365
msgid "fury"
msgstr "fúria"

#. [trait]: id=TRAIT_fury
#: data/campaigns/Eastern_Invasion/utils/items.cfg:1366
